NK030(a)001:5149: bu khyod bsgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK030(a)001:5150: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK030(a)001:5151: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru //
NK030(a)001:5152: gtsang sbras 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:5153: dri sha chu yi bza' btung dang //
NK030(a)001:5154: nga yi b+ha ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK030(a)001:5157: sems chu btung par khyod nus sam /
NK030(a)001:5161: bdag ni gang yang mi nus med //
NK030(a)001:5162: de dag bdag gis sbyad par bgyi //
NK030(a)001:5163: ci ltar sad phyir bdag la stsol //
NK030(a)001:5166: rig ma'i lag nas bzung ste /
NK030(a)001:5167: slob ma la gtod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5168: skye med chos dbyings rig pa 'byung pa'i yum //
NK030(a)001:5169: mtshan ldan rig ma mchog gi brgyan //
NK030(a)001:5170: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rol pa las //
NK030(a)001:5171: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK030(a)001:5173: / 'phags mchog bde bsgrub 'bras bu kun mnyes so //
NK030(a)001:5174: gnyis med don spyod chos nyid dag pa'i brgyan //
NK030(a)001:5175: dgyes pa'i ro mchog bde chen dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:5176: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu he pra dz+ny+aa shwa ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)001:5178: de nas 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5179: bde ba dbab pa'i thabs gtum mo sbar ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5180: rtsa rlung thig le bsgom pa'i thabs rnams bslabs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5181: sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK030(a)001:5182: dri chen gyi bza' ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5184: nye'u shing gi khu ba btung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5187: dri zhim pos byug la rgyan gyis brgyan /
NK030(a)001:5188: lus sems stong pa nyid las /
NK030(a)001:5189: khro mor bsgom gnas lngar khro mo lnga 'god /
NK030(a)001:5190: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi 'god /
NK030(a)001:5191: nam mkha' bam las pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa e mthing khas mtshan pa 'od dang ldan pa bskyed /
NK030(a)001:5192: slob bu bud+d+ha he ru kar bsgoms la /
NK030(a)001:5194: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi bskyed la /
NK030(a)001:5195: gsang ba h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga
NK030(a)001:5196: pa bsgoms pa'i rwa la yab kyi 'bru lnga dang
NK030(a)001:5197: / dbus kyi rtsa gsum las 'bru gsum mdor phata sgom /
NK030(a)001:5198: dri zhim po sbrang gis sbyar ba'i ril bu mur zhing /
NK030(a)001:5199: pad+ma la bltas te yongs su rgyas nas /
NK030(a)001:5200: phyag rgya bzhis rol du gzhug /
NK030(a)001:5202: spyi bo nas 'khor lo bzhi la rim bzhin dbab cing /
NK030(a)001:5203: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bskyed la //
NK030(a)001:5204: rang rig ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK030(a)001:5205: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo rdo rje'i
NK030(a)001:5206: nor bu rtser phebs pa'i dus na gzung zhing bskyil
NK030(a)001:5207: ste / de yang rlung bum pa can gzung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5208: yig 'bru'i sbyor bas gzung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5209: lus kyi 'phrul 'khor gyis bzung ba la sogs pas /
NK030(a)001:5210: thig le bzung ba'i dus na gzung 'dzin gyi rtog
NK030(a)001:5211: pa thams cad dang bral ba'i lhan gcig skyes pa'i
NK030(a)001:5212: ye shes bde stong dbyer med kyi chos nyid 'od
NK030(a)001:5213: gsal dri ma med pa'i don /
NK030(a)001:5214: ci bzhin ye mnyam chen po'i dgongs pa gnyis med
NK030(a)001:5215: thig le nyag gcig gi rtogs pa ci lta ba
NK030(a)001:5216: bzhin nyams su myong zhing ngo shes par gyur to
NK030(a)001:5217: // gnyis ka'i lag pa nas gzung nas //
NK030(a)001:5218: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK030(a)001:5219: sgrol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK030(a)001:5220: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK030(a)001:5221: bla ma chen po'i sar gnas su //
NK030(a)001:5222: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)001:5223: gcig pu sa bzung mnga' mnyes nas //
NK030(a)001:5224: bde khyab chen po'i 'phrin las las //
NK030(a)001:5225: khams gsum sras su bzung bar byos //
NK030(a)001:5229: rang byung gi ye shes 'char ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5231: bdun pa ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK030(a)001:5233: mngal gyis yi dwags su btung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5234: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi 'byung pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5235: gsum pa bde ba chen po'i dbang la'ang bdun las /
NK030(a)001:5237: don dam gyis shes bya sbyang ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5238: dug gis dug sbyang ba'i ched do //
NK030(a)001:5240: 'dod chags kyi ro bden pa gnyis med kyi ye
NK030(a)001:5241: shes rang la gnas pa thob bya nyid rgyu rkyen
NK030(a)001:5244: gnyis med kyi ye shes skye 'jig med kyi /
NK030(a)001:5245: gzung 'dzin spangs par rang bral bas /
NK030(a)001:5246: bde ba dang ldan pa zhes bya la /
NK030(a)001:5247: de gang la snang bas na /
NK030(a)001:5253: rten can dang rten med gnyis dang mtshon byed dang mtshon bya gnyis /
NK030(a)001:5255: dngos po lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes dang rang bzhin gyis gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5257: phyag rgya ma lo bcu gnyis ma bkug gcing khrus bya /
NK030(a)001:5259: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla ma la 'bul /
NK030(a)001:5260: de nas ji ltar 'os pa'i yum la dbang bskur la sbyor ba bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5261: gzungs ma'i don dam pa'i lte ba na /
NK030(a)001:5262: zla ba tshes pa lta bu'i nang na byang chub
NK030(a)001:5263: sems kyi thig le dkar po yungs dkar tsam zhig
NK030(a)001:5264: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa la ting 'dzin gyis dmigs
NK030(a)001:5265: te gsang ba'i rdo rje ye shes kyi ro can
NK030(a)001:5266: dang / b+ha ga'i theg le dang /
NK030(a)001:5268: yab kyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi theg le dang mkha' la gnas pa de basre'o //
NK030(a)001:5270: pad+ma'i khyams na b+ho d+hi yod pa 'theb srin kyis blangs la /
NK030(a)001:5271: gzungs ma'i lce thog tu bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:5272: de nas yab yum gnyis ka sa //
NK030(a)001:5273: bdag bskyed khro ba'i dkyil 'khor snying po brjod la
NK030(a)001:5274: rdzogs pa'i tshul du lus dkyil bskyed sa man dzas
NK030(a)001:5275: snyan gsan dbab / e h+ya his sbyan drangs /
NK030(a)001:5276: dzah+aum bam hognyis su med par bstim la /
NK030(a)001:5277: mchod bstod bsnyen pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK030(a)001:5278: mdun bskyed kyang gong bzhin du bsnyen pa yan chad byas la /
NK030(a)001:5280: de nas slob bu'i gung mo g.yas pa dang gzungs ma'i gung mo g.yon rat+na phreng bas bcings te /
NK030(a)001:5281: de'i mdo nas slob dpon gyis bzung ste /
NK030(a)001:5282: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK030(a)001:5283: shes rab thabs kyi rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:5285: / 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK030(a)001:5286: dngos grub gter bas 'di mi spongs /
NK030(a)001:5287: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK030(a)001:5288: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod las byung //
NK030(a)001:5289: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal //
NK030(a)001:5290: dgug dang bsgom pa ma shes na //
NK030(a)001:5291: rdo rje bskal ba mtha' klas pa //
NK030(a)001:5292: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK030(a)001:5293: de'i don rgyas par bshad do //
NK030(a)001:5295: dga' ba bzhi'i dbang gdam ngag 'bog ste /
NK030(a)001:5300: thog ma gzungs ma mthong bas bde ba g.yos pas dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5301: de nas gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5302: srin lag sbrel ba la sogs pa byas pas bde ba skyes pa mchog dga' 'o /
NK030(a)001:5304: / 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyi cha byed pa dga' bral lo //
NK030(a)001:5305: gzung ma dang rang lus rngul zhing bems kyis song ba ni /
NK030(a)001:5306: lhan gcig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5308: rang dang gzung ma gnyis ka la 'khor lo bzhi sgoms te /
NK030(a)001:5309: bde ba chen po'i tsa kra ni dga' ba /
NK030(a)001:5310: longs spyod kyi tsa kra ni mchog dga' /
NK030(a)001:5312: sprul pa'i tsakra ni lhan skyes so //
NK030(a)001:5314: gu h+ya badz+ra rtsa ba ni dga' ba /
NK030(a)001:5315: rdo rje'i sked pa ni mchog dga' /
NK030(a)001:5316: rdo rje'i bum pa ni dga' bral /
NK030(a)001:5319: de rnams re re la yang /
NK030(a)001:5320: thig le bzhi bzhi rtsis pas bcu drug ste /
NK030(a)001:5323: bcu gsang ba'i sa bcur shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5324: de ltar gdam ngag phog nas bus sbyor ba la snyoms par 'jug ste /
NK030(a)001:5325: rdo rje h+aum gcig bkod de spro bsdu la rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu gyur /
NK030(a)001:5328: rtse mo'i bu gar phata nag po b+ha ga la phatahnaga po gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:5329: de la spro bsdus pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa /
NK030(a)001:5330: de'i dbus su e mthing ga gru gsum pa de'i steng du h+aum dmar po gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)001:5331: de nas gzungs ma la 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyi cha rnams bya /
NK030(a)001:5333: rdo rje phyed tsam pad+mara bsdams te /
NK030(a)001:5335: sra bas myong ba 'byung ba sa /
NK030(a)001:5336: rdul cung zad gsher ba chu /
NK030(a)001:5338: de nas shes pa zhib tu bltas pas bde ba g.yos pa rlung ngo //
NK030(a)001:5339: de nas bde ba bzlog ste /
NK030(a)001:5343: dang po ni bde ba g.yo ba tsam na /
NK030(a)001:5344: rdo rje e tsam gcig pha tshad la phyung la lto ba rgal tshig la sbyar /
NK030(a)001:5347: ting nge 'dzin gyis bzlog pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5348: bde ba g.yos tsam na bstod kyi dbugs bsdams la /
NK030(a)001:5349: ro rkyang gnyis kyis rtsa sna dbus gyi kun d+har 'brel nas yod pa'i /
NK030(a)001:5350: ro rkyang nas dbugs zhugs pa las /
NK030(a)001:5351: kun d+har lhags pa'i b+ho d+hi gyen la 'khyil gyis ldog nas dkar chil gyis ldog par bsam mo /
NK030(a)001:5353: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas phar sor gnyis kyis thub tshad du mnan la ldog /
NK030(a)001:5354: sprul pa'i 'khor lo nas gyen la de ltar ldog /
NK030(a)001:5355: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas sked pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5356: rtse mo nas rim par ldog /
NK030(a)001:5358: rdo rje'i rtsa bar dga' ba'i thig le bzhi'i theg le gsum pa nas /
NK030(a)001:5359: rdo rje sked ba'i mchog dag'i thig le gnyis pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5361: de rdo rje rtse mo lhan gcig skyes pa gnas su zla ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5362: nyi ma'i theg le rdo rje dang /
NK030(a)001:5363: pad+ma rang rang gi kha nas ma shor bar zin tsa na /
NK030(a)001:5364: rang rig pa'i don dam nyams su myong ba de kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK030(a)001:5365: de'i dus su rgyu'i zung 'jug nyi zla 'dres pas /
NK030(a)001:5366: 'bras bu'i zung 'jug ye shes rang snang gi lha dang /
NK030(a)001:5367: lha mor snang bzhin du rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5368: de tsam na zhen pa med pa pad+ma can gyi sa'o //
NK030(a)001:5369: de la smon lam gyi dbang gis gzugs sku gnyis 'byung ba ni /
NK030(a)001:5370: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK030(a)001:5371: de ni theg pa 'og ma dang sgo bstun pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5372: de nas rgyu 'bras ldog pa'i theg pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5373: nyi zla thig le rang gi gnas su rtse mo na tshur ldog pas //
NK030(a)001:5375: rdo rje'i rtsa bar phyin pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5377: de nas sprul pa'i tsa krar phyin pa ni pad+ma can no //
NK030(a)001:5378: thig le rang gnas su phyin pa la dgye /
NK030(a)001:5379: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba ni /
NK030(a)001:5380: tshogs chen gyi sa mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK030(a)001:5381: gal te b+ho d+hi shor na /
NK030(a)001:5382: byang sems h'u dmar po sha rtag tu bsam la /
NK030(a)001:5383: mtheb srin gyis blang la khong du mid do //
NK030(a)001:5385: sbyor lam gyis mi rtogs pa'i bde ba skyes pa'i dus su /
NK030(a)001:5386: de la blo 'jog na gzungs ma mi dgos /
NK030(a)001:5387: mi rtag par blo gnas nas mi rtog pa sangs na yang dbang don de la blo gtad pas /
NK030(a)001:5389: de ltar sgom pa'i don la gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5391: pha rol tu phyin pa sngon du 'byin /
NK030(a)001:5393: bdun pa skyon ni de las bzlog pa nyid do //
NK030(a)001:5394: de ltar phyin nang zab mo'i dbang rnams la bye
NK030(a)001:5395: brag tu dbang gi rnams grangs sum cu so bdun
NK030(a)001:5397: de las mang ba 'dir sangs rgyas gsang bas ma bkral la /
NK030(a)001:5398: nyung na gzhung nas bshad pa'i dbang mi tshang ba'i phyir te /
NK030(a)001:5399: man ngag gi gzhung 'di nyid la legs par sbyad pas shes so //
NK030(a)001:5400: spyi don tha ma 'jug bsdu ba ni rjes kyi bya ba las /
NK030(a)001:5401: dang po dbang gi yon tan brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5402: bla mas gsang bum phyag tu bzhes la 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:5403: phyag rgya dbu rgyan snying po dang //
NK030(a)001:5404: gtso bo rus pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK030(a)001:5405: gzi mdangs rgyal mtshan zhing gi gdugs //
NK030(a)001:5407: lha dang phyag mtshan brgyan chas dang //
NK030(a)001:5408: sgrub rdzas gsang ba'i dbang gsum mo //
NK030(a)001:5411: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK030(a)001:5412: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK030(a)001:5413: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK030(a)001:5414: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)001:5415: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK030(a)001:5416: thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las
NK030(a)001:5417: kyi zhing khams dag pa zad mi shes pa brgyan
NK030(a)001:5418: gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5419: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs gyis /
NK030(a)001:5420: bdag rdo rje che ge mos rigs kyi bu 'di
NK030(a)001:5421: rnams sgyu 'phrul dra ba khrag 'thung khro bo'i dbang
NK030(a)001:5422: lnga yongs su rdzogs par bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:5423: dus 'di nas bzung ste rgyal ba rnams kyi sras kyis dam par dgongs shing /
NK030(a)001:5424: ngan song gsum gyi duh kha thams cad dang bral nas /
NK030(a)001:5425: mtho ris bde ba thams cad dang ldan nas /
NK030(a)001:5426: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag po rgyal
NK030(a)001:5427: ba sku lnga'i go 'phang bsgrod de yi ge 'khor
NK030(a)001:5428: lo tshogs chen kyi sa la lhun gyis gnas par
NK030(a)001:5429: gyur cig / gzhan yang dbang bskur chen po 'di'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK030(a)001:5430: yul phyogs 'di dang rgyal khams thams cad du yang /
NK030(a)001:5431: dus kyi 'khrugs pa zhi ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5432: mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5433: mi nad dang phyugs nad rgyun chad pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5434: char chu dus su phebs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5435: lo phyug rtag tu legs te /
NK030(a)001:5436: sems cad thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:5438: de nas gnyis pa dbang bsab par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5440: nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa thams cad 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)001:5441: rdo rje slob dpon bdag nyid la thim pas /
NK030(a)001:5442: sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin bkrag dang gzi mdangs su ldan ste /
NK030(a)001:5443: sngon bas kyang mthu che bar bsam pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5444: dbang bsab zhes bya ba rdo rje slob dpon nyid la shin du gces pa yin no //
NK030(a)001:5445: de nas gsum pa smon lam gdab ste /
NK030(a)001:5446: slob dpon gyis khri las babs te /
NK030(a)001:5447: rdo rje dril bu thogs shing /
NK030(a)001:5448: yum gyis mar me thogs nas //
NK030(a)001:5449: mched lcam thams cad thal mo sbyar nas /
NK030(a)001:5452: bsam rdzogs lhun grub phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dang //
NK030(a)001:5453: rgyal sras dpa' bo rnal 'byor kun gshegs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:5454: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK030(a)001:5455: lung dang man ngag zab mo kun bsdus pa //
NK030(a)001:5456: gsang sngags nang nas sgyu 'phrul dbang gi rigs //
NK030(a)001:5457: theg pa'i nang nas spyi blugs rgyal thabs te //
NK030(a)001:5458: yang gsang gter du spas ba'i man ngag 'dis /
NK030(a)001:5460: / 'gro ba kun gyis spyod yul ma yin yang //
NK030(a)001:5461: khams gsum 'khor ba'i duh kha brtsad gcad phyir //
NK030(a)001:5462: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:5463: blo sbyangs skal bar ldan pa'i bu rnams kyis //
NK030(a)001:5464: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi don rtogs shog /
NK030(a)001:5465: gzhan yang sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las /
NK030(a)001:5466: ngo mtshar rmad byung 'bras bu ci snyed pa /
NK030(a)001:5467: thabs shes 'gro don lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:5468: ces dril bu gsil zhing me tog dor la /
NK030(a)001:5469: ru lu gar gyis dkyil 'khor lan gsum bskor ro //
NK030(a)001:5470: de nas bzhi pa bslab bya brjod de /
NK030(a)001:5471: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)001:5472: he ru ka ni nga yin gyis //
NK030(a)001:5473: nga yis 'di skad bgo ba bzhin //
NK030(a)001:5474: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK030(a)001:5478: bslabs bya thams cad nan chags su bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5479: de nas lnga pa gtor ma btang par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5480: gtor ma rnams cha gsum du gcad la /
NK030(a)001:5482: chos kyi dbyings kyi gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5483: gter du sba ba'i cho ga bya /
NK030(a)001:5484: bar pa de ye shes rol ba'i gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5486: tha ma de thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5487: las mkhan gyi mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad mchod /
NK030(a)001:5490: nang du las bzhi'i bro bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5491: de nas drug pa bkra shis gsol te /
NK030(a)001:5492: dkar tshal btegs la me tog dor zhing /
NK030(a)001:5493: bkra shis kyi cho ga rgyas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5495: bla ma la btang rag btang zhing //
NK030(a)001:5496: bu rnams kyis phyag 'tshal zhing zhabs la sbyi bos gtug go /
NK030(a)001:5497: de nas brgyad pa dkyil 'khor bsdu /
NK030(a)001:5500: bum chu lhag mas mched lcam rnams khrus bya /
NK030(a)001:5501: dkyil 'khor zhabs bsil rdul tshon sman ma dang /
NK030(a)001:5503: sbyin bsreg gi thal ba rnams chu bo chen po la bskyal /
NK030(a)001:5505: de nas dgu pa bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o /
NK030(a)001:5506: spyod lam thams cad lha dang ma bral bar bya ste /
NK030(a)001:5510: longs spyod dus bzhir nyams blangs tshe //
NK030(a)001:5511: rig phyir thams cad dkyil 'khor lhar //
NK030(a)001:5512: gsal byas tha snyad zhen las grol /
NK030(a)001:5514: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK030(a)001:5515: de ltar sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang rdzogs nas /
NK030(a)001:5516: lha dbang de dag chags par byed pa'i rten du lha sgom pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5517: man ngag bsgom pa gnyis las /
NK030(a)001:5519: sngar me tog phog pa'i lha gang yin pa de /
NK030(a)001:5521: de'i rjes su snying po rjes gnang byin pas gsungs ngo sprad /
NK030(a)001:5522: dbang rdzas mgo thog tu bzhag nas dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:5524: de yang thog ma nas yin pa la yin pa ltar ngo sprad zhes pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5525: gser sprang ngo shes pa lta bu ste /
NK030(a)001:5526: de ni lha ngo sprad pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5527: de nas nye bar mtshon nas /
NK030(a)001:5528: snang grags thams cad lha dang gzhal yas khang gi
NK030(a)001:5529: dkyil 'khor du longs spyod pa ni lam du 'khyer
NK030(a)001:5530: ba'o // lhar snang ba thams cad sems nyid du thag chod pa ni lha la lhar rol ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5531: thams cad lha'i rang bzhin du blta ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5532: de'i ngang la gnas pa bsgom pa /
NK030(a)001:5533: spyod lam rnam bzhi lha dang mi 'bral ba ni spyod pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5534: de las mi 'da' ba ni dam bca' /
NK030(a)001:5537: glang po che rgun chang gis myos pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:5538: thad ka ni ngang sgom chung ngu'i thad kar slob ste /
NK030(a)001:5539: de yang bdag cag lhar gsal ba'i spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)001:5540: de nas khru gang gis mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)001:5541: de nas sna bug g.yon nas 'od dmar po sran ma tsam gcig byung nas /
NK030(a)001:5542: spyi bo'i thig le dmar po la phog pas /
NK030(a)001:5543: des bdag rkyen byas nas thig le dmar po las 'od 'phros pas /
NK030(a)001:5545: byang chub sems dpa' la phog pas thugs mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK030(a)001:5546: 'od de tshur 'dus theg le dmar po la thim pas //
NK030(a)001:5547: thig le 'od du zhu bar bsam yang sna bug g.yon nas 'od dkar por byung nas /
NK030(a)001:5548: gong gi thig le dkar po la phog pas /
NK030(a)001:5550: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog pas thugs mnyes tshur 'dus /
NK030(a)001:5551: thig le dkar po la thim /
NK030(a)001:5552: de babs nas dmar po la thim pas /
NK030(a)001:5553: snying kha snying gi dkyil du thim pas /
NK030(a)001:5554: dkar dmar 'dres nas spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar thim /
NK030(a)001:5555: de nyid snying gi dkyil du dkar dmar 'dres pa'i
NK030(a)001:5556: ngo bo bde stong gnyis med kyi ngang la blo
NK030(a)001:5557: skyur bzhag go / de ni lha bsgoms pa'i man ngag ces bya'o //
NK030(a)001:5558: man ngag bsgom pa la steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis las /
NK030(a)001:5559: dang po ni ngang sgoms 'bring po'i thad kar sleb ste /
NK030(a)001:5560: rang gi lus rkyal stong sang nge ba'i nang na /
NK030(a)001:5561: rtsa a wa d+hu ti sbom phra mda' snyug tsam phyi dmar la nang dkar ba /
NK030(a)001:5562: yar sna rtse'u chung la thug pa /
NK030(a)001:5563: mar sna gnyer mo che la thug pa de ni srog shing yin /
NK030(a)001:5564: sgrom mdo'i 'khor lo dang 'og sgo rlung gi 'khor lo la gnyis khri 'phangs yin no //
NK030(a)001:5565: lte ba bang rim snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo bum pa mgrin pa longs spyod chos 'khor /
NK030(a)001:5567: lus mchod rten chen po gcig tu bsgom /
NK030(a)001:5568: de spyi bor srog mi shig pa'i thig le /
NK030(a)001:5569: ham gyi rang bzhin sran ma tsam gcig gnas pa las 'od phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK030(a)001:5571: sems can gyi don byas tshur 'dus gong gi yig ge ham gyi theg le la phog pas /
NK030(a)001:5573: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma ni mchod rten gyi tog gi tshul du bzhugs par bsgom /
NK030(a)001:5574: de la shes pa bcug bas bla ma yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)001:5575: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas rang gi snying gi dkyil du /
NK030(a)001:5576: rang gi shes pa dang 'dres pa la blo skyur la bzhag go /
NK030(a)001:5577: da 'og sgo bde ba sgom pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5578: yang rang gi sbyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgom /
NK030(a)001:5579: de las mda' gang gis mtho bar theg le dkar po sran ma tsam gcig sgom /
NK030(a)001:5580: dmar po de shes rab kyi cha yin la /
NK030(a)001:5581: dkar po thabs kyi cha yin no //
NK030(a)001:5582: de nas thig le dmar po de la shes pa bcug pas /
NK030(a)001:5583: chags pa'i rang bzhin yin pas 'dar bar bsgom /
NK030(a)001:5584: de 'dar bas bdag rkyen byas nas theg le dkar po'ang 'dar ste /
NK030(a)001:5585: mar la de babs nas dmar po la thim pas /
NK030(a)001:5586: dkar dmar dbyer med du 'dres nas /
NK030(a)001:5587: spyi gtsug nas mar thim pas /
NK030(a)001:5588: snying gi dkyil du bde stong dbyer med du blo skyur la bzhag go /
NK030(a)001:5589: de dag ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang gi man ngag sgom 'debs yin no //
NK030(a)001:5590: ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK030(a)001:5591: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:5594: // gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo las /
NK030(a)001:5595: mdo dbang gi khro bo'i mngon rtogs /
NK030(a)001:5596: khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga'o //
NK030(a)001:5597: de nas khro bo'i lha tshogs bskyed pa la /
NK030(a)001:5599: e las chos 'byung gru gsum pa mthing nag /
NK030(a)001:5600: rgya 'khyon nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK030(a)001:5601: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa kha dog duhkha dbyibs rdo rje rgya gram //
NK030(a)001:5602: bam las khrag gi rgya mtsho rba brlabs 'khrugs pa dbyibs zlum po /
NK030(a)001:5603: mam las sha chen gyis gzhi sra zhing 'thas pa dbyibs pa gru bzhi /
NK030(a)001:5604: kam las kem rus kyis ri rab kha khyer dang rgya mnyam pa /
NK030(a)001:5606: khrag gi rol mtsho bdun mtsho chen la /
NK030(a)001:5609: mtha'i lcags ri dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)001:5610: ri rab kyi steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor phyed dmar spros pas rlung gi'oda zer dang 'dres /
NK030(a)001:5611: me rlung tshubs ma yar byung ba las //
NK030(a)001:5612: me ri'i gur khang dmar po /
NK030(a)001:5614: rdo rje'i gur khang mthing nag  /
NK030(a)001:5615: 'og gzhi rdo rje brag gi steng du /
NK030(a)001:5616: sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram /
NK030(a)001:5621: lte ba mthing nag leb mo gru bzhi /
NK030(a)001:5622: zur la bang rim bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5623: de nas gzhal yas khang rnams ni /
NK030(a)001:5624: b+h+r+aum s+pha ra na phatah sam ha ra na h'uh
NK030(a)001:5625: b+h+aum b+hi shwa b+hi shud d+he b+han d+ha dz+ny+aa na
NK030(a)001:5626: / tsakra s+aur+yatsana tra pad+ma e ka man+dala la /
NK030(a)001:5629: ru tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK030(a)001:5631: sangs rgyas zhing khams thams cad khyab /
NK030(a)001:5632: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su dgongs /
NK030(a)001:5633: byang chub sems dpa'i spun du dgongs /
NK030(a)001:5634: ma mo dang mkha' 'gros rje bor dgongs /
NK030(a)001:5635: gzhal yas khang gi che ba'i yon tan thams cad snang ba'i tshul gyis bsdus ste /
NK030(a)001:5636: b+h+r+aum la thim 'od du zhu ste /
NK030(a)001:5637: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)001:5638: gru bzhi la sgo bzhi pa /
NK030(a)001:5639: phyi nang bcu rim du yod pa /
NK030(a)001:5640: de yi dri ra ga'i rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)001:5643: phyi skam po las rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)001:5644: sha chen dang raka ta'i rtsigs 'jim /
NK030(a)001:5645: thod pa'i dpral ba nas rdo rje'i thog 'phro ba /
NK030(a)001:5651: pan tsa ra ga'i rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)001:5657: rmang dang rtse mo phyir ngom pa /
NK030(a)001:5658: de rgyab e rag gi rtsigs pa /
NK030(a)001:5662: byang ral gri ljang khu gzugs brnyan gyis tshul du 'char ba /
NK030(a)001:5663: rtse rtsig phyir ngom pa'i steng du /
NK030(a)001:5664: thod pa'i pha gu ser po bzhi gnyis sna gcig non /
NK030(a)001:5665: de'i nang ngos la 'dod snams dmar po /
NK030(a)001:5667: zhing gi bka' gdung bcu drug dang /
NK030(a)001:5668: rtsib ma'i bkrag rtsi bres pa /
NK030(a)001:5669: ka thung bcu drug gis gam du mchod pa'i lha
NK030(a)001:5670: mo bcu drug gis mchod rdzas du ma thogs pa
NK030(a)001:5671: / ka gdung gi steng du gza' chen brgyad kyi
NK030(a)001:5672: dmar po gru bzhir bres pa'i phyi ngos la thod
NK030(a)001:5673: skam gyi shar bu bsgrigs pa /
NK030(a)001:5674: nang lha rnams kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du /
NK030(a)001:5675: sa bdag sbal pa ser po brgyad kyi ka gdan /
NK030(a)001:5676: de'i steng du lha chen brgyad kyi ka ba /
NK030(a)001:5677: nyi zla'i ka zhu dang bcas pa brgyad btsugs pa /
NK030(a)001:5678: de'i steng du klu chen brgyad kyi gdung ma bzhi zur du bres pa'i steng nas /
NK030(a)001:5679: phyi'i mdzes gdung gi thog du /
NK030(a)001:5680: rgyu skar nyer brgyad kyis bres pa'i kha nas /
NK030(a)001:5681: sbrul nag gi dra ba la dril bu g.yer kha dang /
NK030(a)001:5682: rgyu ma la dril bu tshon 'chang ba /
NK030(a)001:5683: dra khug gi sbrul mgos tsit+ta'i phol phyings 'dzin pa'i steng du nyi zla'i gdan bting ba /
NK030(a)001:5684: gnod sbyin nyer brgyad kyis cham 'thud byas /
NK030(a)001:5685: de'i steng du zhing bran gyi dral grab rtsig gshog gi sa tshags /
NK030(a)001:5688: de'i steng du rdo rje'i mo gyo ring yug tu
NK030(a)001:5689: song pa'i rtse mor pad+ma phyed pa mar 'phyang ba
NK030(a)001:5690: / pho gyo ring yug tu song pa'i rtse mor mchod rten /
NK030(a)001:5697: zur bzhir gnam lcags kyi gzer chen gdab pa /
NK030(a)001:5698: des ni lha rnams nang ma khebs pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5699: de'i steng du ka thung gi kha la /
NK030(a)001:5700: mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa /
NK030(a)001:5701: nang pad khar rtsigs pa gru bzhi'i steng du gdung zlum bres pa /
NK030(a)001:5702: gdung zlum gyi steng nas mdzes gdung gi kha la
NK030(a)001:5703: phyam nyi shu rtsa bzhi bres pa'i kha la dra
NK030(a)001:5705: rdo rje'i gyo ba la sogs kyi gru chad bzhi bakababa pa /
NK030(a)001:5706: de'i steng du phyi ka gdung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa'o /
NK030(a)001:5707: nang bad dkar rtsigs pa zlum po'i kha la gdung ma gru bzhir bres pa /
NK030(a)001:5708: de'i thog du phyam nyu shu bres pa'i kha la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)001:5711: de'i steng du phyi ka thung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhi bris pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5712: nang bad dkar rtsigs pa gru bzhi gting du gdung ma zlum por bres pa /
NK030(a)001:5713: de'i steng phyam bcu drug bres pa'i kha la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)001:5714: rdo rje mthing nag gi gyo mo las gyes rtsibs bzhi bkab pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5715: de'i steng du bum gdan gru bzhi /
NK030(a)001:5717: bre ske dang bre gru bzhi chos 'khor dang gdugs zlum /
NK030(a)001:5718: dar 'phyangs nyi zla rdo rje tog dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5719: de ni 'khyams dang po'i rim pa'o /
NK030(a)001:5721: / 'khyams dgu po kun la phyi rtsigs pa nas /
NK030(a)001:5724: lha rnams kyi nang zur nas ka ba phyogs bzhi
NK030(a)001:5725: mtshams su gtsugs pa'i thog tu gdung gru bzhir bres
NK030(a)001:5726: pa'i steng du phyam nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi kha
NK030(a)001:5727: la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK030(a)001:5728: rdo rje gyo sogs kyis lha rnams bkab pa dang /
NK030(a)001:5729: de nas rim bzhin du bang rim bzhi dang /
NK030(a)001:5730: bum pa bzhi la sogs pa'ang nang dang mthun par gsal ba /
NK030(a)001:5731: mchod rten gyi nang du mchod rten bcu ba rtsig pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:5732: rgyal chen pho mos sgo skyes byas pa /
NK030(a)001:5735: zhing phran la sbrul nag gis sgo srog byas pa'i sgo leb /
NK030(a)001:5737: sgo thog du bcu gcig rdo rje'i dra mig /
NK030(a)001:5738: sgo khang nang gis rgyan dgu dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5739: sgo them gyi phyi rgyab tu /
NK030(a)001:5740: stegs rta babs bang rim bzhi bzhi /
NK030(a)001:5741: sgo khang gi phyi zur bzhi nas ka ba bzhi bzhi'i kha la //
NK030(a)001:5742: glang gur dang bcas pa brgyan rta babs bang rim bzhi bzhi pad+ma dang bcas pa la /
NK030(a)001:5744: de'i steng du yu ba chos 'khor bcu gsum dang bcas pa'i zhing lpags kyi gdugs /
NK030(a)001:5746: nyi zla rdo rje'i tog dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5747: chos 'khor g.yas g.yon du 'brug gi ri dwags gnyis gnyis 'brug sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5748: gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol du /
NK030(a)001:5749: dur khrod chen po brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5750: gzhal yas khang gi nang 'khor lo'i lte ba dang /
NK030(a)001:5752: rin po che'i khri la sogs pa'i gdan drug ba
NK030(a)001:5753: rtsegs gzhan rnams la rang rang gi gdan bsam mo
NK030(a)001:5754: // de nas lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:5755: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5756: ka ta ma ha kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:5758: che mchog sku mdog mthing nag dbu nyer gcig ste /
NK030(a)001:5762: de'i steng dbus ser g.yas gnyis ljang dmar g.yon gnyis mthing dkar /
NK030(a)001:5768: rtse mo dmar po rta dbu ljang kus rta skad bsgrogs pa /
NK030(a)001:5769: phyag zhe gnyis kyi dang po gnyis kun bzang yab yub thugs khar bsnol nas 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:5782: yi dwags dmyal ba'i thub pa nyi shu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5784: dpal chas brgyad gyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)001:5786: me ri me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:5787: byol song bco brgyad kyi khri la //
NK030(a)001:5788: dregs pa pad zla nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)001:5789: yum khro mo rnam zhal ma sku mdog mthing nag
NK030(a)001:5790: dbu dgu'i dbus ma mthing ka'i zhal che mchog gi
NK030(a)001:5791: gsang ba'i rdo rje dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)001:5794: che mchog zhabs g.yas pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)001:5798: dmar gyi zhal bzhi che mchog zhabs g.yon pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK030(a)001:5799: phyag bco brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod pa thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5800: g.yas kyi 'og ma brgyad kyi gnas ma brgyad kyi lha mo brgyad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5801: g.yon gyi 'og ma brgyad kyi yul ma phra men brgyad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5802: gnas ma brgyad dang yul ma brgyad kyis thod pa bcu drug bsnams pa'ang snang ngo //
NK030(a)001:5803: zhabs bzhi nyi ma la sogs pa'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)001:5804: dpal dang dur khrod kyi chas la sogs pa yab dang 'dra ba la /
NK030(a)001:5805: gzig gis sham thabs can gsal bar bskyed do //
NK030(a)001:5806: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5807: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5808: che mchog yab yum gyis mdun du /
NK030(a)001:5809: badz+ra he ru ka mthing nag /
NK030(a)001:5814: phyag dang po gnyis thugs khar rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK030(a)001:5815: g.yas 'og ma gnyis kha tam dang rnge'u chung /
NK030(a)001:5816: g.yon 'og ma gnyis thod khrag dang rnga yab /
NK030(a)001:5817: yum sngo skya g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK030(a)001:5818: g.yon thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)001:5819: dom gyi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)001:5820: me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5821: bud+d+ha sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5822: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5823: shar rtsibs la bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum smug nag g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK030(a)001:5824: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu thugs khar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)001:5825: g.yas 'og ma gnyis pad+ma dang rtse gsum //
NK030(a)001:5826: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ban dmar sdig mdzub /
NK030(a)001:5827: khyu mchog gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:5828: rat+na sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5829: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5831: rat+na he ru ka ser nag /
NK030(a)001:5833: phyag dang po gnyis rin chen dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5834: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang ral gri /
NK030(a)001:5835: g.yon 'og ma gnyis b+han dmar dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:5836: dregs pa ma he'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:5837: pad+ma sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5838: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK030(a)001:5840: pad+ma he ru ka dmar nag /
NK030(a)001:5842: phyag dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5843: g.yas 'og ma gnyis dgra s+t+wa dang rtse gsum //
NK030(a)001:5844: g.yon 'og ma gnyis thod khrag dang ral gri /
NK030(a)001:5845: stag gi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)001:5846: karma sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:5847: kar+m+aa kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK030(a)001:5849: karma he ru ka ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:5851: dang po gnyis rgya gram dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5852: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang gshol /
NK030(a)001:5853: g.yon 'og ma gnyis b+han dmar dang ti ra bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5854: dregs pa khyo shugs gzig gi gdan la bzhugs pa //
NK030(a)001:5855: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK030(a)001:5857: g.yon pa thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)001:5858: yab yum kun dpal chas dang /
NK030(a)001:5859: dur khrod brgyad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5860: ma h+aa raka sha he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK030(a)001:5861: sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK030(a)001:5862: tsa h+aum phata / ma h+aa rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:5864: raka sha he ru ka mthing nag /
NK030(a)001:5865: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa zhal dang po gsum dbus mthing /
NK030(a)001:5867: de'i steng ma gsum dbus smug /
NK030(a)001:5871: dbus mthing g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK030(a)001:5872: phyag bac+wa brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dung dmar bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5873: g.yas 'og ma brgyad na dgra s+t+wa /
NK030(a)001:5874: g.yon 'og ma brgyad na mdung rtse gsum /
NK030(a)001:5875: yum raka sha he ru ka dung khrag stobs pa dang 'khril ba /
NK030(a)001:5876: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)001:5877: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK030(a)001:5878: sarba dush+ta na ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK030(a)001:5879: tsa h+aum phata / ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:5881: yak+sha he ru ka mthing nag yab yum zhal dbus ma mthing /
NK030(a)001:5884: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5885: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang rnga chung /
NK030(a)001:5886: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ral gri dang sta re /
NK030(a)001:5887: yum gzig sham dregs pa bsnol pa'i gdan la //
NK030(a)001:5888: ma h+aa sa nu sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK030(a)001:5889: tsan d+ha sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha da ha
NK030(a)001:5891: ma h+aa sa nu kro ti shwa ri dza la h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:5893: sa nu he ru ka dmar nag g.yas dkar g.yon sngo /
NK030(a)001:5894: dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:5895: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rtse gsum dang rnga chung /
NK030(a)001:5896: g.yon 'og ma gnyis ban dmar dang kha tam kha /
NK030(a)001:5897: g+hu ya sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:5898: g+hu ya kro ti shwa re s+t+wam /
NK030(a)001:5900: g+hu ya he ru ka ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:5903: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang ban dmar bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:5904: bar ma gnyis gtun shing dang rtse gsum /
NK030(a)001:5905: tha ma gnyis glang chen lpags pa gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:5906: dregs pa'i gdan la yum sngar bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:5908: shar gyi glo 'bur la ko r+ai ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:5911: zhing lpags kyi na bza' stod du g.yog pa /
NK030(a)001:5916: zhabs ga dub la sogs pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:5920: tso ri ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK030(a)001:5922: nub kyi glo 'bur la pra mo dmar mo /
NK030(a)001:5923: g.yas chu srin gyis rgyan mtshan /
NK030(a)001:5927: be t+aa l+ai nag mo g.yas rdo rje /
NK030(a)001:5928: g.yon zhing zhal du gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:5932: phyag g.yon pas zhing bsnams nas /
NK030(a)001:5933: g.yas pas de'i rgyu ma zhags pas 'dren pa /
NK030(a)001:5934: badz+ra g+ha sa ma r+ai h+aa /
NK030(a)001:5935: lho nub kyi gru chad la /
NK030(a)001:5936: g+hasma ri ljang khu g.yon pas thod khrag g.yas pa rdo rjes dkrug cing gsol pa /
NK030(a)001:5938: nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK030(a)001:5940: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung la /
NK030(a)001:5943: byang shar du gtum mo ser mo /
NK030(a)001:5944: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas mgo lus bral ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5945: badz+ra sing ha mu kh+ai hi /
NK030(a)001:5946: 'khyams dang po'i lha snams dang po shar du /
NK030(a)001:5947: sir ha mu kh+ai ser mo /
NK030(a)001:5948: mgo seng ge dkar mo'i kha nas ro za ba /
NK030(a)001:5949: phyag gnyis kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)001:5950: badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)001:5951: lhor bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai dmar mo stag mgo ser mo /
NK030(a)001:5952: phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK030(a)001:5953: badz+ra sring+ga la mu khi hi /
NK030(a)001:5954: nub tu sring+ga la mu khe nag mo wa ser po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:5955: phyag gnyis kyi zhing gi lpags pa bsnams nas de'i chu ser ldag pa /
NK030(a)001:5956: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)001:5957: byang du sho na mu khi 'thing nag spyang ka'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:5958: phyag gnyis zhing bzung nas de'i glo snying za ba'o //
NK030(a)001:5960: shar lhor g+r+aing d+ha mu kh+ai dmar mo bya rgod dkar po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:5963: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai he /
NK030(a)001:5964: lho nub tu kam ka mu ki sku mdog dmar mo /
NK030(a)001:5965: phyag gnyis kyis zhing phrag pa la khur ba /
NK030(a)001:5966: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai ha //
NK030(a)001:5967: nub byang du kha kha mu kh+ai nag mo /
NK030(a)001:5970: badz+ra u lu mu kh+ai he //
NK030(a)001:5971: byang shar du hu lu mu khi mthing kha 'ug pa ser po'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:5972: g.yas lcags kyu g.yon thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:5973: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK030(a)001:5974: shar sgor rta gdong lcags kyu ma dkar mo rta'i gdong can /
NK030(a)001:5978: lho sgor phag gdong zhags pa ma ser mo /
NK030(a)001:5981: nub sgor sprel gdong dmar mo lcags sgrogs bsnams pa'i
NK030(a)001:5982: mdo mig smin mtshams su yod pa'i nang ma nyi
NK030(a)001:5983: zla ga'u nang du rnal 'byor ba'i tshe 'dzin pa
NK030(a)001:5984: / badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya b+ha to ho /
NK030(a)001:5985: byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang khu //
NK030(a)001:5986: g.yas dril bu g.yon thod khrag bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:5987: brgyan cha lugs gong dang mthun pa'o /
NK030(a)001:5989: badz+ra a pra ti ha a r+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:5992: mi zad sna tshogs mdog g.yas nyi zer g.yon zhags pa /
NK030(a)001:5994: lhor gtum mo ser mo mdung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:5996: nub rdo rje mtshon me ma dmar mo g.yas dril bu g.yon thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:5998: byang du thog med ma sngo nag /
NK030(a)001:6001: shar lhor me khyer ma dmar nag /
NK030(a)001:6004: lho nub gshin rje ma sngo nag ral gri dang dgra sta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6007: gnod sbyin mo mthing nag khyung thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6009: byang shar du 'jigs rten ma smug nag /
NK030(a)001:6011: sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6012: shar sgor mig gcig ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:6013: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6014: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga ma shwa ra y+aa ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6015: lho sgor tshe 'phel ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa //
NK030(a)001:6016: sh+ri kha tam kha pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6017: nub sgor dmar mo dbang sdud ma /
NK030(a)001:6018: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6019: sh+ri badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6020: byang sgor ljang nag ral gcig ma /
NK030(a)001:6021: gsung rab dril bu khrol ba /
NK030(a)001:6023: shar stod nas rim pa ltar ma drug bskyed /
NK030(a)001:6024: ma nu raka sha si b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6025: dbang phyug chen mo mi srin mo /
NK030(a)001:6026: sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang thod rlon bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6028: mi srin ma dmar ser g.yag gi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6029: zhing chen dang tri shul bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6031: tshangs ma sku mdog dmar ser /
NK030(a)001:6034: tshangs ma dmar skya sbrul mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6035: rtse lnga dang ban dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6037: 'khrug mo sku mdog dkar mo rdo rje dang tri shul bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6038: de nyid gnas gyur pa khro mo dmar ser gzig mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6041: dbang mo ma sku mdog dkar mo in tra gdeng ba dang /
NK030(a)001:6043: de nyid gnas gyur pa in tra dkar dmar sre mong mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6047: rtog 'dod ma sngon mo rdo rje dang 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6049: khyab 'jug ser mo pha wang gi mgo can 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6051: gzhon nu ma dmar mo rdo rje dang mdung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6052: de nyid gnas gyur pa dbang mo dmar skya /
NK030(a)001:6053: dred kyi mgo can bam dbyug bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6059: zhi ba dmar mo sku mdog dmar mo dom gyi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6062: bdud rtsi ma sku mdog dmar mo rdo rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6064: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin gyi gdong pa can /
NK030(a)001:6065: rin po che'i bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6067: zhi ba ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)001:6068: rdo rje dang pun+d+ha ri ka bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6070: zhi ba mo sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6071: bam ril khog smad bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6073: be con ma sku mdog sngon mo rdo rje dang dbyug to 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)001:6075: be con nag mo khra'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6076: bam chen gyi thod rlon bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6078: srin mo sku mdog dmar ser rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:6080: srin mo dmar nag wa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6083: za ba mo sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang ba su 'dren pa /
NK030(a)001:6085: za byed nag mo stag gi mgo can dang /
NK030(a)001:6089: dga' ba mo sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)001:6090: rdo rje dang ga dar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6092: dga' byed dmar mo bya rgod kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6094: badz+ra ru ti ri ma ti b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6095: khrag 'thung myos ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK030(a)001:6096: rdo rje dang gshol bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6098: khrag 'thung dmar nag rta'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6099: rdo rjer dbyug dang dung dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6100: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6101: rdo rje ser mo rdo rje dang spu gri /
NK030(a)001:6103: gcig pu dkar dmar lding gi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6104: rdo rje dang ban d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6105: am ma nu ha ram b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6106: yid 'phrog ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK030(a)001:6109: yid 'phrog dmar ser khyi'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6112: grub mo sku mdog dkar mo rdo rje dang bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6114: gru mo dkar dmar pu shud kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6115: pad+ma dang byi snying za ba /
NK030(a)001:6117: rlung mo sku mdog sngo nag /
NK030(a)001:6118: rdo rje dang ba dan 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)001:6120: rlung mo dmar skya sha ba'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6123: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra na b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6124: khyo med ma sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang ral gri /
NK030(a)001:6126: gsod byed ljang nag sbyang khu'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6127: bam chen dang rnga chung 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6129: me lha mo sku mdog dmar mo rdo rje dang gsal shing 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6131: me long ljang dmar skyiin gyi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6132: sreg rgyu 'dren pa badz+ra b+aa ra hi b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6133: sna chen ma sku mdog dmar nag /
NK030(a)001:6134: rdo rje dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:6136: sna chen ljang dmar glang gi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6137: bam chen la longs sbyod pa /
NK030(a)001:6139: chu lha mo sku mdog dkar mo sngo sbrul zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6140: de nyin gnas gyur pa las /
NK030(a)001:6141: klu mo ljang nag sbrul mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6142: bdud rtsi dung dmar gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:6144: gnyis shar sgor nag mo sku mdog nag po /
NK030(a)001:6145: rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6146: de nyid gnas gyur pa nag mo khu byug gi mgo can dang /
NK030(a)001:6148: badz+ra ma h+aa ka la ye b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6149: lho sgor ra mgo ma sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6150: de nyid kyi sprul pa ra gdong ma /
NK030(a)001:6151: sngon mo ra mgo can zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6152: badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6153: nub tu bum sna ma sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6154: de'i sprul pa be con ma dmar mo /
NK030(a)001:6158: byang sgor pus 'dzin ma sku mdog ljang nag rdo rje dang dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK030(a)001:6159: de'i sprul pa gsus 'dzin ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)001:6161: dril chen dang dung dmar bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6162: de ltar dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po kun /
NK030(a)001:6165: dar dang rin chen brgyan kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)001:6167: zhing skam tshal pa'i gdan dang bcas pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6168: de nas 'khyams sgo bzhi pa'i mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu rtsa gnyis la /
NK030(a)001:6176: mkha' 'gro dga' byed dkar mo rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6177: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6180: badz+ra ma h+aa he la ba ti h'u /
NK030(a)001:6181: bsod byed ma dkar mo mda' gzhu 'gengs ba /
NK030(a)001:6182: ku ma ra pra ye h'u /
NK030(a)001:6183: spor byed dkar skya spu gri bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6184: ma h+aa badz+ra ma ti h'u /
NK030(a)001:6185: 'bar byed ma mthing nag rin chen bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6186: badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya h'u /
NK030(a)001:6190: khro gnyer ma mthing nag 'phyar dar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6191: ma h+aa badz+ra kro d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6192: 'joms byed ma mthing kha mchu 'grams zhing kha gdangs bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6193: ma h+aa a smri tot+pa ti h'u /
NK030(a)001:6195: pad+ma dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6200: 'khor lo ma dmar ser 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6201: ma h+aa ra ma ni h'u /
NK030(a)001:6203: lce dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6204: ma h+aa a smri ti ka pa la hasti ta ki h'u /
NK030(a)001:6205: sna tshogs lus 'chang ma ljang khu rgya gram dang s+t+wa re bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6207: bsrung ba mo ljang khu go khrab /
NK030(a)001:6208: badz+ra smri ta su ta dan+da ri h'u /
NK030(a)001:6210: mche ba dang sgrom bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6212: yang dag 'phrog byed ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)001:6213: rdo rje khu tshur bsnams pa b+hi b+ha ri ram h'u /
NK030(a)001:6214: bya rog gdong ma nag mo /
NK030(a)001:6215: dri dang mkhar gzhong bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6217: 'jig byed ma dkar sngo mche ba gtsigs ma dkar mo /
NK030(a)001:6218: rin chen dang dung dmar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6219: badz+ra sha ni ta ka h'u //
NK030(a)001:6220: thams cad sgrol byed dkar sngo gzhad kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6223: las byed ma dkar sngo 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6226: dur khrod 'joms ma khyi'i mgo can mthing nag kem rus 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6228: rtog bral ma mthing nag phag mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6231: 'dod 'joms ma sngo nag rnga mo'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6233: ta ki bi ka te thon dbyug ma sngo mo /
NK030(a)001:6234: bong bu'i mgo can dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6235: badz+ra ti ra shi ta h'u /
NK030(a)001:6237: / 'joms ma dmar mo ra'i mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6240: k+aa li pra be sha h'u /
NK030(a)001:6241: sgrol byed ma dmar nag byi la'i mgo can //
NK030(a)001:6244: zhe sdang 'jom byed ma dmar ljang //
NK030(a)001:6246: kem rus dang mi mgo 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)001:6248: kun rdzogs ma dmar ser lce spyang gi mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6251: srin mo bum sna dmar ser seng ge mgo can /
NK030(a)001:6252: rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6257: d+ha sha g+h+ri wa ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6259: lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6260: badz+ra s+aa b+han a ki h'u /
NK030(a)001:6262: dril bu dang dgra sta bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6263: thams cad thod pa skams rlon zhing lpags gzig la sogs khro bo'i rgyan chas du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6264: sgo 'khyams lnga pa'i phyogs bzhir ma bdun /
NK030(a)001:6265: sgo bzhir sring mo bzhi ste /
NK030(a)001:6266: ma ma d+ha du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6267: rdo rje kun drag ma dmar sngo ri rab thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6268: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6269: kun tu bzang mo dmar ma nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6270: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6271: rdo rje kun grags ma sngon mo //
NK030(a)001:6273: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6274: rdo rje ye shes ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:6276: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)001:6277: rdo rje 'od chags ma sngon mo //
NK030(a)001:6278: rdo rje dra ba'i phreng ba thogs pa //
NK030(a)001:6279: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6280: rdo rje 'od 'phro ma sngon mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6281: ma ma da du kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6282: rdo rje g.yu sgron ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:6283: ral gri dang thod khrag bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6286: gling bzhi 'gyogs ma lha'i sring mo dkar mo /
NK030(a)001:6287: bya rgod kyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6288: rgod thul gsol ba badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:6289: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring mo ser mo stag gi rgyal mtshan dang /
NK030(a)001:6292: dmar mo g.yag thod klu'i sring mo //
NK030(a)001:6293: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)001:6294: chu srin gyis thul ba gsol ba //
NK030(a)001:6296: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin gyi sring mo /
NK030(a)001:6298: rma bya'i thul pa gsol ba'o //
NK030(a)001:6299: sgo 'khyams drug pa ging chen bac+wa brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:6300: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6301: dpal chen las kun byed mthing nag ral gri dang /
NK030(a)001:6302: b+han d+ha thogs pa badz+ra ka tar+shi shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6303: khro mo khams gsum dbang bsdud ma sngo nag /
NK030(a)001:6304: thod khrag dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6305: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6306: rdo rje ka tar ging ka ra dmar nag b+han d+ha dang ga tar 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6307: badz+ra ka ti ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6308: rdo rje ging chen gnod sbyin ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6310: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6311: rdo rje ging chen spyang ki dmar nag spyang gdong can /
NK030(a)001:6313: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6314: rdo rje ging chen ya ma mthing nag be con dang dgra sta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6315: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6316: rdo rje ging chen rol pa dmar nag /
NK030(a)001:6317: b+han d+ha dang phal tshab bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6318: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6319: rdo rje ging chen 'chi bdag ljang ser /
NK030(a)001:6321: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6322: rdo rje ging chen dus mtshams ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6323: shag ti b+han d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6324: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6325: rdo rje ging chen ro langs ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa //
NK030(a)001:6326: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6327: rdo rje ging chen 'joms pa smug nag /
NK030(a)001:6328: rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6329: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6330: rdo rje ging lcags dbang bsgyur ma /
NK030(a)001:6331: lcang nag rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6332: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h'u /
NK030(a)001:6333: rdo rje ging lcam dbang bsgyur ljang nag lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6334: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6335: rdo rje ging lcam 'phrul mo dmar mo zhing lag na thod pa bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6336: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6337: rdo rje ging lcam glog 'gyu ma /
NK030(a)001:6338: rdo rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6339: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6340: rdo rje ging chen mthu mo che /
NK030(a)001:6341: ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6342: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6343: rdo rje ging lcam rtsam mo che //
NK030(a)001:6344: mthing nag rdo rje dang dgra sta thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6347: rdo rje ging lcam bsgrol byed ma /
NK030(a)001:6348: smug nag b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6351: rdo rje ging lcam za byed ma /
NK030(a)001:6352: ljang nags lcags kyu dang ban d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6353: de thams cad stag sham dang gzig sham la sogs khro bo dang /
NK030(a)001:6354: khro mo'i rgyan du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6355: sgo 'khyams bdun pa steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu ste /
NK030(a)001:6356: shar du khro bo yab yum drug /
NK030(a)001:6361: steng 'og gnyis na gnyis ste drug cu gsal bar bskyed de /
NK030(a)001:6362: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6363: rnam par rgyal ba dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum phyag g.yas rdo rje /
NK030(a)001:6365: yum snye ma dkar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK030(a)001:6366: g.yon pas thod khrag yab la stobs pa /
NK030(a)001:6367: gnyis ka dri za'i gdan la bzhengs pa'o //
NK030(a)001:6368: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6369: khro bo dbyug sngon can sngon po'i rin chen dang sdig mdzub /
NK030(a)001:6370: yum rdo rje sder mo me lha'i gdan la bzhengs pa //
NK030(a)001:6371: kro ta kro ri shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6372: khro bo gshin rje gshed mthing nag /
NK030(a)001:6374: yum dur khrod bdag mo thod pa //
NK030(a)001:6375: gshin rje'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK030(a)001:6376: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6377: mi g.yo ba ser dmar ral gri dang //
NK030(a)001:6379: rdo rje gtun khung ma thod pa srin po'i gdan la /
NK030(a)001:6380: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)001:6381: rta mgrin dmar po mda' gzhu dang pad+ma /
NK030(a)001:6383: klu'i gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6384: khro bo gzhan gyi mi thub pa sngo ljang khu //
NK030(a)001:6385: dgra sta dang gtun shing bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6386: yum mda' snyems ma thod pa //
NK030(a)001:6388: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6389: bdun rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6391: gnod sbyin gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6392: khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba nag po rdo rje dang tho ba /
NK030(a)001:6394: dbang ldan gyis gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6395: khro bo stobs po che dud kha rnga yab thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6397: sa gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6398: khro bo h+aum mdzad dmar skya mda' gzhu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6400: nyi zla gza' skar rnams gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6401: badz+ra ki la mthing nag phur pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6403: dgra dang lha gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6404: rme rtsegs mthing nag rdo rje bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6406: bdud dang ru tra'i gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6409: yag mo dung dmar rmu gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6410: khro chen dmar nag rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6411: khro mo dbang bsgyur ma dung dmar /
NK030(a)001:6412: mo gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6413: khro bo za 'og ljang khu sbrul bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6414: khro mo za 'og mo thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:6415: smu gdon gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)001:6416: khro bo rab 'khrug sngon po ral gri bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6417: khro mo rab 'jigs ma thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:6418: gdon chen bac+wa brgyad kyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6419: ma h+aa ka la dmar nag zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6420: khro mo ral sgreng ma thod khrag /
NK030(a)001:6421: ya bdud kyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum //
NK030(a)001:6424: khro mo 'joms byed ma dung dmar sri can gyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6425: gu langs smug nag gtun shing stobs pa /
NK030(a)001:6426: khro mo las kun ma ban dmar /
NK030(a)001:6427: khams gsum bsad pa dang gso bar mdzad pa /
NK030(a)001:6428: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6429: rab rngam ljang nag rdo rje dang dung gtum chen ma /
NK030(a)001:6430: thod khrag dang tsit+ta stobs pa za byed kyi gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6431: 'jig rten gsum snang sngo nag be con dang sdig 'dzub /

NK030(a)001:6433: 'jig rten gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba 'phyar ba khro mo lcags kyu ma lcags kyu /

NK030(a)001:6435: 'jig rten dmar nag ral gri dang sdig mdzub /
NK030(a)001:6437: lho gdon gyi kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:6438: 'jig rten gsum 'khyil sngo nag dbyug tho 'phyar ba /

NK030(a)001:6454: rngam chen smug nag be con dang sdig 'dzub can /
NK030(a)001:6455: khro mo dbang sdud ma thod khrag /

NK030(a)001:6457: rdo rje tho ba dud ka tho ba bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6458: khro mo za byed dung khrag /
NK030(a)001:6459: ma mo gshin rje'i gdan la kro ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /

NK030(a)001:6860: gardza pho nya myur byed dmar smug glog gi zhags pa can /
NK030(a)001:6861: gardza pho nya rings byed ma bud med lus la mchu mo che //
NK030(a)001:6862: ri lung med par rjes kyi 'gengs pa /
NK030(a)001:6863: gardza pho nya srog byed ma dmar smug lag na gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6864: gardza pho nya glog byed ma dmar smug rdo rje dang be con bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6865: gardza pho nya tho ba ma dmar smug rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6866: gardza pho nya gtun khung ma dmar smug lag na gtun khung thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6867: gardza pho nya zhags 'phen ma dmar smug bdud kyi zhags pas gang la dmigs 'dzin par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:6868: gardza pho nya me khyer ma dmar smug dur khrod kyi mes phyi nang bsreg par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:6869: gardza pho nya sdud byed ma dmar smug gser gyi phreng ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6870: gardza pho nya g.yengs byed ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)001:6872: gardza pho nya bdud 'joms ma dmar skya gtun dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6873: gardza pho nya dpal mo srid pa'i dpal 'phrog par
NK030(a)001:6874: byed pa dmar skya lcags kyu gser g.yu spel ma'i
NK030(a)001:6876: gardza pho nya dbang phyug ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)001:6877: rdo rje rtse gsum dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:6878: gardza pho nya grags pa mo dmar skya //
NK030(a)001:6880: gardza pho nya gtum bag can dmar smug /
NK030(a)001:6881: dgra bo'i snying 'byin cing cho nge 'debs pa /
NK030(a)001:6882: gardza pho nya ka la yangs pa dmar skya ka li'i mtshon thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6883: gardza pho nya bde tshogs ma dmar skya //
NK030(a)001:6884: pad khrag khrag gis char 'babs pas /
NK030(a)001:6885: ma mo 'bum sde bran du 'khol ba /
NK030(a)001:6886: gardza pho nya ha la'i gdong /
NK030(a)001:6887: dmar skya bdud rtsi thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6888: gardza pho nya rab brjid ma dmar skya /
NK030(a)001:6889: mi mgo rnam gsum gyis 'phreng ba sbreng zhing glad
NK030(a)001:6890: la bskor bas dgra bgegs la rgyal bar mdzad pa'o
NK030(a)001:6891: // dgra dang gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)001:6893: / 'jigs byed pho nya sku sprul pa /
NK030(a)001:6894: byang phyogs 'od zer sngon po las //
NK030(a)001:6895: g.yu'i mi mo drug bcur sprul /
NK030(a)001:6896: pa tsa pa tsa g+ha n+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)001:6897: he sha d+ha ra sa ma y+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:6898: las kyi pho nya mo ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6899: rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6900: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)001:6901: e sha d+ha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:6902: 'phrin las kyi pho nya 'joms ma chen mo /
NK030(a)001:6903: ljang sngon khyung gi khra thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6904: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)001:6906: 'phrin las kha lo bsgyur bar mdzad ma ljang sngon dred kyi g.yang gzhi rdeb pa /
NK030(a)001:6907: pa tsa pa tsa pho nya dbang phyug ma ljang sngon thod rlon khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:6909: pa tsa pa tsa pho nya 'gug byed ma ljang sngo mi mag dung du 'bud pa /
NK030(a)001:6910: pa tsa pho nya bskul byed ma ljang sngon /
NK030(a)001:6912: pa tsa pho nya grub pa mo ljang sngon g.yu'i 'khor lo 'chang ba /
NK030(a)001:6913: pa tsa pho nya mthar phyir ma ljang khu g.yu'i thor tsug can /
NK030(a)001:6915: pa tsa pho nya mthar byed ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)001:6916: rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6917: pa tsa pho nya chud mi za ba ljang sngon dung gi mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6918: pa tsa pho nya dbang bsgyur ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)001:6919: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6920: pa tsa pho nya thogs med ma /
NK030(a)001:6921: 'dab chags bya'i rgyal po la zhon pa ljang khu /
NK030(a)001:6922: 'jigs su rung ba'i mtshon cha 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)001:6923: pa tsa pho nya grub pa ma ljang dmar shel gyi za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:6924: pa tsa pho nya gsal byed ma ljang dmar me'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK030(a)001:6925: pa tsa pho nya dbang mo che ljang dmar rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:6926: pa tsa pho nya dam tshig ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)001:6928: pa tsa pho nya bya ra ma lcags kyi spyang khu g.yu'i mig can /
NK030(a)001:6931: pa tsa pho nya stangs 'dzin ma ljang dmar /
NK030(a)001:6932: rtsibs kyi byang bu thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6933: pa tsa pho nya stangs gcod ljang dmar brtsis kyi khram thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6934: pa tsa las kyi pho nya gsal 'dzin ma dmar ljang /
NK030(a)001:6936: pa tsa pho nya bskul byed ma ljang ser /
NK030(a)001:6938: pa tsa pho nya dbang mo ljang ser khrag gi phor ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6939: pa tsa pho nya phag mo ljang ser /
NK030(a)001:6941: pa tsa pho nya spyan brgya mo mgo lus med par mig gis gang ba /
NK030(a)001:6942: pa tsa pho nya mig stong ma dbu stong /
NK030(a)001:6946: 'ja' tshon gyi lus la 'od kyi mig /
NK030(a)001:6947: bltas pas mi mthong ba gang yang med pa /
NK030(a)001:6948: pa tsa pho nya rlung zhon ma ljang khu la ga na lcags kyi dgra s+t+wa thogs pa //
NK030(a)001:6949: rlung nag 'tshub ma la zhon pa /
NK030(a)001:6950: pa tsa pho nya rdzu 'phrul can ljang ser /
NK030(a)001:6951: sbrul nag stong gi zhags pa 'phen pa //
NK030(a)001:6952: ltas ngan rnga mong gwa pa la zhon pa /
NK030(a)001:6953: pa tsa pho nya rgyu ba mo cir yang ma
NK030(a)001:6954: nges gzugs su ston pa re 'ga' chu srin sbrul
NK030(a)001:6955: gyis yu ba spu gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6956: pa tsa pho nya dbang phyug rgyal ljang ser //
NK030(a)001:6958: pa tsa pho nya drag rgyal mo ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6959: dred kyi mgo can stag la zhon pa gri thod /
NK030(a)001:6960: pa tsa pho nya dpal bsham ma ljang nag dmar gyi gtor ma glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)001:6961: khrag gi gtor ma'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK030(a)001:6962: pa tsa pho nya yaka sha mo ljang nag gnod sbyin gyi mgo thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6963: pa tsa pho nya khro bag can /
NK030(a)001:6964: bud med kyi lus la skyes pa'i mgo /
NK030(a)001:6967: pa tsa pho nya mche ba can /
NK030(a)001:6968: lag gnyis rdo rje mche ba 'debs pa /
NK030(a)001:6969: pa tsa las kyi pho nya dbang skur ma /
NK030(a)001:6970: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya can /
NK030(a)001:6971: pa tsa pho nya dngos grub bdag mo ljang nag 'dod yon lnga la rol ba /
NK030(a)001:6972: pa tsa pho nya sgrol byed ma chen po ljang nag gcod pa'i phal tshab thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6973: pa tsa pho nya mnga' bdag mo ljang nag rnga chung brdungs ba /
NK030(a)001:6974: pa tsa pho nya 'od 'phro ma ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:6976: pa tsa pho nya drag mo ljang nag gru gsum mthing nag thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6977: pa tsa pho nya khros skyes ma ljang smug glo nag sa la brdeb pa /
NK030(a)001:6978: pa tsa pho nya myur 'grub ma ljang dpal sngon po lag na ral gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6979: pa tsa pho nya chud ma zos ma //
NK030(a)001:6980: ljang smug rin chen me sgron thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6981: pa tsa pho nya 'dul byed ma ljang smug /
NK030(a)001:6982: srin po'i thod pa thod pa /
NK030(a)001:6984: sna tshogs lus 'chang rgya mtsho skyom pa /
NK030(a)001:6985: pa tsa pho nya ltung 'dzin ma /
NK030(a)001:6987: pa tsa pho nya sgrol byed ma dmar smug /
NK030(a)001:6989: pa tsa pho nya kun gnyen ma ljang smug g.yu'i zhags pa 'debs pa /
NK030(a)001:6990: pa tsa pho nya 'dul mkhan mo /
NK030(a)001:6991: skyes bu na chung gi gzugs 'chang ba /
NK030(a)001:6992: pa tsa pho nya goms pa mo ljang khu dug gi mda' 'phen pa /
NK030(a)001:6993: snying dkar nag gi mtshams su brdeg pa /
NK030(a)001:6994: pa tsa pho nya las mkhan ma ljang skya mche ba'i zor 'phen pa /
NK030(a)001:6995: pa tsa pho nya dbang sgyur ma nyi zla gza' skar gyis slog pa gyon pa /
NK030(a)001:6996: gling bzhi lag na thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:6997: pa tsa pho nya mchog sgrol ma ljang skya mchog gi tsit+ta 'byin pa /
NK030(a)001:6998: pa tsa pho nya rgyug 'dzin ma ljang khu /
NK030(a)001:6999: shel dang long thang gi spu bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7000: pa tsa pho nya rngams pa mo ljang skya sha khrag rlon pa za ba /
NK030(a)001:7001: pa tsa pho nya so skyes ma ljang skya 'debs pa'i las la myur ba /
NK030(a)001:7002: pa tsa pho nya gtum mo ljang skya /
NK030(a)001:7003: nyi ma dang zla ba'i 'khor lo 'phen pa /
NK030(a)001:7004: pa tsa pho nya mig dmar ma ljang skya //
NK030(a)001:7005: khrag chang gi myos par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7006: mig rtsa dmar ba ra'i gdong pa can /
NK030(a)001:7007: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK030(a)001:7008: e sha ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:7009: 'phrin las pho nya sen mo can dmar smug sen
NK030(a)001:7010: mo lcags kyus bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dzin par byed
NK030(a)001:7012: 'og gi ma mo drug bcu bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:7013: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyi //
NK030(a)001:7014: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:7016: ma mo las byed drug bcur sbrul /
NK030(a)001:7020: tri shul dang nad rkyal thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7022: ma mo spal mo thal mdog /
NK030(a)001:7024: dur khrod rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)001:7026: dur khrod tshogs kyi ral can ma /
NK030(a)001:7031: khrag ral gos su gon pa /
NK030(a)001:7032: phyag gi skye 'gro'i tsit+ta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7033: ma ma khams gsum sdud pa'i mtshan ma dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:7035: ma ma rgyu drug sgrol ba'i ma chen mo /
NK030(a)001:7038: mi snying dang rus 'phreng glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)001:7039: ma ma srid gsum za byed ma /
NK030(a)001:7041: gnam sa gnyis kyi gos gon pa /
NK030(a)001:7042: ma ma snang srid yongs la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK030(a)001:7043: ser nag nyi zla'i thod bcings pa /
NK030(a)001:7044: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ma /
NK030(a)001:7045: ma ma mthu rtsal snyems ma ljang nag zhing gi go zu gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7046: lag pa g.yas kyis nam mkha' 'degs pa /
NK030(a)001:7047: ma ma sha khrag gsur la dga' ba ma /
NK030(a)001:7048: mi sha rta sha zas su za ba /
NK030(a)001:7049: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:7050: ma ma sgrol byed ma chen mo /
NK030(a)001:7051: mthing nag nang 'khrol blo snying 'byin pa /
NK030(a)001:7052: ma ma za byed chen mo sngo nag g.yu'i za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7053: ma ma rngam byed ma ser nag 'brug sngon 'chibs su bcibs pa /
NK030(a)001:7054: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin pa /
NK030(a)001:7055: ma ma 'dzin byed chen mo ser nag thod khrag dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7056: ma ma bgegs chen 'joms ma sngo nag spu gri dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7057: ma ma zhing bcu sgrol byed ma ljang nag b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7058: ma ma chad pa gcod pa'i mi mo sngon nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi brdeb pa dang /
NK030(a)001:7060: ma ma 'byung po sgrol byed ma /
NK030(a)001:7061: b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7062: ma ma gshin rje sgrol byed ma b+han+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7063: ma ma klu sgrol byed ma //
NK030(a)001:7064: b+han d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7065: ma ma gnod sbyin sgrol byed ma ljang nag b+han+da dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7066: ma ma srin mo bsgrol byed ma chen mo sngo nag b+han+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7067: ma ma srin mo bsgrol byed chen mo smug nag /
NK030(a)001:7069: ma ma gzugs la dbang ba'i dbang mo /
NK030(a)001:7070: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7071: ma ma khrag ma dbang ba'i dbang mo sngon mo thod khrag dkrugs cing 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:7072: ma ma drod la dbang ba'i dbang mo /
NK030(a)001:7073: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7074: ma ma dbugs la dbang mo ljang nag thod khrag dang zhags pa thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7075: ma ma bkrag mdangs la dbang ba'i dbang mo ser nag ral gri dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:7076: ma ma srog la dbang ma smug nag gri dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7078: khrag 'thung ma bya rgod mgo ser ljang ral gri dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)001:7079: ma ma ma mo za byed stag gi mgo can dmar ser thod khrag gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7080: ma ma ma mo 'jigs byed ma /
NK030(a)001:7081: chu srin gyi mgo can khrag gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7082: ma ma ma mo dur khrod rgyan byed ma //
NK030(a)001:7083: mi lpags rlon pa'i na bza' gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7085: ma ma gar gyi dbang mo /
NK030(a)001:7086: dbu rgyan spyan stong dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:7087: ma ma pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma /
NK030(a)001:7088: lag na mi mgo'i phor ba'i nang du /
NK030(a)001:7089: mi snying tshil bus bkang nas gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7090: ma ma sa bdag pad+ma phreng ba dmar nag phyag na b+han d+ha khrag gi bkang gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7091: ma ma srid gsum bdag mo /
NK030(a)001:7092: g.yas ri rab rtse gsum nas brnyil bar byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7093: g.yon rgya mtsho'i gting nas rnyog par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7094: ma ma rgya mtsho'i gting gi mthu mo che //
NK030(a)001:7095: chu srin lpags pa'i na bza' gsol //
NK030(a)001:7096: sbrul nag 'bum gyi gdengs ka can //
NK030(a)001:7097: ma ma ma mo rdo rje tho ba mo /
NK030(a)001:7098: sngo nag rdo rje tho ba thogs pa /
NK030(a)001:7099: ma ma ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma /
NK030(a)001:7100: mthing nag dgra bo gtun tu brdung bar byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7101: ma ma rdo rje dur khrod bdag mo sngon nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug pa gdengs ba /
NK030(a)001:7102: ma ma rdo rje sring mo sngo nag /
NK030(a)001:7104: ma ma rdo rje gsal bkra dmar nag /
NK030(a)001:7106: ma ma rdo rje khrag 'thung ma ljang nag /
NK030(a)001:7107: b+han d+ha rak+tasa bskang ba gsol ba /
NK030(a)001:7108: ma ma nag mo drel zhon ma /
NK030(a)001:7109: nad kyi rkyal pa gang du rtags pa /
NK030(a)001:7110: mtshon gyis gru gu glad la bskor ba /
NK030(a)001:7112: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing /
NK030(a)001:7113: sku cir yang bsgyur bar byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7114: ma ma ma mo gnas nyul ma /
NK030(a)001:7115: spyang khu'i mgo can mi sha za ba /
NK030(a)001:7116: ma ma ma mo rdzu byed ma stag dang dom dang /
NK030(a)001:7117: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul pa /
NK030(a)001:7118: ma ma 'dzum byed pho nya ma /
NK030(a)001:7121: ma ma gnam sa phyed kyi bdag mo ri lung med par gzugs gyis kheb pa /
NK030(a)001:7122: che chung med par 'joms par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:7123: ma ma ma mo rgyug byed ma /
NK030(a)001:7124: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gyi gos gon pa /
NK030(a)001:7125: ma ma pho nya za byed ma bud med kyi lus la stag gis gos gon pa /
NK030(a)001:7126: zas su gtsang rme med par za ba /
NK030(a)001:7127: ma ma rdo rje ya byin ma /
NK030(a)001:7128: dkar khra lcags kyu dang phur bu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7129: ma ma rdo rje bse sbyin rtsal mo che /
NK030(a)001:7132: ma ma rdo rje de byin dbang mo che /
NK030(a)001:7133: dmar mo rdo rje lcags sgrogs dang phur bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7134: ma ma rdo rje phag byin ma ljang nag rdo rje dril bu dang /
NK030(a)001:7136: ma ma sa bdag rgyal mo ser nag /
NK030(a)001:7137: gser gyi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7138: ma ma phyi 'khor skyong ba'i bdag mo //
NK030(a)001:7139: brgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul can no //
NK030(a)001:7140: ma ma 'phrog srin rje mo bud med bzang sdug 'od chags ma bkra shis pa /
NK030(a)001:7141: ral ba gyen du bsig pa /
NK030(a)001:7143: khro tshigs myur ba'i ma mo //
NK030(a)001:7144: bud med khrag gi las 'phran can no //
NK030(a)001:7146: bla ma rig 'dzin brgyud pa rnams bskyed de //
NK030(a)001:7147: rdzogs pa chen po'i brgyud pa dang //
NK030(a)001:7148: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa dang /
NK030(a)001:7149: sgyu 'phrul gyi brgyud pa dang gsum shar stod de byang shar nas /
NK030(a)001:7150: byang shar gyi bar du rim pa ltar bskyed /
NK030(a)001:7152: thog mar rdzogs chen brgyud pa ni /
NK030(a)001:7153: chos kun tu bzang po yab yum sku mdog sngon po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK030(a)001:7154: rus pa dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)001:7155: rin chen la sogs pa'i khri dang pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan la skyil krung gi bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7156: de'i g.yon du rgyal ba rigs lnga seng ge la sogs pa'i khri sogs spyi dang mthun par bskyed /
NK030(a)001:7157: de'i g.yon du sdud pa po /
NK030(a)001:7159: phyag na rdo rje gnyis spyi dang mthun par bskyed /
NK030(a)001:7160: gu ru mah+aa sha ri ram /
NK030(a)001:7162: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje rab byung gi tshul du gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7163: 'jal dpal bshes gnyen dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa'i tshul /
NK030(a)001:7164: rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo rgyal po'i gzugs /
NK030(a)001:7165: sras ra dza hasti rgyal bu'i gzugs can /
NK030(a)001:7166: sras mo wa ra ni btsun mo'i tshul /
NK030(a)001:7167: klu'i rgyal po 'jog po klu'i tshul /
NK030(a)001:7169: sbrul mgo'i gdeng ka sbrul gyi khri la pad dkyil bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7171: rgyal po'i sras mo gnod sbyin byang chub mo //
NK030(a)001:7172: bud med kyi gzugs can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7173: smad 'tshong ma a ra li bud med gyi tshul rdo rje 'adzinapa /
NK030(a)001:7174: kha che'i slob dpon a k+sho b+h+yahraba byung gi cha lugs /
NK030(a)001:7175: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku ra dz+aa ras dkar bcings pa /
NK030(a)001:7177: gzung ma smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha m+aa ti bud med kyi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7178: smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa ma ya /
NK030(a)001:7179: bud med kyi gzugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7180: o rgyan rgyal po ma h+aa ra dza ni rgyal bu dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7181: sras mo go ma de byi ni /
NK030(a)001:7182: bud med kyi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7183: +aa tsar+ya a lo ke kha che'i mkhan po rab snang dang gcig yin snyam /
NK030(a)001:7185: dge slong gi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7186: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma ras dkar dang ber thul /
NK030(a)001:7187: slob dpon ma h+aa ra dza dge slong gi cha lugs rdo rje 'dzin pa //
NK030(a)001:7188: slob dpon drang srong b+ha shi ti /
NK030(a)001:7189: drang srong gcer bu thor gtsug can /
NK030(a)001:7190: smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid chen mo /
NK030(a)001:7191: bud med kyi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7192: slob dpon n+aa ga rdzu na /
NK030(a)001:7193: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po /
NK030(a)001:7194: slob dpon de ba r+aa tsa ni /
NK030(a)001:7198: rig 'dzin dge bsnyen legs skyes rab byung gi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7199: slob dpon d+harma ra tsa dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7200: slob dpon bud d+ha gug ta phu tung dang chos gos can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7201: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha pan chen gyi cha lugs /
NK030(a)001:7202: slob dpon b+hi ma mi tra dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7204: dge slong gi cha byad rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7205: slob dpon be ro tsa na phu rung dang chos gos can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7206: slob dpon g.yu sgra snying po dge slong gi tshul rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7207: mkhas pa ye shes gzhon nu /
NK030(a)001:7208: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK030(a)001:7210: gnubs khu lung pa nyon yon tan rgya mtsho //
NK030(a)001:7212: mkhas pa nyang can sher mchog /
NK030(a)001:7215: zur chung shes rab grags pa //
NK030(a)001:7217: gsang bdag mda' tsha hor po /
NK030(a)001:7220: de'i sras bla ma thang stong 'bum med /
NK030(a)001:7221: chos rje bla skyabs rdo rje /
NK030(a)001:7222: drin can mkhas grub chen po //
NK030(a)001:7224: ma gcig drin can zur mo //
NK030(a)001:7229: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)001:7233: don grub legs pa dpal 'bar rnams dge slong rdo
NK030(a)001:7234: rje 'dzin pa'i cha lugs pa ci ltar 'os bar
NK030(a)001:7235: bsgom / de nas lung a nu yo ga mdo dbang brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:7236: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum sngon mo /
NK030(a)001:7237: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs rigs lnga /
NK030(a)001:7238: sdud pa po 'jam dpal dang phyag na rdo rje /
NK030(a)001:7239: spyan ras gzigs dam pa'i rigs can lnga gong ltar bskyed /
NK030(a)001:7240: de nas dge slong ku ku r+aa tsa /
NK030(a)001:7243: sras mo go ma de byi /
NK030(a)001:7246: slob dpon rdo rje gzhad pa //
NK030(a)001:7249: slob dpon sogs skya de ba /
NK030(a)001:7250: slob dpon sgegs pa rdo rje /
NK030(a)001:7251: slob dpon dz+nya na ku ma ra /
NK030(a)001:7252: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK030(a)001:7253: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK030(a)001:7254: slob dpon nam mkha' snying po /
NK030(a)001:7255: slob dpon chos blon de ba /
NK030(a)001:7256: rgya gar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong /
NK030(a)001:7257: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che /
NK030(a)001:7258: khu lungs kyi gnub ston yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK030(a)001:7262: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK030(a)001:7263: chu bar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK030(a)001:7265: sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK030(a)001:7270: 'gos ston pa bsod nams grags pa /
NK030(a)001:7271: yang na glan rdo rje 'od nas /
NK030(a)001:7275: glan ston chos kyi seng ge /
NK030(a)001:7283: bla ma dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)001:7287: sprul sku don grub dpal 'bar legs pa rnams dge slong rdo rje 'dzin par bsgom mo /
NK030(a)001:7288: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul brgyud pa'i bla ma bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:7289: chos sku kun bzang yab yum /
NK030(a)001:7290: longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga //
NK030(a)001:7291: sdud pa po rigs gsum mgon po /
NK030(a)001:7292: dam pa'i rigs can lnga ste /
NK030(a)001:7293: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)001:7295: gser mdog nor bu bsam 'phel 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7296: phyed skyil dkrung du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7297: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)001:7300: thal mo sbyar ba'i bar du nor bu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:7301: ma h+aa sha ri ram gi li h+aum /
NK030(a)001:7302: rig 'dzin gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong /
NK030(a)001:7303: dkar ser phyed dkyil rin po che'i sgrom bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:7304: ma h+aa rig 'dzin lang ka mgrin bcu /
NK030(a)001:7305: dkar smug skra bardzisa ro'i gdan la rkyang skum du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7306: ma h+aa rig 'dzin rgyal po li tsa byi /
NK030(a)001:7307: rab byung gi tshul skyil krung gi bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:7308: ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza /
NK030(a)001:7311: rgyal po u pa ra dza /
NK030(a)001:7312: sring mo go ma de w+air /
NK030(a)001:7313: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza /
NK030(a)001:7314: ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub /
NK030(a)001:7318: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK030(a)001:7321: mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis /
NK030(a)001:7324: khu lugs yon tan rgyal mtsho /
NK030(a)001:7326: myang shes rab mchog myang ye shes 'byung gnas /
NK030(a)001:7335: dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge /
NK030(a)001:7345: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK030(a)001:7346: rig 'dzin chos kyi rje rdo rje bzang po /
NK030(a)001:7349: rgyal ba don grub legs pa dpal 'bar rnams phal
NK030(a)001:7350: chen dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa sha stag tu
NK030(a)001:7351: bsgom mo // lha tshogs de dag rnams la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK030(a)001:7352: sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK030(a)001:7353: sa ma dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK030(a)001:7355: dza h+aum bam hos ba stim /
NK030(a)001:7356: ka ya wa ka tsi tas brtan par byas /
NK030(a)001:7357: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK030(a)001:7358: sgrub dang gdug ba 'dul ba yis /
NK030(a)001:7360: / 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs la /
NK030(a)001:7361: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)001:7372: glu ye shes rnams dbyangs dang bcas pas zhi khro ltar /
NK030(a)001:7374: rgya mtshor lnga'i smon lam gdab //
NK030(a)001:7377: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK030(a)001:7379: / 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK030(a)001:7380: bcom ldan dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)001:7381: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
