NK030(a)001:9396: a b+hi kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9398: rdo rje mtshon na dril 'khrol ma'i //
NK030(a)001:9399: nub kyi spor ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9400: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:9402: lha min ston pa gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9403: srin mo 'bar ma thogs med btul //
NK030(a)001:9404: thogs med sngo nag skar mda' gdong //
NK030(a)001:9405: byang gi 'bar ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9407: ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:9409: yi dwags thub pa gnas gyur pas /
NK030(a)001:9411: / 'bar ma srin mo me gdong btul //
NK030(a)001:9413: shar lho'i spor mo'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9414: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:9415: a b+hi dmyal pa'i ston pa gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9416: srin mo 'bar ma ral can brtul //
NK030(a)001:9417: gshin rje sngo nag ral gri dgra //
NK030(a)001:9418: lho nub spor ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9419: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata //
NK030(a)001:9421: lha yi ston pa gnas gyur pas /
NK030(a)001:9423: / 'bar ma srin mo gnod sbyin btul //
NK030(a)001:9424: gnod sbyin mthing nag khyung thogs ma //
NK030(a)001:9425: nub byang 'bar ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9426: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:9428: byol song ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9429: srin mo glang sna 'bar ma btul /
NK030(a)001:9431: / 'jigs rten smug nag glog sha rdebs //
NK030(a)001:9432: byang shar 'bar ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9434: ar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:9436: dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma //
NK030(a)001:9437: ser mo ral can rmongs byed ma //
NK030(a)001:9438: dmar mo dbang bsdud za byed ma /
NK030(a)001:9439: ljang mo las mkhan tshe 'phel la //
NK030(a)001:9440: gsal ba'i yum bzhi dbang 'di bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9441: badz+ra kha kha mu kha sha ra ya y+aa na ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9443: ser mor ral can rmongs byed ma //
NK030(a)001:9444: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad mo'i //
NK030(a)001:9445: lho phyogs g.yas na 'khril ba yi //
NK030(a)001:9446: sangs rgyas kun gyis gzugs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:9447: gsang ba'i yum 'di'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:9448: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sa ma ya y+aa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9450: dmar mo dbang bsdud za byed ma //
NK030(a)001:9451: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad mo //
NK030(a)001:9452: nub kyi phyogs nas rgyab tu 'khril /
NK030(a)001:9453: sangs rgyas kun gyis gzugs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:9454: gsang ba'i yum 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:9455: sh+ri badz+ra kha tam ka pra dz+wa la ya y+aa ma h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9457: ljang mo las mkhan tshe 'phel ma //
NK030(a)001:9458: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad mo //
NK030(a)001:9459: byang phyogs g.yon nas 'khril ba yi //
NK030(a)001:9460: sangs rgyas kun gyis gzugs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:9461: gsang ba'i yum 'dis dbang ba skur ro //
NK030(a)001:9462: sh+ri badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na mah
NK030(a)001:9463: a b+hi des spor mo brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi
NK030(a)001:9464: dang bcu gnyis kyi dbang de song nas //
NK030(a)001:9465: sgo 'khyams gsum pa'i dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:9467: phyir rim lcags ri nag po yi //
NK030(a)001:9468: sgo bzhi'i snam bu ngos bzhi la //
NK030(a)001:9469: dbang phyug tshogs kyi bskor ba la //
NK030(a)001:9470: srin po'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9471: dbang phyug chen mo ming sring mo //
NK030(a)001:9472: sku mdog dmar nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK030(a)001:9473: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9474: mi sring dmar ser zhing chen tri shul g.yag /
NK030(a)001:9475: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK030(a)001:9476: ma nu rak+sha si yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9477: ma nu raka sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9479: tshangs pa'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9480: dbang phyug chen mo tshangs ma ste //
NK030(a)001:9481: sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK030(a)001:9482: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9483: tshangs pa dmar skya rtse lnga b+han dmar sprul //
NK030(a)001:9484: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK030(a)001:9485: badz+ra pra ha ma n+ai'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9486: badz+ra pra ha ma ni b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9487: a b+hi lha chen khyab 'jug chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9488: dbang phyug chen mo 'khrug mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9489: sku mdog dkar mo tril shul la //
NK030(a)001:9490: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9491: khro mo dmar ser dbyug tho snying 'byin gzig /
NK030(a)001:9492: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul byin brlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:9493: badz+ra ro'u tri'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9496: rgya byin chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9497: dbang phyug ma chen dbang mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9498: sku mdog dkar mo in+t+ra gdeng //
NK030(a)001:9499: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9500: in+t+ra dkar dmar byi za dung dmar spre //
NK030(a)001:9501: che ba'i yon tan bsam yas pa /
NK030(a)001:9502: badz+ra be sna be ye dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9505: khyab 'jug chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9506: dbang phyug chen mo 'jug sred mo //
NK030(a)001:9508: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9509: khyab 'jug ser mo 'khor lo pha wa dril //
NK030(a)001:9510: dregs pa'i mthu stos bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9511: badz+ra ku ma ra ya dbang mchog khyod la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9514: gzhon nu chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9515: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9516: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK030(a)001:9517: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9518: dbang mo dmar skya bam dbyug khog chen dred //
NK030(a)001:9519: yon tan mthu rtsal bsam yas pa //
NK030(a)001:9520: badz+ra in+t+ra'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9522: a b+hi lha mo khyo med gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9523: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9524: zhi ba dmar mo tsan d+han 'thung //
NK030(a)001:9525: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9526: dmar mo rgyu zhags dmar mo dom //
NK030(a)001:9527: yid kyi 'dod pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9528: badz+ra sing ka la yi dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9531: nyi ma'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9532: dbang phyug chen mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK030(a)001:9533: sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK030(a)001:9534: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9535: bdud rtsi sngon mo chu srin rin chen bum //
NK030(a)001:9536: sman gyi mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK030(a)001:9537: badz+ra a mri ta'i dbang mchog bu la byin /
NK030(a)001:9540: zla ba'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9541: dbang phyug chen mo zhi ma mo //
NK030(a)001:9542: sku mdog dkar mo pun d+ha ri //
NK030(a)001:9543: de nyid las kyang gyur pa yi //
NK030(a)001:9544: zhi ba sngo skya bam ril khog smad sdig /
NK030(a)001:9545: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyi mthus //
NK030(a)001:9546: badz+ra so'u me'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9549: be con chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9550: dbang phyug chen mo be con mo //
NK030(a)001:9551: sku mdog sngon mo dbyug tho 'chang //
NK030(a)001:9552: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9553: be con nag mo bam chen thod rlon khra //
NK030(a)001:9554: drag shul ldan pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK030(a)001:9555: dom gyis dbang mchog bu la byin //
NK030(a)001:9557: a b+hi srin mo khyo med gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9558: dbang phyug chen mo srin mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9559: sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK030(a)001:9560: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9561: srin mo dmar nag zhing chen rgyu 'dren wa //
NK030(a)001:9562: drag po'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9563: badz+ra rak+sha si'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9565: a b+hi ma h+aa ka la'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9566: dbang phyug chen mo za ba mo //
NK030(a)001:9567: sku mdog dmar nag ba su 'dren //
NK030(a)001:9568: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9569: za byed nag mo bam chen snying 'byin stag /
NK030(a)001:9570: mthu stobs gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9571: badz+ra bag+sha si yi dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9573: a b+hi 'bring gi ri ti'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9574: dbang phyug chen mo dga' mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9575: sku mdog dkar mo dkar dar 'chang //
NK030(a)001:9576: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9577: dga' byed dmar mo khog chen bgegs rgyal dgod //
NK030(a)001:9578: mthu dang longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab mnga' /
NK030(a)001:9582: stobs bzang chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9583: dbang phyug chen mo khrag 'thung myos //
NK030(a)001:9584: sku mdog dkar mo gshol 'chang ma //
NK030(a)001:9585: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9586: khrag 'thung dmar nag rdor dbyug dung dmar rta /
NK030(a)001:9587: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9588: badz+ra ru tri ra ma tram gyi dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9589: badz+ra ru tri re ma ti b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9590: a b+hi shiny+tsa rnam thos chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9591: dbang phyug chen mo gcig pu spyod //
NK030(a)001:9592: rdo rje ser mo spu gri gcod //
NK030(a)001:9593: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)001:9594: gcig pu dkar dmar rdo rje b+han d+ha lding /
NK030(a)001:9596: / 'byor pa'i longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK030(a)001:9597: badz+ra e ka tsa ra dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9598: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9600: 'dod pa lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9601: dbang phyug chen mo yid 'phrog ma //
NK030(a)001:9602: sku mdog dmar mo mda' gzhu thogs //
NK030(a)001:9603: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9604: yid 'phrog dmar ser bzhi bsdom byi za khyi /
NK030(a)001:9606: / 'dod pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9607: badz+ra ma nu ta'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9608: badz+ra ma nu ha ri b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9610: nor bsrungs chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9611: dbang phyug chen mo grub mor byung //
NK030(a)001:9612: sku mdog dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:9613: de nyid las kyang skur gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9614: grub mo dkar dmar pad+ma byi za shud /
NK030(a)001:9615: lhag par nor gyis longs spyod che //
NK030(a)001:9616: badz+ra si ti kam gyi dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9619: rlung lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9620: dbang phyug chen mo rlung mor byung //
NK030(a)001:9621: sku mdog sngo nag ba dan 'phyar //
NK030(a)001:9622: de nyid las kyang sku sprul pas //
NK030(a)001:9623: rlung mo dmar skya ro za sha po mgo  /
NK030(a)001:9625: badz+ra ba ya be yi dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9629: / 'jig rten skyong ba'i khyo med gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9630: dbang phyug chen mo khyod med ma /
NK030(a)001:9631: sku mdog dmar nag ral gris gcod //
NK030(a)001:9632: de nyid las kyang gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9633: gsod byed ljang nag bam chen rnga chung spyang //
NK030(a)001:9634: bsgrol byed mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9635: badz+ra ma h+aa ra ma ni'i dbang chen bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9636: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9637: a b+hi ag+ne me lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9638: sku mdog dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:9639: dbang phyug chen mo me mor byung //
NK030(a)001:9640: de nyid las kyang skur sprul pa //
NK030(a)001:9641: mi mo ljang dmar rgyu 'dren skyin //
NK030(a)001:9642: rnam rtog bag chags 'jig rten kun bsreg bas //
NK030(a)001:9643: badz+ra ag ne ma'i dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9645: a b+hi shiny+tsa sa bdag chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9646: dbang phyug chen mo phag mor sprul //
NK030(a)001:9647: sku mdog dmar nag mche ba bsnams //
NK030(a)001:9648: de nyid las kyang skur sprul pa //
NK030(a)001:9649: ljang ser byi za gri thogs phag  /
NK030(a)001:9650: 'jig rten khams kyi dpal gcig ma //
NK030(a)001:9651: badz+ra da ra'i dbang rdzogs bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9653: a b+hi shiny+tsa gshin rje'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9654: dbang phyug chen mo rgan byed ma //
NK030(a)001:9655: rgan byed dmar smug byi ro'i rgyu ma za //
NK030(a)001:9656: de las 'jigs pa'i sku sprul pa /
NK030(a)001:9658: / 'bar ma ljang sngon rgyu 'dren khrag 'thor khra //
NK030(a)001:9659: ma mo'i mthu dbang kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9660: badz+ra tsa mun di'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9663: b+ai na ya ka'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9664: dbang phyug ma mo sna chen mo //
NK030(a)001:9665: sku mdog dmar nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK030(a)001:9666: de nyid 'jigs pa'i skur sprul pa //
NK030(a)001:9667: sna chen ljang dmar bam chen longs spyod glang //
NK030(a)001:9668: bgegs chen kun 'dul mthu stobs kyis //
NK030(a)001:9669: badz+ra su ta na'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9671: a b+hi shiny+tsa chu lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9672: dbang phyug chen mo chu lha mo //
NK030(a)001:9673: sku mdog dkar sngo sprul zhags 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:9674: de las 'jigs pa'i skur sprul pa //
NK030(a)001:9675: klu mo ljang nag bdud rtsi dung dmar sbrul //
NK030(a)001:9676: rin chen gter gyi longs sbyod bsam yas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:9677: badz+ra ba ru na yi dbang mchog bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9680: nag po chen po'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9681: dbang phyug chen mo nag mo ste //
NK030(a)001:9682: sku mdog nag mo am g+hu sha  /
NK030(a)001:9684: nag ma lcags kyu khu byug pu tra mgo //
NK030(a)001:9685: thams cad 'dzin byed mthu kun rdzogs pa yi //
NK030(a)001:9686: badz+ra ma h+aa ka la'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9687: badz+ra ma h+aa ka li b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9689: ra gdong khyo med gnas gyur ba //
NK030(a)001:9690: dbang phyug chen mo ra mgo ma /
NK030(a)001:9691: sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams /
NK030(a)001:9694: ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren pa'i ra /
NK030(a)001:9696: / 'khor ba mi gtong 'chi bdag dbang mo che /
NK030(a)001:9697: badz+ra tsakra'i dbang mchog bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9699: a b+hi bum sna'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9700: dbang phyug bum sna sngo nag ma //
NK030(a)001:9701: sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrogs sdom /
NK030(a)001:9704: be con lcags sgrogs kun 'joms seng //
NK030(a)001:9705: dgra bgegs bdud srin dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:9706: badz+ra bum pa ka la'i dbang chen bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9708: a b+hi gsus po che'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9709: dbang phyug gsus 'dzin chen mor byung //
NK030(a)001:9710: sku mdog ljang nag dril bu 'khrol /
NK030(a)001:9713: gsus 'dzin ljang dmar dril chen dung dmar skyog /
NK030(a)001:9714: nga rgyal dregs pa'i zhing bcu gnas spor ba //
NK030(a)001:9715: badz+ra lam+b+ho d+ha ra'i dbang chen bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9716: badz+ra lam+b+ho po d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:9717: a b+hi des dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad mgo brnyan med pa dang /
NK030(a)001:9718: mgo brnyan yod pa gnyis gnyis te lnga bcu rtsa drug gi dbang des song nas /
NK030(a)001:9719: 'khyams bzhi pa la mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu so gnyis kyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:9721: phyi rim lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:9722: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK030(a)001:9723: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK030(a)001:9724: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9725: mkha' 'gro dag byed rdo rje bsnams //
NK030(a)001:9726: mkha' 'gro rdo rje rigs dbang phyug /
NK030(a)001:9727: ma h+aa badz+ra da ra'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9730: rdo rje rgyal po gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)001:9732: / 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu ma /
NK030(a)001:9734: kro tishwa ri'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:9736: a rdo rje chags pa gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9737: gsod byed thabs kyi mda' 'gengs ma //
NK030(a)001:9738: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rjogs //
NK030(a)001:9739: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ti dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9740: badz+ra ma h+aa he la ba ti h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9742: rdo rje legs pa gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9743: spor byed dkar skya spu gri thogs //
NK030(a)001:9744: mkha' 'gro nyon mongs gcod mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:9745: badz+ra ku ma ri yi dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9746: badz+ra ku m+aa ra pra ye h+aum //
NK030(a)001:9748: rdo rje rin chen gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)001:9752: ma h+aa badz+ra ma ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9753: ma h+aa badz+ra ma ti h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9754: a b+hi shiny+tsa rdo rje nyi ma gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9756: rnam rtog mun sel mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:9757: badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9758: badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:9760: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9761: khro gnyer mthing nag zhing dar 'phyar //
NK030(a)001:9762: bdud bzhi rgyal byed dbang ldan pa ma /
NK030(a)001:9763: badz+ra tsaka na'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9766: rdo rje gzhad pa gnas gyur pa /
NK030(a)001:9768: / 'joms byed zhing gi kha gdangs ma //
NK030(a)001:9769: dur khrod bgegs 'joms za byed ma'i //
NK030(a)001:9770: ma h+aa badz+ra kro ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9771: ma h+aa badz+ra kro ti h+aum //
NK030(a)001:9773: rdo rje chos rab gnas gyur pas //
NK030(a)001:9774: chags byed dmar nag pad+ma bsnams //
NK030(a)001:9775: nyes pa'i skyon bral legs pa'i dbang rdzogs pa //
NK030(a)001:9776: ma h+aa a mri tod pa ti'i dbang rnams bu la spyin /
NK030(a)001:9777: ma h+aa a mri tot+pa ti h'u /
NK030(a)001:9778: a b+hi rdo rje rnon po gnas gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:9779: chags bral dmar nag gri thogs ma //
NK030(a)001:9780: mkha' 'gro bsgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:9781: ma h+aa so'u ma'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /

NK030(a)001:9787: mkha' 'gro gcod byed mthu dbang rjogs /
NK030(a)001:9788: ma h+aa badz+ra tsan ti'i dbang rnams bu la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:9789: ma h+aa badz+ra tsan ti h+aum //

NK030(a)001:9797: sna tshogs lus can rgya gram thogs //

NK030(a)001:9800: dbang rnams bu ma h+aa smri ti ka pa la

NK030(a)001:9810: rdo rje gnod sbyin gnas gyur pa //

NK030(a)001:11694: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11695: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11698: ljang nag gcod pa'i shag ti thogs //
NK030(a)001:11700: pho nya'i 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11701: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11702: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11704: las kyi pho nya drag mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11705: ljang nag gru gsum mthing nag thogs //
NK030(a)001:11706: drag po las kyi pho nya mo //
NK030(a)001:11707: phyag rgya'i sku 'di'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11708: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11709: e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11712: ljang smug sle'u nag sa la brdebs //
NK030(a)001:11713: rang la rang yang tshig cing khro //
NK030(a)001:11714: pho nya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11715: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11716: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11718: las kyi pho nya myur grub ma /
NK030(a)001:11720: / 'jam dpal rnon po lag na thogs //
NK030(a)001:11721: ha ha ru lu'i sgra sgrog ma'i //
NK030(a)001:11722: phyag rgya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11723: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11724: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa //
NK030(a)001:11726: 'phrin las pho nya chud mi zos //
NK030(a)001:11727: ljang smug re chen me sgron thogs //
NK030(a)001:11728: gdung bas brtse zhing phan 'dogs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11729: phyag rgya'i sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11730: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11732: las kyi pho nya 'dul byed ma'i //
NK030(a)001:11733: ljang smug srin po'i thod pa thogs /
NK030(a)001:11734: khyod kyi mi 'dul gang yang med //
NK030(a)001:11735: pho nya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11736: pa tsa pa e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11738: 'phrin las pho nya rgya mtsho ma //
NK030(a)001:11739: sna tshogs lus 'chang rgya mtsho rlabs /
NK030(a)001:11741: / 'dzam bu gling bzhi g.yo byed ma'i //
NK030(a)001:11742: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11743: pa tsa pa tsa g+ha n+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11744: e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa //
NK030(a)001:11746: las kyi pho nya ltung 'dzin ma /
NK030(a)001:11747: sems can zhing bcu bsgral ba la //
NK030(a)001:11748: dmyal bar ltung nges lcags kyus 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:11749: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11750: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11752: 'phrin las lha mo sgrol byed ma //
NK030(a)001:11754: rdul du brlag pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:11755: pho nya 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11756: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11757: e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11759: las kyi pho nya rang dbang mo //
NK030(a)001:11762: / 'jig rten las kyi gnyen gcig ma //
NK030(a)001:11763: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11764: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11765: e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11768: skyes bu na chung gzugs 'chang bas //
NK030(a)001:11769: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'dul //
NK030(a)001:11770: phyag rgya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11771: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11772: e sha ra dza yan ti s+w+aa h+aa //
NK030(a)001:11773: las kyi pho nya gom pa mo //
NK030(a)001:11774: ljang khu nyungs kyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK030(a)001:11775: dkar nag snying gi mtshams su brdeg /
NK030(a)001:11776: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11777: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11779: 'phrin las pho nya las la mkhas //
NK030(a)001:11780: ljang skya mche ba'i zor 'phen ma //
NK030(a)001:11781: log pa'i phyogs rnams bzlog byed ma'i //
NK030(a)001:11782: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11783: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11784: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11785: a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum las kyi pho nya dbang bsgyur ma //
NK030(a)001:11786: nyi zla gza' skar slog pa gyon /
NK030(a)001:11788: / 'dzam bu gling bzhi lag na thogs //
NK030(a)001:11789: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11790: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11791: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11793: 'phrin las lha mo mchog sgrol ma //
NK030(a)001:11795: skye shi gnyis kyi rtsa da gcod ma //
NK030(a)001:11796: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11797: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11798: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11800: las kyi pho nya rgyu sgrol ma //
NK030(a)001:11801: thugs dam gnyan po rgyud bskul phyir //
NK030(a)001:11802: shel dang lung thang sbu bu bsnams //
NK030(a)001:11803: pho nya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11804: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11805: e sha ra sha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11807: 'phrin las pho nya rngam pa mo //
NK030(a)001:11808: ljang skya sha khrag rlon pa za //
NK030(a)001:11809: gsod pa'i las la rngam pa mo //
NK030(a)001:11810: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11811: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11813: las kyi pho nya spro rkyeen mo //
NK030(a)001:11814: ljang skya 'debs pa'i las la myur //
NK030(a)001:11815: dza dza ha ha'i sgras 'debs ma //
NK030(a)001:11816: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11817: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11819: 'phrin las lha mo gtum pa mo //
NK030(a)001:11821: gtum pas 'dod khams lha mi btsan //
NK030(a)001:11822: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11823: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho //
NK030(a)001:11824: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11826: las kyi pho nya dmig dmar ma //
NK030(a)001:11827: khrag gi char pas myos par byed //
NK030(a)001:11828: mig rtsa dmar la ra gdong che //
NK030(a)001:11829: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11830: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+ta ho e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11833: / 'phrin las pho nya sen mo can //
NK030(a)001:11834: dmar smug sen mo lcags kyus bltams //
NK030(a)001:11835: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dzin byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11836: phyag rgya sku 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11837: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+da ho /
NK030(a)001:11838: e sha ra sa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:11840: des byang phyogs kyi pho nya drug bcu'i dbang bskur ba de song nas /
NK030(a)001:11841: sgo khyams dgu pa 'og gi ma mo drug bcu'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)001:11842: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)001:11843: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:11844: sku yis 'od zer smug nag las //
NK030(a)001:11845: ma mo las byed drug bcur sprul //
NK030(a)001:11846: ral pa gcig ma ma thing kha 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK030(a)001:11847: tri shul ral gri dril bu nad rkyal thogs //
NK030(a)001:11848: ma mo 'di yis dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:11849: ma me raka shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:11851: sbas pa'i ma mo thal mdog thod khrag 'thung //
NK030(a)001:11852: g.yang gzhi dur khrod brgyan gyis mdzes par klubs //
NK030(a)001:11853: srid pa gsum na mthu che rtsal drag pa //
NK030(a)001:11854: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:11857: dur khrod tshogs kyi ma mo ral ba can //
NK030(a)001:11858: mi thod phreng bas skur brgyan rab tu brjid //
NK030(a)001:11859: khams gsum 'di na mthu chen khyod la 'dud //
NK030(a)001:11860: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11863: za byed rngam pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11864: mthing skya khrag gi ral pa gos su gon //
NK030(a)001:11865: phyag gi skye 'gro yongs kyi tsit+ta bzung //
NK030(a)001:11866: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11869: khams gsum sdud pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11870: dmar mo thod khrag skom du 'thung byed pas //
NK030(a)001:11871: nga rgyal dreg pa'i 'khor kyang 'joms byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11872: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11875: rgyu drug sgrol ba'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11876: smug nag me 'bar rgya mtsho gos su gyon //
NK030(a)001:11877: mi snying rgyus pa'i phreng ba klad la bskor //
NK030(a)001:11878: ma mo 'di yis dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11881: srid gsum za byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11882: dmar nag gnam sa gnyis kyang gos su gon //
NK030(a)001:11883: bdud dang srin po'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing mdud //
NK030(a)001:11884: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11887: snang srid yongs la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK030(a)001:11888: ser nag nyi zla thod du bcings //
NK030(a)001:11889: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11890: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11893: mthu rtsal snyems pa'i ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11894: ljang nag zhing gi go zu gsol //
NK030(a)001:11895: lag pa g.yas kyi nam mkha' 'degs //
NK030(a)001:11896: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya /
NK030(a)001:11899: khro chen sha khrag gsur la dga' /
NK030(a)001:11901: / mi sha rta sha zas su za //
NK030(a)001:11902: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung /
NK030(a)001:11903: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11906: sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11907: mthing nag nang khrol glo snying 'byin //
NK030(a)001:11908: las su dam nyams sgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)001:11909: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang yang bskur //
NK030(a)001:11911: a b+hi ma mo za byed chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11912: sngo nag g.yu'i za ma tog /
NK030(a)001:11913: nyams pa len cing bsgrub la stobs //
NK030(a)001:11914: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur //
NK030(a)001:11916: a b+hi rngam byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11917: gnam gyi 'brug sngon chibs su chibs //
NK030(a)001:11918: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK030(a)001:11919: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11922: 'dzin byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11923: ser nag thod khrag lcags kyu thogs //
NK030(a)001:11924: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen mo //
NK030(a)001:11925: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11927: a b+hi bgegs chen 'joms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11928: sngo nag spu gri tho ba thogs //
NK030(a)001:11929: bgegs kyi rgyal po'i snying la 'gems //
NK030(a)001:11930: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:11933: sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni /
NK030(a)001:11934: ljang nag b+hany+tsa gri thogs ma /
NK030(a)001:11936: / 'jig rten khams kyi dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:11937: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:11940: chad bas gcod pa'i ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11941: sngo nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi brdebs //
NK030(a)001:11942: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK030(a)001:11943: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:11946: 'byung po bsgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11947: ban d+ha gri thogs 'byung po bsgrol //
NK030(a)001:11948: shar gyis phyogs nas las byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11949: ma mo 'di yi dbang yang bskur bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:11952: gshin rje sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11953: ban+ha gri thogs gshin rje sgrol //
NK030(a)001:11954: lho yi phyogs nas las byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11955: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11958: nub phyogs klu sgrol chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11959: ban+d+ha gri thogs klu chen sgrol //
NK030(a)001:11960: nub kyi phyogs nas las phyed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11961: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11964: gnod sbyin ma mo chen mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11965: ljang nag ban+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK030(a)001:11966: byang gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK030(a)001:11967: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11970: srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:11971: sngo nag ban+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK030(a)001:11972: steng gi phyogs kyi las byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11973: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11976: srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni /
NK030(a)001:11977: smug nag ban+d+ha gri thogs ma /
NK030(a)001:11979: / 'og gi phyogs nas las byed ma'i //
NK030(a)001:11980: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11983: gzugs la dbang pa'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:11984: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa can //
NK030(a)001:11985: dgra bo'i gzugs rnams 'phrog byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:11986: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11989: khrag la dbang pa'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:11990: sngon mo thod khrag dkrug cing 'thung //
NK030(a)001:11991: dgra bo'i khrag rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK030(a)001:11992: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:11995: drod la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:11996: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta bsnams //
NK030(a)001:11997: sdang pa dgra bo'i drod 'phrog ma //
NK030(a)001:11998: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12001: dbugs la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:12002: ljang nag thod khrag zhags pa thogs //
NK030(a)001:12003: dgra bo'i dbugs rnams 'phrog byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:12004: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12006: a b+hi bkrag mdangs dbang ba'i dbang mo che /
NK030(a)001:12007: ser nag ral gri thod khrag 'thung /
NK030(a)001:12009: / 'jig rten khyab pa'i mthu mo che //
NK030(a)001:12010: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12013: ma mo za byed stag gi mgo /
NK030(a)001:12014: dmar ser thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:12016: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12019: ma mo 'dzin byed chu srin mgo /
NK030(a)001:12020: sha khrag gsur la dga' byed pas /
NK030(a)001:12023: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12026: ma mo chen mo dur khrod brgyan //
NK030(a)001:12027: mi lpags rlon pa na bza' gsol //
NK030(a)001:12028: dur khrod bgegs chen 'dul mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:12029: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12032: rdo rje gar gyi dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:12033: dbu stong spyan stong kun la khyab //
NK030(a)001:12034: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen mo //
NK030(a)001:12035: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12038: pad+ma gar gyis dbang phyug ma //
NK030(a)001:12039: lag na mi mgo'i phor pa ru //
NK030(a)001:12040: mi snying tshil bus bkang zhing gsol //
NK030(a)001:12041: ma mo 'di yis dbang yang bskur //
NK030(a)001:12045: dmar nag ban+d+ha khrag gis bkang //
NK030(a)001:12046: mig rtsa dmar zhing rngam pa che //
NK030(a)001:12047: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12049: a b+hi srid pa gsum gyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK030(a)001:12050: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil byed cing //
NK030(a)001:12051: rgya mtsho gting nas rnyog byed pas //
NK030(a)001:12052: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12055: rgya mtsho gting gi mthu mo che //
NK030(a)001:12056: na bza' chu srin lpags pas g.yogs //
NK030(a)001:12057: sbrul nag 'bum gyi gdengs ka can //
NK030(a)001:12058: ma mo 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12061: ma mo rdo rje tho ba ma //
NK030(a)001:12062: sngo nag mi bsrun tho ba thogs //
NK030(a)001:12063: srin po'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhig g.yo /
NK030(a)001:12064: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12067: ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK030(a)001:12068: mthing nag dgra bo gtun du brdung //
NK030(a)001:12069: gang la bya ba brdul du rlog /
NK030(a)001:12070: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12073: ma mo rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK030(a)001:12074: sngo nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug /
NK030(a)001:12075: gdug pa'i tshogs kyang 'joms par byed //
NK030(a)001:12076: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12079: ma mo rdo rje gdeng mo ni //
NK030(a)001:12080: sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum 'phyar //
NK030(a)001:12081: gdug cing gtum la drag shul che //
NK030(a)001:12082: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12085: ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma //
NK030(a)001:12086: dmar nag me yis rgyu zhags 'phen //
NK030(a)001:12088: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12091: ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma //
NK030(a)001:12094: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12097: ma mo nag mo dred zhon ma //
NK030(a)001:12098: nad kyi rkyal pa gong du btang //
NK030(a)001:12099: mtshon gyi gru gu klad la bskor //
NK030(a)001:12100: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12103: dus bzhi rgyal mo mthu mo che /
NK030(a)001:12104: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing //
NK030(a)001:12105: cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK030(a)001:12106: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12109: ma mo gnas nyul spyang ku'i mgo /
NK030(a)001:12110: mi sha za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK030(a)001:12111: bltas pas bdud rnams brlag byed pa'i //
NK030(a)001:12112: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12115: ma mo rdzun byed stag dang dom //
NK030(a)001:12116: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul //
NK030(a)001:12117: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK030(a)001:12118: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12121: ma mo 'dzum byed pho nya mo //
NK030(a)001:12122: khra ltar 'jums zhing khyi ltar zugs //
NK030(a)001:12123: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi len //
NK030(a)001:12124: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12127: ma mo gnam sa phyed kyi bdag /
NK030(a)001:12128: ri klung med par gzugs kyis khengs //
NK030(a)001:12129: che chung med par 'joms par byed //
NK030(a)001:12130: ma mo 'di yis dbang yang bskur //
NK030(a)001:12133: ma mo chen mo rgyug byed ma //
NK030(a)001:12134: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gos //
NK030(a)001:12135: bang ni ri klung med par rgyug /
NK030(a)001:12136: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12139: ma mo pho nya za byed ma //
NK030(a)001:12140: bud med lus la stag gis mgo //
NK030(a)001:12141: zas su gtsang rme med par za //
NK030(a)001:12142: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12145: rdo rje ya byin pho nya mo //
NK030(a)001:12146: dkar bkra lcags kyu phur bu 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:12147: gang la bya ba grub bar byed //
NK030(a)001:12148: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12151: rdo rje phag 'byin thogs pa med //
NK030(a)001:12152: dkar nag lcags sgrogs phur bu thogs //
NK030(a)001:12153: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK030(a)001:12154: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12157: rdo rje de byin dbang grub ma //
NK030(a)001:12158: ljang nag dril bu phur bu 'phen //
NK030(a)001:12159: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK030(a)001:12160: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12162: a b+hi sa bdag rgyal mo chen mo 'di //
NK030(a)001:12163: ser nag gser gyi bum pa can //
NK030(a)001:12164: tshe srog kun la dbang bsgyur ma'i //
NK030(a)001:12165: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12168: phyi 'khor skyong pa'i mnga' bdag mo //
NK030(a)001:12169: brgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK030(a)001:12170: gnas ni g.ya' dang gangs la bca' /
NK030(a)001:12172: / ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12175: 'brog srin rnams gyi rje mo ni //
NK030(a)001:12176: bud med bzang sdug 'od chags la //
NK030(a)001:12177: skra bshis ral pa gyen du gsigs //
NK030(a)001:12178: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12180: a b+hi 'khro tshig myur ba'i ma mo ni //
NK030(a)001:12181: bud med khrag gi lan phran can //
NK030(a)001:12182: nag mo lag na thod pa thogs //
NK030(a)001:12183: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12186: rdo rje bse byin rtsal mo che //
NK030(a)001:12187: sngo nag zhags pa phur bu 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:12188: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK030(a)001:12189: ma mo 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:12192: sgo khyams bcu pa'i rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi rgya
NK030(a)001:12193: dang dgu bcu go gnyis kyi dbang bskur ba ni
NK030(a)001:12194: / thog mar rdzogs chen rgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi dbang bskur ba ni //
NK030(a)001:12195: bla ma rnams khyed rang rnams la thim pas //
NK030(a)001:12196: thugs lnga lhun grub kyis sangs rgyas thob nas 'gro don lhun gyis grub par bsgom cig /
NK030(a)001:12197: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:12198: thugs lnga lhun grub kun bzang yab yum gyis //
NK030(a)001:12199: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:12200: thugs lngas 'gro don lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:12201: ma h+aa gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12202: dbus phyogs chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:12203: chos dbyings ye shes rdor sems yab yum gyis //
NK030(a)001:12204: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:12205: chos dbyings ye shes 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:12206: ma h+aa gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12207: shar phyogs chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:12208: me long ye shes rnam snang yab yum gyis //
NK030(a)001:12209: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:12210: me long ye shes 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:12211: ma h+aa gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12212: lho phyogs chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:12213: mnyam nyid ye shes rin 'byung yab yum gyis //
NK030(a)001:12214: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:12215: mnyam nyid ye shes 'gro don lhun grub shog /

NK030(a)001:12235: ma h+aa gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12236: rnam dag chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:12237: mthu stobs mnga' bdag phyag rdor thugs //
NK030(a)001:12238: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:12239: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK030(a)001:12240: ma h+aa gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12241: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje ni //
NK030(a)001:12242: rab byung tshul ste gsang ba'i mtshan //
NK030(a)001:12243: rdo rje bde byed rtsal zhes bya /
NK030(a)001:12245: / 'og min gnas bzhugs byin brlabs can //
NK030(a)001:12246: bdag gi grogs mdzod gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK030(a)001:12247: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur stsol //
NK030(a)001:12248: gu ru ma h+aa sha ri ram gyi li h+aum /
NK030(a)001:12250: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ni //

NK030(a)001:12840: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges can rtsal //

NK030(a)001:13187: sku yi 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13190: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13191: rig 'dzin rgyal po yon tan rgyal po yis //
NK030(a)001:13192: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13193: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13196: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13197: rig 'dzin sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)001:13198: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13199: sku yis yon tan lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13202: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13203: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho yis //
NK030(a)001:13204: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13205: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13208: rnam dag lha yis dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13209: rig 'dzin ye shes rgya mtsho yis //
NK030(a)001:13210: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13211: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13214: rnam dag lha yis dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13215: rig 'dzin nyang ni shes rab mchog /
NK030(a)001:13216: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13217: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13220: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13221: myang ni ye shes 'byung gnas kyis //
NK030(a)001:13222: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13223: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13224: ma h+aa gu ru h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13225: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13227: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13228: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13231: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13232: rig 'dzin zur chung shes rab grags //
NK030(a)001:13233: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13234: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13237: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13239: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13240: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13243: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13244: gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK030(a)001:13245: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13246: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13249: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13250: tsag tsha sh+aakya rdo rje yis //
NK030(a)001:13251: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13252: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13255: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13257: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13258: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13261: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13262: glan ston rdo rje 'od po yis //
NK030(a)001:13263: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13264: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13267: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13268: glan ston bsod nams rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK030(a)001:13269: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13270: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13273: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13274: dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge yis //
NK030(a)001:13275: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13276: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13279: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13280: glan ni sangs rgyas dpal ba yis //
NK030(a)001:13281: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13282: sku yis 'gro ngon lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13285: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13286: glan ni bsod nams mgon po yis //
NK030(a)001:13287: skal ldan rnams la dbang bas //
NK030(a)001:13288: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13291: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13293: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13294: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13297: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13299: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13300: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13303: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13304: zur ston sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyis //
NK030(a)001:13305: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13306: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13309: rnam dag lha yis dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13311: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13312: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13315: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13317: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13318: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13321: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13322: rig 'dzin dkon mchog bzang po yis //
NK030(a)001:13323: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13324: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13327: rnam dag lha yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:13328: rig 'dzin rdo rje bzang po yis //
NK030(a)001:13329: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13330: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13333: rnam dag lha yi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)001:13335: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13336: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13339: rnam dag lha yi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)001:13341: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13342: sku yis 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK030(a)001:13345: des bla ma brgyud pa'i dbang bskur ba de song /
NK030(a)001:13346: de'i gong du 'og gi ma mo drug bcu /
NK030(a)001:13347: de'i gong du pho nya drug bcu tshan bzhi /
NK030(a)001:13348: de'i gong du steng gi khro bo khro mo drug bcu /
NK030(a)001:13349: de'i gong du ging pho dgu mo dgu /
NK030(a)001:13350: de'i gong du ma bdun sring bzhi //
NK030(a)001:13351: de'i gong du mkha' 'gro so gnyis //
NK030(a)001:13352: de'i gong du dbang mo nyer brgyad //
NK030(a)001:13353: de'i gong du spor ma brgyad /
NK030(a)001:13355: de'i gong du phra men ma sgo ma bzhi /
NK030(a)001:13356: de'i gong du gnas ma brgyad /
NK030(a)001:13357: de'i gong du khrag 'thung nyi shu ste /
NK030(a)001:13358: phyag rgya'i lha bdun rgya'i dbang de song nas //
NK030(a)001:13359: spyi don brgyad pa ye shes lnga'am dgu'i dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13360: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13361: mar me'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)001:13362: dpal chen yab yum gsang ba'i thugs mchog pas //
NK030(a)001:13363: skye med dbyings nas ye shes mar me gsal //
NK030(a)001:13364: kun gzhi gnas gyur spyan gyi ye shes 'dis //
NK030(a)001:13365: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13366: badz+ra dz+nya na a lo ke shwa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13369: dpal chen po'i ye shes dgu la ma skyes pa chos kyi dbyings /
NK030(a)001:13374: ma g.yos ba stong pa klong du gyur ba 'da' ka /
NK030(a)001:13375: bdag nyid chen po'i ngang du gyur pa //
NK030(a)001:13376: dbyings su bsgrol ba'i ye shes //
NK030(a)001:13377: bde ba chen po'i ye shes //
NK030(a)001:13378: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dam pa dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13379: des ye shes lnga'am dgu'i dbang de song nas /
NK030(a)001:13380: rigs lnga'i tsaka li gtad de /
NK030(a)001:13381: ye shes chen po'i don ldan pas //
NK030(a)001:13382: ye shes lnga yi rtags mchog phyag rgya yis //
NK030(a)001:13383: gnas lngar gtug ste thugs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13384: ma h+aa shudz+nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)001:13386: dgu pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13387: rgyu rkyen la sogs bcu gsum dang ldan pas gnas gsum du rdo rje gsum bsam ste /
NK030(a)001:13389: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje dbang //
NK030(a)001:13390: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK030(a)001:13391: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK030(a)001:13392: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13394: ka ya wa ga tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13395: bcu pa bkra shis rtags brgyad kyi dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13396: rgyu rkyen la sogs bcu gsum dang ldan pas //
NK030(a)001:13397: dbang mchog thob pa'i bu mchog de //
NK030(a)001:13398: don dam 'grub pa'i bkra shis phyir //
NK030(a)001:13399: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK030(a)001:13400: rtags kyi brgyan te sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13402: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13403: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13404: phyag zhabs mthil la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13406: / 'di ni 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13408: phyag zhabs las bzhi'i don mdzad dbang //
NK030(a)001:13409: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13410: rdo rjes phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13411: nya sha gcig la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13413: / 'di ni gser nya dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13415: dpal gyi be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13416: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13417: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams las ni rnam par rgyal //
NK030(a)001:13418: thugs kha nyid la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13420: / 'di ni dpal be dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13422: mgur chu thugs rjes kun 'dzin dbang //
NK030(a)001:13423: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13424: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13425: mgur gyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13427: / 'di ni bum pa'i dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13429: ljags kyi pad+ma gos pa med pa'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13430: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13431: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13432: ljags kyi mchog la nges par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13434: / 'dis ni pad+ma dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13436: dung gis rgol ba dpal bkong sgrogs pa'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13437: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13438: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13439: tshems kyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13441: / 'di ni dung gi dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13443: rgyal mtshan bdud bzhi dag las rgyal ba'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13444: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13445: bsdo ba'i dngos po kun las khyad par 'phags /
NK030(a)001:13447: / 'di ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13449: dbu skra gdung gsil gdugs kyi dbang /
NK030(a)001:13450: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:13451: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK030(a)001:13452: dbu skra'i mchog la mngon pa gsal bar ston /
NK030(a)001:13454: / 'di ni gdugs kyi dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:13456: des bkra shis rtags brgyad kyi dbang de song nas /
NK030(a)001:13457: bcu gcig pa thig le ming gi dbang /
NK030(a)001:13458: rgyu rkyen la sogs bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13459: 'o khyed rang rnams la thig le ming gi dbang bskur ba yin pas /
NK030(a)001:13496: zhes thig le ming gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13497: sna ba'i dbang po la thig le byed do //
NK030(a)001:13498: de rnams kyi nang dbang bcu gcig song nas /
NK030(a)001:13499: spyi don gsum pa sgrub dbang la bcu gsum ste /
NK030(a)001:13500: shes rab rigs pa'i gtan tshig gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13503: dug gsum dag pa'i dbang dang //
NK030(a)001:13504: srid gsum bsgrol ba'i dbang dang //
NK030(a)001:13505: skyon gyis ma gos rnam dag gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13506: las rnams rdzogs pa'i dbang dang //
NK030(a)001:13508: gsang ba sbyor ba'i dbang dang //
NK030(a)001:13509: kun la dbang ba 'dod yon kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13510: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gtso bo'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13511: thams cad bsgrub pa rdzas kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13512: gnyis su med ba rdo rje ming gi dbang ngo //
NK030(a)001:13513: dang po shes rab rigs pa'am //
NK030(a)001:13515: rgyu rkyen la sogs pa don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13516: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK030(a)001:13517: sems kyi dbang bsgyur thob pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13518: shes rab chen po'i rigs pa'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13519: sems nyid don gyi gtan tshig sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13521: gsang ba sbyor ba'i shes rab ma //
NK030(a)001:13522: dri med rnam dag lha mo zhig /
NK030(a)001:13523: mtshan ldan rgyan gyis brgyan byas la //
NK030(a)001:13524: dbang thob khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13525: pra dz+nya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13526: des shes rab rigs ma'i dbang song nas /
NK030(a)001:13527: gnyis pa snying rje rtags kyi dbang ngam khams gsum dbang bsgyur gyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13528: rgyu rkyen la sogs bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13529: bya ba'i bsam pa kun bral zhing /
NK030(a)001:13530: rtsol med gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK030(a)001:13531: snying rje chen po bde mchog gis //
NK030(a)001:13532: khams gsum kun la dbang bskur sbyin /
NK030(a)001:13534: des snying rje rtags kyi dbang de song nas /
NK030(a)001:13535: gsum pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dbang ngam /
NK030(a)001:13537: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13538: nyon mongs lnga po gnas dag nas //
NK030(a)001:13539: ye shes lnga po thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:13541: dbang thob bu la sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13542: sarba ta tha ga ta dz+ny+aa na pany+tsa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13543: des yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang de song /
NK030(a)001:13545: yang gsum pa mthong gshol gyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13546: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK030(a)001:13547: thams cad rdzogs par nus pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13548: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa 'di //
NK030(a)001:13549: thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13551: bzhi pa dug gsum sprugs pa ga bu rnams gsum gyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13552: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13553: dug gsum rtsad nas za byed pa //
NK030(a)001:13554: ga bu gsum gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13555: sangs rgyas sku gsum thob par thob //
NK030(a)001:13557: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13558: rtag chen ga bu gsum gyi nang //
NK030(a)001:13559: dmar chen khrag gis bkang nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:13560: dbang thob de yis lag du sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13562: lnga pa srid gsum bsgrod ba'i gri'i dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13563: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13564: thog ma med pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK030(a)001:13565: dug gsum rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:13566: ral gri la sogs mtshon cha yis //
NK030(a)001:13567: dbang mchog dam pa khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13569: drug pa skyon gyis ma gos rnam dag pad+ma'i dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13570: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13572: / 'khor ba'i chos la ci spyad kyang //
NK030(a)001:13573: skyon gyis gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK030(a)001:13574: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK030(a)001:13575: rnam dag rdzas kyi pad+ma sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13576: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos rnams la //
NK030(a)001:13577: spyad kyang thabs kyis mi gos pa'i //
NK030(a)001:13578: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK030(a)001:13579: pad+ma'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13581: bdun pa las rnams rdzogs pa ti ra dbyug pa'i dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13582: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas //
NK030(a)001:13583: las rnams rdzogs par byed pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13584: dbang mchog dam pa rtags chen 'di /
NK030(a)001:13585: ti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dag /
NK030(a)001:13586: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13587: rnam bzhi las kyi 'dul ba yis //
NK030(a)001:13588: phyag rgya chen po bstan pa ni //
NK030(a)001:13589: ti ra chen po dbyug pa'i dbang /
NK030(a)001:13590: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13592: brgyad pa gnyis med 'khril ba sbrul nag chun po'i dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13593: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu dang ldan pa /
NK030(a)001:13594: sngon gyi dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)001:13595: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)001:13596: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13597: thugs rje zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK030(a)001:13598: de bzhin rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK030(a)001:13599: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13600: bdud dang srin po kun bcom nas /
NK030(a)001:13602: / 'jigs byed chen po'i mthu dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)001:13603: yab yum gnyis med 'khril ba yis //
NK030(a)001:13604: chos nyid ngang ni gnyis med rtags //
NK030(a)001:13606: dbang thob de yi lag du sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13608: dgu pa gsang ba sbyor ba shes rab lha mo'i dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13609: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas //
NK030(a)001:13610: don dam rang bzhi na spros dang bral //
NK030(a)001:13611: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK030(a)001:13612: zhi byed gzugs ma rgyal mo'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13613: skal ldan rnams 'byor khyod la sbyin /
NK030(a)001:13615: bcu pa kun la dbang ba 'dod yon lnga'i dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13616: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13617: dbang thob rgyal po chen po de //
NK030(a)001:13618: kun gyi bdag po yin pas na //
NK030(a)001:13619: rol mo dri dang zhal zas dang /
NK030(a)001:13621: / 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:13622: nye ba'i longs spyod brgyan rnams kun //
NK030(a)001:13623: thams cad thams cad sbyin par bya //
NK030(a)001:13625: bcu gcig pa sgrub pa'i rgyal po rdo rje gtso bo'i dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13626: rgyu rkyen la sogs don bcu gsum dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:13627: sgrub ba'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK030(a)001:13628: bsgrub ba'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK030(a)001:13629: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:13630: rgyal ba thams cad bsgrub pa dang //
NK030(a)001:13631: tshe dang sman la sogs pa rnams //
NK030(a)001:13632: bsgrub pa ma lus kun bsgrub cig /
NK030(a)001:13634: dbu brgyan ni thod pa'i zhal yas khang lngar gyur pa'i nang du /
NK030(a)001:13636: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin po che //
NK030(a)001:13637: dpag tu med pa'i 'od dang ldan /
NK030(a)001:13638: rigs mchog phyag rgya lnga ldan pas //
NK030(a)001:13639: khams gsum bdag pos dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:13640: rat+na mu gu ta ab+hi shiny+tsa h+aum tram tram tram /
NK030(a)001:13641: rigs kyi bu khyod la dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13642: dregs pa bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13644: slob ma 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos la mnga' mnyes shing /
NK030(a)001:13646: chos kyi rgyal po byed pa //
NK030(a)001:13647: rgyal ba tshe dpag tu med par sgom la /
NK030(a)001:13650: cod pan mi 'gyur mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK030(a)001:13651: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po'i dbang //
NK030(a)001:13652: khams gsum kun gyis dbang phyug cha /
NK030(a)001:13653: chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:13654: d+harma ra tsa shwa ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13655: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13656: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po mnga' mnyes nas //
NK030(a)001:13657: chos kyi 'khor lo yongs su bskor bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13659: phreng ba mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la spyod /
NK030(a)001:13661: / 'gro kun yang dag chos kyi don la 'dzud //
NK030(a)001:13662: me tog phreng ba la sogs dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13663: gzungs dang ting 'dzin ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13664: rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13665: me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13666: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13667: sngon gyi dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)001:13668: thod phreng tshar gsum dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13669: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK030(a)001:13670: dug gsum gnas su dag nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:13671: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13673: sngon gyi dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)001:13674: bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK030(a)001:13675: bcom ldan sku la bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:13676: zhing gi g.yang gzhi gsol nas kyang /
NK030(a)001:13678: / 'khor ba rdul du brlag mdzad bzhin //
NK030(a)001:13679: de bzhin rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK030(a)001:13680: zhing gis g.yang gzhis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13681: thams cad 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13682: sngon gyi dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)001:13683: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)001:13684: glang po che yis ko rlon gyis //
NK030(a)001:13685: gti mug gnas su dag bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:13686: khams gsum rgyal por gyur pa bzhin //
NK030(a)001:13687: de ring rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK030(a)001:13688: glang chen ko bas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13689: gti mug chos skur lhun grub nas //
NK030(a)001:13690: mthu dpung chen po 'joms par shog /
NK030(a)001:13691: sngon gyi dpal chen he ru kas //
NK030(a)001:13692: stag gi sham thabs gsol pa yis //
NK030(a)001:13693: bdud dang srin po kun bsgral nas //
NK030(a)001:13694: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdud //
NK030(a)001:13695: de bzhin rnal 'byor che ge la //
NK030(a)001:13696: stag gis sham thabs dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13697: dpa' bo bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK030(a)001:13698: rnam rtogs 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13700: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)001:13701: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)001:13702: khyung gis gshog pas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13703: bdud dang srin po zil gyis mnan //
NK030(a)001:13704: de bzhin rnal 'byor dbang phyug la //
NK030(a)001:13705: khyung gi gshog pas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13706: rdo rje khyung ltar thogs med pas //
NK030(a)001:13707: mkha' ltar yongs la khyab par shog /
NK030(a)001:13708: h+aum 'bar ma 'phro ba ye shes thugs rjer ldan //
NK030(a)001:13709: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcu'i mun pa sel //
NK030(a)001:13710: bskal ba'i me dbung 'bar bar dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13711: mtshan ma 'dzin rtog bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13712: badz+ra badz+ra dz+wa la ri dz+nya na h+aum /
NK030(a)001:13714: des bsgrub ba'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gtso bo'i dbang de song nas /
NK030(a)001:13715: bcu gnyis pa thams cad bsgrub pa rdzas kyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:13716: rgyu rkyen la sogs bcu gsum dang ldan pas rdo rje dril bu sbyin la /
NK030(a)001:13717: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pas //
NK030(a)001:13718: thugs mchog rtogs pa'i rig pas brgyan //
NK030(a)001:13719: rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13720: thabs dang shes rab dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:13721: badz+ra g+han+d+ha sha ri s+w+aa h+aa //
NK030(a)001:13722: rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13723: sku dang ye shes ldan pa'i chos la longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13725: nyung dkar rgyal po byin rlabs sha ri ram //
NK030(a)001:13726: bar chad bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms bsgrub rdzas 'dis //
NK030(a)001:13727: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13728: bar chad bgegs rnams brdul du brlag par shog /
NK030(a)001:13729: nyung dkar gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13731: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13733: dpal chen yab yum thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)001:13734: thar byed bgegs rnams tshar gcod mtshon char ldan //
NK030(a)001:13735: rdo rje ki la ya yi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13736: log 'dren dgra bgegs tshogs rnams 'joms par shog /
NK030(a)001:13737: badz+ra ki li ki la ya a be sha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13739: ya ma dam sri bar chod bsgrol ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13740: ban+ha sbyin la snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan pa bsgom la 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:13741: mtshan ma'i rtog bral ban+d+ha'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK030(a)001:13742: sngon gyis skyes mchog bsgrub pa'i rdzas yin te //
NK030(a)001:13743: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:13744: snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)001:13745: d+harma ka ya sha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13747: snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13749: shes rab gsang ba'i sgra sgrogs rnga mchog 'di /
NK030(a)001:13750: khams gsum kun la sgra sgrogs pas //
NK030(a)001:13751: nga rgyal drag shul bdud 'joms pa'i //
NK030(a)001:13752: rgyal mtshan 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:13753: pra dz+nya tsa ma ra sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13754: rnga chung gis dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13755: chos skye ba med pa'i sgra sgrags nas //
NK030(a)001:13756: bdud dang srin po zil gyis mnan te //
NK030(a)001:13757: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro dbang du 'dus pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13759: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK030(a)001:13760: dkar la dag pas gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK030(a)001:13761: skal ldan rnams 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13762: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:13764: byang chub sems kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13765: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan ste //
NK030(a)001:13766: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13768: dri chen bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK030(a)001:13769: rnam rtogs dug sel bdud rtsi bdag nyid de //
NK030(a)001:13770: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13771: de ni rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:13773: dri chen gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13774: stobs chen po ye shes rtogs te //
NK030(a)001:13775: de bzhin rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13777: ma rigs khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can 'di //
NK030(a)001:13778: gnas na bsgrol mdzad rdzas mchog 'di //
NK030(a)001:13779: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13780: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:13782: sha chen gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:13783: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rtogs te /
NK030(a)001:13784: rin chen gyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13786: gsang ba dbang gi rdzas mchog rak+ta 'di //
NK030(a)001:13787: chags med bde la spyad pas dmar la dngas //
NK030(a)001:13788: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13789: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:13792: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes rtogs te /
NK030(a)001:13793: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13795: rang byung dag pas las mchog rigs kyi rdzas //
NK030(a)001:13796: phyi nang gsos gyur bdud rtsi'i rigs na 'di //
NK030(a)001:13797: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13798: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:13799: kri ta dri chus dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13800: bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes rtogs te //
NK030(a)001:13801: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13802: bdud rtsi a mri ta sbyin la /
NK030(a)001:13803: thams cad sman ni bdud rtsi mchog /
NK030(a)001:13804: rgyal ba kun gyis bsgrub pa'i lam //
NK030(a)001:13805: ra sa ya nas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:13806: bdud rtsi'i bcud dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)001:13807: sarba a mri ta sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:13809: skye ba med pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13810: bcu gsum pa gnyis su med pa rdo rje ming gi dbang ni //
NK030(a)001:13847: zhes rdo rje'i ming gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:13848: de rnams kyi bsgrub dbang bcu gsum song nas //
NK030(a)001:13849: spyi don bzhi pa gsang dbang la gnyis te /
NK030(a)001:13851: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo /
NK030(a)001:13853: de don rnam pa bcu gsum ste //
NK030(a)001:13854: rang gi ngo bo rgyu rkyen nas //
NK030(a)001:13855: nges tshig sgrib pa tshad dang chos //
NK030(a)001:13856: snod 'bras dgongs pa skyon yin no //
NK030(a)001:13857: rdzas la rab gnas ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:13858: tha mi dad pa'i thob bya ste //
NK030(a)001:13859: rang gi ngo bo zhes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:13860: rgyu gnyis mtshungs rgyu rang la gnas //
NK030(a)001:13861: thabs kyi yan lag lhan cig byed //
NK030(a)001:13862: dbang ba'i shes pa rkyen bzhi ste //
NK030(a)001:13863: kun gzhi bag chags rgyu'i rkyen /
NK030(a)001:13864: slob dpon dbang ldan bdag po'i rkyen //
NK030(a)001:13865: thob bar bya rgyu dmigs pa'i rkyen //
NK030(a)001:13866: gcig thob gcig gi go byed pa //
NK030(a)001:13867: de ma thag pa'i rkyen zhes bya //
NK030(a)001:13868: mgo snying yan lag lag pa gnas //
NK030(a)001:13869: khyad par can gyis nus 'jog dang //
NK030(a)001:13870: rgyun mi chad dang 'khru phyir ro //
NK030(a)001:13871: las dang nyon mongs shes bya yis //
NK030(a)001:13872: sgrib pa rim par sbyong ba'o //
NK030(a)001:13873: dbang thob tshad ni rnam pa gsum //
NK030(a)001:13874: go ma 'gag dang rgyu nas thob //
NK030(a)001:13875: mngon sum dag tu thob pa'o //
NK030(a)001:13876: rang gis thob nas gzhan la bskur /
NK030(a)001:13878: de bzhin dus rig pa shar ba'o //
NK030(a)001:13879: phyi nang gsang ba mthar thugs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:13880: chos ni rim par gnyan du rung //
NK030(a)001:13881: dad brtson rtags drug ldan pa snod //
NK030(a)001:13882: bdag gzhan gnyis pa'i brtson 'grus ldan //
NK030(a)001:13883: spyod dang rig dang mnyam par ldan /
NK030(a)001:13886: lam mthar phyin dang nus pa mthar phyin snga //
NK030(a)001:13887: rig 'dzin dang ni bde gshegs so //
NK030(a)001:13888: lam lnga bsgrod pa dgos pa'o //
NK030(a)001:13889: dbang ma thob par las brtsam pas /
NK030(a)001:13892: dbang thob phan chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK030(a)001:13893: tshe ring longs spyod phun sum tshogs //
NK030(a)001:13894: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)001:13895: yon tan khyad par bsam mi khyab //
NK030(a)001:13896: dbang don go rim bstan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:13898: dang por phyag rgya mtshan ldan btsal /
NK030(a)001:13902: gu rus mdun du bzhags ste sgrib pa bral //
NK030(a)001:13903: lus sems stong pa nyid las kun tu bzang mor brlabs /
NK030(a)001:13905: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi dgod /
NK030(a)001:13906: mkha' la pam las pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i dbus su /
NK030(a)001:13907: e mthing kha 'od dang ldan pa gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:13908: slob dpon gyi bdag kun tu bzang por brlabs //
NK030(a)001:13910: yan lag bzhi la sgo ba bzhi dgod /
NK030(a)001:13911: gsang gnas su rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa bsgom /
NK030(a)001:13913: dbu brgyan cod pan gyi dbang sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13914: de nas bus thal mo sbyar la //
NK030(a)001:13915: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs /
NK030(a)001:13918: dgyes pa chen po thabs lam gyis //
NK030(a)001:13919: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol mdzod //
NK030(a)001:13922: bu khyod sgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK030(a)001:13923: rgyal ba yongs kyi sbas pa yin //
NK030(a)001:13924: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK030(a)001:13925: gtsang rme'i 'ching pa sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:13926: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK030(a)001:13927: nga'i ba ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK030(a)001:13929: / 'o dang ljib dang drang ba dang //
NK030(a)001:13930: sems chu btung bar spyod nus sam //
NK030(a)001:13932: e ma ho thabs lam ye shes phyir /
NK030(a)001:13933: bdag ni ci la yang mi nus med /
NK030(a)001:13934: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi /
NK030(a)001:13935: ci ltar bde phyir bdag la brtsol /
NK030(a)001:13936: de nas dam rdzas la 'dzem ba'i nyes dmigs bshad /
NK030(a)001:13937: de nas yol bas spyad la /
NK030(a)001:13938: yum gyis mkha' la dkyil 'khor bskyed la drang stim brtan par bya /
NK030(a)001:13941: rol pa 'dod pa'i dngos po spang bar byas la /
NK030(a)001:13942: mkha' la byang sems 'phros pa mkha'i dkyil 'khor mchod /
NK030(a)001:13943: byang chub kyi sems slar bzlog ste /
NK030(a)001:13944: mkha'i dkyil 'khor kun 'od du zhu ba dang /
NK030(a)001:13945: byang sems dang tha mi dad pa ste /
NK030(a)001:13947: lce rnam gnyis gang rung gis blangs te /
NK030(a)001:13951: bya dang byi'u'i tshul du rtse nas bstim /
NK030(a)001:13953: rdo rje sems dpa' phra mo 'ga' zhig 'phros //
NK030(a)001:13954: sgo gsum gyis sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK030(a)001:13956: slob ma'i sgo gsum du ye shes sems dpa' gsal bar bsam pa las /
NK030(a)001:13957: shes pa h+aum ring po las lhar bskyed de /
NK030(a)001:13959: de ltar gsal ba la dbang sbyin //
NK030(a)001:13960: bde ba chos kyi sku zhes bshad //
NK030(a)001:13961: gnyer la gtad pa sgyu 'phrul dang mthun par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:13964: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang la gsum ste /
NK030(a)001:13968: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gnyis ka'i lhan thabs so //
NK030(a)001:13970: gong ltar shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi ngo bo dang /
NK030(a)001:13971: rgyu rkyen dang bskur gnas dang //
NK030(a)001:13975: chos gang nyan bar dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:13978: dbang thob ba'i dgos ched dang //
NK030(a)001:13979: dbang ma thob ba'i skyon dang //
NK030(a)001:13980: dbang thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK030(a)001:13981: bcu gsum po legs par bshad la ngo sprad do /
NK030(a)001:13983: las kyi mu tra mtshan ldan rnyed nas /
NK030(a)001:13986: de nas phyi'i dbang rnams bskur la lha sgom du bzhugs /
NK030(a)001:13989: 'dod pa'i bstan chos rnams rim par bslabs /
NK030(a)001:13990: rang gi bde ba dbab pa'i thabs /
NK030(a)001:13992: rtsa rlung thig le bsgoms ba'i thabs /
NK030(a)001:13993: gang bde ba rnams bslabs la /
NK030(a)001:13994: bde ba dang ldan nas sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK030(a)001:13997: nye shing khu ba btung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:13999: lus gu gum dang dri zhim pos byug la khrus gsum byas nas //
NK030(a)001:14000: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan du rung /
NK030(a)001:14001: de nas brgyan gyis brgyan la /
NK030(a)001:14003: gu rus mdun du bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:14004: lus sems stong pa nyid la kun tu bzang mor brlabs /
NK030(a)001:14006: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi dgod //
NK030(a)001:14008: pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i ze 'bru e mthing ka me 'od dang ldan par brlabs /
NK030(a)001:14009: bu rdo rje sems dpar bsgom la //
NK030(a)001:14010: rigs lnga dang sgo ba bzhi bsgom //
NK030(a)001:14011: gsang bar h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lngar
NK030(a)001:14012: bsgom pa'i rwa lnga la yab kyi 'bru lnga dang
NK030(a)001:14013: // dbus kyi rtsa gsum 'bru gsum bkod //
NK030(a)001:14015: de nas bus thal mo sbyar la //
NK030(a)001:14016: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs /
NK030(a)001:14019: dgyees pa chen bo thabs lam gyis //
NK030(a)001:14020: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol gcig /
NK030(a)001:14022: bu khyod sgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK030(a)001:14023: rgyal ba yongs kyi sbas pa yin //
NK030(a)001:14024: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru //
NK030(a)001:14025: gtsang rme 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:14026: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK030(a)001:14027: nga'i ba ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK030(a)001:14029: / 'o dang gzhib dang drang ba dang //
NK030(a)001:14030: sems chu btung par spyod nus sam //
NK030(a)001:14034: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med //
NK030(a)001:14035: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyis //
NK030(a)001:14036: ci ltar pad phyir bdag la rtsol //
NK030(a)001:14038: de nas dbang rdzas ma 'dzoms pa'i nyes dmigs bshad nas /
NK030(a)001:14040: de nas dri zhim po sbrang gis sbyar ba'i ril bu mur zhing /
NK030(a)001:14041: gu rus chas rnams byas zhing pad+ma lta ste /
NK030(a)001:14042: yongs su rgyas nas bde ba chen po chos kyi sku /
NK030(a)001:14043: ces pa'i tshig gis phyag rgya gtad do //
NK030(a)001:14045: thabs dang ting nge 'dzin la brten bde ba brnyed nas /
NK030(a)001:14047: de nas gnyis ka'i lag pa nas bzung la //
NK030(a)001:14048: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las /
NK030(a)001:14049: grol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK030(a)001:14050: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK030(a)001:14051: bla ma chen po'i sa gnas su //
NK030(a)001:14052: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)001:14053: spyi dpal bcu'i mnga' mnyes nas //
NK030(a)001:14054: bdal khyab chen po'i 'phrin las las /
NK030(a)001:14055: khams gsum sras su gzungs par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:14056: ces dbang phyug la gtang rag btang ngo //
NK030(a)001:14057: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bsdus pa rjogs so /
NK030(a)001:14058: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang rgyas pa ni /
NK030(a)001:14059: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)001:14060: gsang ba'i dbang thob nas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang la /
NK030(a)001:14061: gnas pa bskur ba'i las rim ni /
NK030(a)001:14062: gzungs ma mtshan ldan rnyed nas /
NK030(a)001:14063: zhi ba yi tshogs yan chad bya /
NK030(a)001:14064: de ma grub na pu tsa lnga bsham ste /
NK030(a)001:14065: skad cig las zhi dal bskyed /
NK030(a)001:14066: lha zhe gnyis kyi snying po brjod la /
NK030(a)001:14068: sa man dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK030(a)001:14070: dzahh+aum bam hohganyisa su med par bstim la //
NK030(a)001:14072: pu tsa rab tu dga' yan chad 'bul /
NK030(a)001:14073: de nas gzungs ma khrus byas te /
NK030(a)001:14074: rgyan gyis brgyan te gu ru la 'bul lo //
NK030(a)001:14075: gu rus gsang dbang gi yum dang /
NK030(a)001:14077: de nas gzungs ma dang sbyor ba byas te //
NK030(a)001:14078: gzungs ma'i don dam pa'i lte ba na //
NK030(a)001:14079: zla ba tshes pa lta bu'i nang na byang chub
NK030(a)001:14080: kyi sems thig le dkar po yungs dkar tsam zhig
NK030(a)001:14081: rang bzhin gyi gnas pa la //
NK030(a)001:14083: gsang ba'i rdo rje ye shes kyi ro can dang ba ga'i thig le dang reg pa bcings te /
NK030(a)001:14084: yab kyi lhag pa'i b+ho de thig le mkha' la gnas pa de la spro'o //
NK030(a)001:14085: de nas gu ru bab la pad+ma'i khyim nas b+hoo
NK030(a)001:14086: de yod pa thebs srin gyis blangs la gzungs ma'i
NK030(a)001:14087: lce thog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:14089: bu'i gung mos g.yas pa dang //
NK030(a)001:14090: gzungs ma'i gung mo g.yon pa //
NK030(a)001:14092: de'i mdo nas gu rus bzungs te //
NK030(a)001:14093: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK030(a)001:14094: shes rab thabs kyi rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:14096: / 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK030(a)001:14097: dngos grub gter bas 'di ma sbongs //
NK030(a)001:14098: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)001:14099: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod la 'byung //
NK030(a)001:14100: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal //
NK030(a)001:14101: sku gsung thugs dang bsgom pa ma shes na //
NK030(a)001:14102: rdo rje skal pa mtha' 'das par //
NK030(a)001:14103: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK030(a)001:14104: de'i don rgyas par bshad do //
NK030(a)001:14105: de nas gzungs ma phyi log la btang la /
NK030(a)001:14106: bu la dga' bzhi'i gdam ngag 'bog ste /
NK030(a)001:14110: dang po phyi'i bzhi thog mar gzungs ma mthong bas bde ba g.yo ba dga' ba /
NK030(a)001:14111: de nas gu rus gzung ma byin gyis brlabs pa dang srin lag sbrel ba la sogs byas pas /
NK030(a)001:14112: bde ba skye ba mchog daga'o /
NK030(a)001:14114: / 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi chad 'byed pa ni dga' bral lo //
NK030(a)001:14115: gzungs ma dang rang lus dngul zhing //
NK030(a)001:14116: bem gyi song ba ni lhan gcig skyes daga'o //
NK030(a)001:14117: nang gi dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK030(a)001:14118: rang rang gzungs ma gnyis ka la 'khor lo bzhi bsgom ste /
NK030(a)001:14119: bde ba chen po tsakra ni dga' ba /
NK030(a)001:14120: longs spyod kyi tsakra ni mchog dga' 'o //
NK030(a)001:14121: d+har ma tsakra ni dga' bral sprul pa'i tsakra ni lhan gcig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)001:14123: g+h+ya h+ya badz+ra'i rtsa ba ni dga' ba //
NK030(a)001:14124: rdo rje'i sked pa mchog dga' /
NK030(a)001:14126: / rdo rje'i bum pa ni dga' bral //
NK030(a)001:14127: rdo rje'i rtse mo ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)001:14128: de rnams re re la'ang thig le bzhi bzhi rtsis pas bcu drug ste /
NK030(a)001:14131: bcu gsang ba'i sa bcur shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:14132: de nas bu'i rdo rje la h+aum gcig bkod de
NK030(a)001:14133: spro bsdus la rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu
NK030(a)001:14136: rtse mo'i bu gar phata nag po gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:14137: de la spro bsdu byas pas pad+ma 'dab bzhi pa /
NK030(a)001:14138: de'i dbus su e mthing ka gru gsum pa /
NK030(a)001:14139: de'i steng du h+aum dmar po bsgom //
NK030(a)001:14140: de nas gzungs ma la 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi chas rnams bya /
NK030(a)001:14141: tha ma pad+ma rgyas pa dang /
NK030(a)001:14142: gzungs ma bos la rdo rje phyed tsam pad mar bu sbyor bcug la bltas te /
NK030(a)001:14144: sra ba myong pas sa'i rlung //
NK030(a)001:14145: cung zad gsher ba chu'i rlung //
NK030(a)001:14146: cung zad dro ba me'i rlung /
NK030(a)001:14147: de nas shes pa zhi ba du btags pas /
NK030(a)001:14148: bde ba g.yo ba rlung gi rlung /
NK030(a)001:14149: de nas bde ba bzlog ste /
NK030(a)001:14152: phyag rgya mas bzlog pa dang gsum las /
NK030(a)001:14153: dang po ni bde ba g.yo ba tsam na rdo rje en tsam gcig pha tshad du phyung la /
NK030(a)001:14154: lto ba sgal tshig la sbyar /
NK030(a)001:14158: bde ba g.yo tsam na stod kyi sbug sdom la /
NK030(a)001:14159: ro rkyang gnyis kyi rtsa sna /
NK030(a)001:14160: dbus kyi ku d+har 'brel ba yod pa'i ro rkyang nas dbugs bzhugs pa yis /
NK030(a)001:14161: kun d+har gyi lhag pa'i ngo bo de /
NK030(a)001:14162: gyen la sne 'khyil gyi bzlog nas //
NK030(a)001:14163: dkar chil gyis log par bsam mo //
NK030(a)001:14165: rdo rje'i rtsa na phar sor mo gnyis kyis thub tshad mnan pas bzlog /
NK030(a)001:14166: sprul ba'i 'khor lo nas gyen la de ltar bzlog go /
NK030(a)001:14167: rdo rje rtsa ba nas dang /
