NK030(a)001:15661: slob ma rang rang gi snying gi pad+ma lnga pa'i a la phog pas /
NK030(a)001:15662: lus 'od kyis gang ba de sngar bas kyang shin tu gsal bar sgom du gzhugs cing /
NK030(a)001:15663: bla mas bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pas dbang bstan par byed pa 'gre /
NK030(a)001:15664: rjes shes lus 'od shin tu gsal ba la shes
NK030(a)001:15665: pa gtad nas gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas
NK030(a)001:15666: par bya'o // drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:15667: rma bya dug gis 'tsho ba lta bu zhes pas //
NK030(a)001:15668: rma byas dug zos pas slar gyi lang 'tsho rgyas pa bzhin /
NK030(a)001:15669: dug lnga rang grol gyi man ngag gis rig pa
NK030(a)001:15670: rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i stobs kyis nyon mongs pa'i
NK030(a)001:15671: rang ngo ye shes su gsal ba mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15673: seng ge 'gying ba lta bu zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:15674: nyon mongs lnga nyid ye shes lnga ru gsal zhes so //
NK030(a)001:15675: brgyad pa gdams ngag gi dgongs 'brel ni /
NK030(a)001:15676: nyon mongs gang rung skyes pa'i dus su /
NK030(a)001:15677: dper na sgras sgra gcod pa dang 'dra ste //
NK030(a)001:15678: nyon mongs pa de nyid kyis nyon mongs pa gnas zhi sde zil gyis mnan te /
NK030(a)001:15679: nyon mongs bas de nyid la thabs gnyis kyis gnas par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:15680: dbang po rtul po lha ru gsal bar gnas pa dang /
NK030(a)001:15681: rnon po ye shes sam chos nyid du gsal bar byas la /
NK030(a)001:15682: btsal ba med ba'i tshul du gnas par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:15684: mdog ma bsgyur bar rang sar grol ba'o //
NK030(a)001:15685: de'i phyir nyon mongs pa thams cad ye shes su gsal bas /
NK030(a)001:15686: dper na rma bya dug gi 'tsho ba bzhin te /
NK030(a)001:15687: de nyid kho na bdun rtsi'i sman du gyur pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15688: ye shes lnga ru gsal ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:15689: rnam rtog ye shes su gsal bas shin tu rnal
NK030(a)001:15690: 'byor la gnas pa rnams kyis nyon mongs pa mi
NK030(a)001:15691: spong zhes bya'o // de yang rdo rje brtsegs pa las //
NK030(a)001:15692: rnam rtog ye shes ngang du gsal //
NK030(a)001:15693: des na ma sbangs rang zhir zhog /
NK030(a)001:15695: dgu pa glu ni rmad 'byung gi dgongs pa 'byung lnga ye shes kyi klong rdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:15696: dmar rengs dang po shar tsam na //
NK030(a)001:15697: rgya bo'i 'grams du khyi'i rgyal po phyi ma 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:15698: h+aum chos nyid byang chub sems ni 'byung ba lnga yin te /
NK030(a)001:15699: ma bcos rang bzhin gsal bas mkha' ltar gnas /
NK030(a)001:15701: / 'gro ba'i gzung 'dzin sreg pas me ltar gnas //
NK030(a)001:15702: dmigs med gdod nas dag pa rlung ltar gnas //
NK030(a)001:15703: gzung 'dzin skyon dang bral bas chu ltar gnas //
NK030(a)001:15704: cis kyang skyon med sra bas sa ltar gnas /
NK030(a)001:15706: / 'byung pa lnga nyid ye nas chos nyid byang chub sems /
NK030(a)001:15707: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha' 'dra ba la //
NK030(a)001:15708: dmigs pa med par ma yengs gnas pa las //
NK030(a)001:15709: sgom pa 'di la med par rtogs //
NK030(a)001:15711: dbye ba med ba'i sa la mchi //
NK030(a)001:15712: g+hi ta ma ko la sa a ho /
NK030(a)001:15713: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:15714: yid bzhin nor bu dang rjes su 'brel ba dbang brgyad pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:15716: 'khor ba dong sprugs kyis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang
NK030(a)001:15717: bskur ba dpa' bo g.yul du 'jug pa lta bu'o
NK030(a)001:15718: // gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:15719: bde ba chen po rtogs pas khyad par 'phags pa'i gdeng /
NK030(a)001:15720: nyi zla dus gcig shar ba lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15721: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15722: mi 'gyur thabs mkhas kyi spyod pa phyogs rigs med pa ste /
NK030(a)001:15723: gar mkhan gyis 'du byed lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15725: lnga pa 'khor ba dong sprugs kyi man ngag gi rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:15729: bla ma'i tsit+ta pad+ma drug pa la gnas pa'i a 'od du zhu /
NK030(a)001:15730: 'od de rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor gyis pad 'dab drug pa'i a la phog /
NK030(a)001:15732: steng gi bum pa'i a la phog /
NK030(a)001:15733: a zhu ba'i 'od dkar nar gyi byung nas //
NK030(a)001:15734: slob ma rang rang gi snying pad 'dab drug pa'i a la phog pas /
NK030(a)001:15736: lus gang ba sngar bas cher song ba la sems gtad la bsgom du gzhugs cing //
NK030(a)001:15737: bla mas bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa dbang bstan par byed pa 'gre /
NK030(a)001:15738: rjes lus 'od kyi gang ba sngar bas cher 'phel
NK030(a)001:15739: ba la shes pa gtad la gnas pa med pa'i
NK030(a)001:15741: drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:15742: dpa' bo g.yul du 'jug pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15744: dpa' bo go mtshon dang ldan pas gzhan gyis g.yul
NK030(a)001:15745: bzlog bar byed bzhin 'khor ba dong sprugs kyi man
NK030(a)001:15746: ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pa'i stobs
NK030(a)001:15747: kyis 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog so zhes mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15749: mkha' lding chen po zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:15750: 'khor ba ma rtsal ye nas sangs rgyas yin //
NK030(a)001:15752: brgyad pa gdams ngag gi dgongs 'brel bshad pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15753: khams gsum 'khor ba 'di nyid ye shes chen po
NK030(a)001:15754: skyong ba'i thabs su gyur pas khams gsum sku gsung
NK030(a)001:15756: de'i phyir 'khor ba dong sprugs shes bya te /
NK030(a)001:15758: / 'khor ba nyid bde gnas su rtogs pas /
NK030(a)001:15759: de phyir bdag gzhan du snang ba la ma dmigs pas de la gnas bar bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15760: ye nas sangs rgyas yin zhes bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:15761: mnyam bzhag gi dus su rtog pa ci 'gyur ba ye shes su gsal bas /
NK030(a)001:15762: dpa' bo g.yul du zhugs pas nyams nga ba med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK030(a)001:15763: de phyir 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15764: de yang ra hu la chen pos 'khor ba ma spangs ngang gis gsal ba la /
NK030(a)001:15765: ye shes nyi ma de nyid tshul du 'char //
NK030(a)001:15768: yid bzhin nor bu'i dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:15769: dur khrod klong rdol glu'i bsam gtan //
NK030(a)001:15770: dmar rengs gnyis pa shar tsam na //
NK030(a)001:15771: gnod sbyin mo byang chub 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:15772: h+aum chos nyid byang chub sems la blang zhing lta med de //
NK030(a)001:15773: lta ba'i gzugs med yongs la snang //
NK030(a)001:15774: cis kyang bcos su med do spyad du med //
NK030(a)001:15775: sems kyi rang bzhin ci la'ang mi gnas te //
NK030(a)001:15776: rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin te //
NK030(a)001:15777: ji ltar slad kyang dbyings la 'gyur ba med //
NK030(a)001:15778: dbyings nyid rig pas mi rtsal te //
NK030(a)001:15779: sems nyid mkha' ltar dag pa te //
NK030(a)001:15780: ma bcos rang bzhin med pa las //
NK030(a)001:15781: sgom pa 'di las med par bdag gis rtogs //
NK030(a)001:15782: bdag gi phung po brdos bcas 'di brnyil nas //
NK030(a)001:15783: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la shar /
NK030(a)001:15784: g+hi ta ma ko la sa la ho /
NK030(a)001:15785: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:15786: rtse mo byung rgyal dang rjes su 'brel ba /
NK030(a)001:15787: dbang dgu pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:15789: ye shes gsal ba'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal
NK030(a)001:15790: gyi dbang bskur ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor chen po
NK030(a)001:15791: lta bu'o // gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:15792: snang srid thams cad nam mkhar gcig pas /
NK030(a)001:15793: re dogs thams cad med pa'i gdeng ni /
NK030(a)001:15794: sa thob pa lta bu thob bo //
NK030(a)001:15795: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15796: thig le chen po'i spyod pa gcig las ma 'das ste /
NK030(a)001:15799: lnga pa ye shes gsal ba'i man ngag gis dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:15802: tsit+ta pad+ma a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:15803: bla ma'i tsit+ta pad 'dab bdun pa la gnas pa'i a dang /
NK030(a)001:15804: dkyil 'khor pad 'dab bdun pa la gnas pa'i a
NK030(a)001:15805: 'od du zhu ba la sogs pa a bzhi bskor
NK030(a)001:15807: khyad par gyis dmigs pa lus 'od kyi gang ba
NK030(a)001:15808: je cher song ba la dmigs pa gtad la sgom
NK030(a)001:15809: du bzhugs cing / bla mas bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pas brtan par byed pa 'gree /
NK030(a)001:15810: rjes shes lus 'od chen 'phel ba la shes pa
NK030(a)001:15811: gtad nas gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi gnas pa
NK030(a)001:15812: kun la 'agree'o // drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:15813: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor chen po lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15814: zhes pas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor chen po la gsal 'grib med pa bzhin /
NK030(a)001:15815: ye shes gsal ba'i man ngag gis /
NK030(a)001:15816: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pa'i stobs kyis /
NK030(a)001:15817: ting nge 'dzin bying rgod dang bral bas gsal 'grib med par mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15819: ye shes phreng ba zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:15820: snang srid ye shes ngang du gsal //
NK030(a)001:15822: brgyad pa man ngag gi dgongs 'grel ni /
NK030(a)001:15824: / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK030(a)001:15825: cad ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas bas
NK030(a)001:15826: sangs rgyas nyid las zhan pa ngang gi med /
NK030(a)001:15827: 'khor ba ka nas dag pas thams cad ye shes
NK030(a)001:15828: gsal bar khong du chud pas sangs rgyas dgongs pa'i
NK030(a)001:15829: zhe phugs rtogs pa zhes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15830: de'i phyir na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo 'char ba dang mtshung so //
NK030(a)001:15831: ngang du gsal zhes pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15832: nyi ma dang 'od dbyer med pa dang 'dra ste /
NK030(a)001:15833: mi rtogs pa dang rtogs pa /
NK030(a)001:15834: dbyer med du 'dres zer ba'am 'dug go rtogs pas dag go /
NK030(a)001:15835: de'i phyir gsal la rtog pa med pa zhes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15836: de yang gu ru chen pos /
NK030(a)001:15837: thams cad ye shes gsal ba'i brgyan /
NK030(a)001:15838: de ltar rtogs pas dag pa yin /
NK030(a)001:15841: rtse mo byung rgyal gyi dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:15842: rtsal med klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan //
NK030(a)001:15843: shing nal byi sa la'i rtsar //
NK030(a)001:15844: dmar rengs gsum pa shar tsam na //
NK030(a)001:15845: smad 'tshong ma bud d+has 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:15846: e ma ho chos nyid byang chub sems //
NK030(a)001:15847: rtag du med do spyad du med //
NK030(a)001:15848: rtsal zhing gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK030(a)001:15849: sems las sangs rgyas logs na med //
NK030(a)001:15850: brtsal bas mi rnyed sems las sangs rgyas med //
NK030(a)001:15851: sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos sangs rgyas yin //
NK030(a)001:15852: gdod nas ma brtsal byang chub snying po la //
NK030(a)001:15853: ting 'dzin ma slad ngang gis gsal ba las //
NK030(a)001:15854: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di las med par khums //
NK030(a)001:15855: bdag gi phung po brdos bcas 'di brnyil nas //
NK030(a)001:15856: kun bzang thugs kyi 'od der bdag la shar //
NK030(a)001:15857: g+hi ta ma ko la sa a ho /
NK030(a)001:15858: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:15859: spyi gcod dang rjes su 'brel ba dbang bcu pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:15861: bde ba chen pos rig pa rtsal gyis dbang bskur ba lha'i bdud rtsi 'tsho ba lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15862: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:15863: rig pa phyogs bral rtogs pas gol sgrib kyi g.yang sa med pa'i gdeng /
NK030(a)001:15864: 'phrul gyi skyes bu bgrod ba lta bu thob bo //
NK030(a)001:15865: gsum pa gdeng lam du slong ba'i sbyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15866: dbye ba med par kun la spyod pa ste //
NK030(a)001:15867: kun tu rgyu 'jigs pa med pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15869: lnga pa bde ba chen po rig pa rtsal gyis dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:15873: pad 'dab brgyad pa'i a bzhis bskor gyi dmigs pa 'gree /
NK030(a)001:15874: bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)001:15876: rtogs pa ye shes su rgyas pa'i ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15877: drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:15878: lha'i bdud rtsis 'tsho ba lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15880: lha lus zag pa dang bral zhing bde nyams dang ldan pa de bzhin du //
NK030(a)001:15881: rtog pa ye shes su rgyas pa mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15883: sems kyi 'khor lo zhes bya ba'i man ngag las //
NK030(a)001:15884: sems kyi nyams myong bde chen gsal //
NK030(a)001:15886: brgyad pa man ngag gi dgongs 'grel ni /
NK030(a)001:15887: snang srid thams cad ye shes su gsal la /
NK030(a)001:15888: sems bde ba chen por gsal bas /
NK030(a)001:15889: de bzhin du nyams su myong ba dang 'dra bas /
NK030(a)001:15890: gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen po /
NK030(a)001:15892: ma slad par nyams su myong ba'o //
NK030(a)001:15893: des na lha'i lus bdud rtsi rgyas pas bde dang ldan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15895: bying rgod bde chen du gsal ba'o //
NK030(a)001:15896: des na bying rgod mi bcos par yan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15898: thams cad bde ba chen po las ma g.yos par rtogs pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15899: de yang lung phyi ma las /
NK030(a)001:15900: nyams su myong ba'i bde chen ni //
NK030(a)001:15901: thams cad gsal bas zhe phugs nyid //
NK030(a)001:15905: gsang ba klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:15906: shing n+ya gro d+ha'i rtsar srod thun la /
NK030(a)001:15907: 'jam dpal bshes gnyer phyi ma 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:15909: kun gzhi yangs pa'i dbye thang la //
NK030(a)001:15910: dag pa'i klong nas nyi ma shar //
NK030(a)001:15911: shar ba'i dus na nub pa med //
NK030(a)001:15912: shar nas ma bcos gsal ba las //
NK030(a)001:15913: sangs rgyas chos nyid snga phyi gsum //
NK030(a)001:15914: gang du btsal yang brnyed mtha' med //
NK030(a)001:15915: kun gzhi yangs pa'i chos nyid la //
NK030(a)001:15916: rig pa sems kyi nyi shar ba //
NK030(a)001:15917: ma bcos nub pa med pa las //
NK030(a)001:15918: sgom du 'di las med par khums //
NK030(a)001:15919: mya ngan sems kyi bdud rtsi myong //
NK030(a)001:15920: lta na rig ba'i ye shes ltos //
NK030(a)001:15921: pad ma ko la sha a ho //
NK030(a)001:15922: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:15923: spyi bcings dang rjes su 'brel pa dbang bcu gcig pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:15925: sems kyi na da'i man ngag gis /
NK030(a)001:15926: rig pa rtsal gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:15927: drang srong rlung nad can sman pa'i ngag nyan pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15928: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:15929: sna tshogs skye med du 'gyur la //
NK030(a)001:15930: de las mi 'gyur ba rtogs pas //
NK030(a)001:15931: nyon mongs pa mi spongs ba'i gdeng mgron po 'khrul pa spong ba lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15932: gsum pa gdeng de lam slang pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15934: sna tshogs kyi spyod pas sna tshogs gcig tu mdzad pa de lan tsh+aa'i rgya mtsho lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15936: lnga pa sems gyi na da'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:15940: pad 'dab dgu pa'i a 'od du zhu ba'i dmigs
NK030(a)001:15941: pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing bum dbang smon lam dang
NK030(a)001:15942: bcas pa 'gree / rjes shes rtog pa ye shes
NK030(a)001:15943: gyi dbang du 'dus pa'i ngang la gnas pa med
NK030(a)001:15944: pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:15945: drug pa des ni drang srong rlung nad can sman pa'i gnyan pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15946: zhes pas rlung nad can sman pa mkhas pa'i ngag nyan pas 'bad med du grol ba bzhin /
NK030(a)001:15947: sems gyi de'i man ngag gi rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pas //
NK030(a)001:15948: dug lnga'i nad 'bad med du grol ba'o //
NK030(a)001:15951: sgron ma gsal ba zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:15952: sems nyid gyin dal rnal mar bzhag /
NK030(a)001:15955: chos thams cad sems gyin 'da' ma rtogs pa skra'i tshal pa brgyar bshag pa tsam yang med pas //
NK030(a)001:15956: gyin 'da' ma bcos rnal ma la ma slad par bzhag par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:15957: nam mkha' dang sems dang chos nyid la sbyar ro //
NK030(a)001:15958: des na drang srong rlung nad can sman pa'i ngag
NK030(a)001:15959: nyan nas lus ngag yid gsum gyi ngang gnas pa
NK030(a)001:15960: lta bu'o // rnal mar bzhag ces bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:15961: lus ngag yid gsum ma bcos par bzhag pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15962: de'i phyir na chos thams cad ma bcos pa'o //
NK030(a)001:15964: des na gyin d+har gnas par gyis shig /
NK030(a)001:15965: de yang lung gi rgyal po las /
NK030(a)001:15966: sems kyi de nyid ma bcos gsal //
NK030(a)001:15967: de ltar yin pas rtog pa med //
NK030(a)001:15971: nam mkha' klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:15972: dpag bsam shing gi grib ma la /
NK030(a)001:15974: ar+ya pa lo sa'adi skad do //
NK030(a)001:15976: byang chub sems ni nam mkha' lta bu'i klong //
NK030(a)001:15977: gsal la rtog pa med pa'i ye shes ni /
NK030(a)001:15978: phyi dang nang med kun la gsal bar snang //
NK030(a)001:15979: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha'i klong 'dra ba //
NK030(a)001:15980: rnam rtog sreg pa'i ye shes mngon shar pas //
NK030(a)001:15981: skye 'gags yangs dog rang bzhin med pa las //
NK030(a)001:15982: sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'di las med par mjal //
NK030(a)001:15983: za na sems nyid bdud rtsi zo //
NK030(a)001:15984: gon na chos nyid gos su gon //
NK030(a)001:15985: e ma ko la sha a ho /
NK030(a)001:15986: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:15987: bde ba 'phra bkod dang rjes su 'brel ba dbang bcu gnyis pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:15989: rig pa mi g.yo ba'i rig pa rtsal gyis dbang ba rgya mtsho chen po'i gting lta bu'o /
NK030(a)001:15990: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:15991: sgo gsum gyis 'khrul bas mi 'jigs pa'i gdeng /
NK030(a)001:15992: thag pa la sbrul zhen gyi zhen pa log pa lta bu thob bo //
NK030(a)001:15993: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:15994: ye shes rang shar gyis spyod pa kun tu mdzes pa ste /
NK030(a)001:15995: rin po che mgul mdzes pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:15997: lnga pa sems mi g.yo ba'i rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:15999: drag rlung bum pa can gzung /
NK030(a)001:16000: tsit+ta'i pad+ma a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:16001: pad ma bcu pa'i a 'od du zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16002: bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'dre /
NK030(a)001:16003: rjes shes bde la mi rtogs pa'i ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16005: rgya mtsho chen po lta bu zhes pas /
NK030(a)001:16006: rgya mtsho chen po kha cung zad rlung gis g.yo yang /
NK030(a)001:16007: gting g.yo ba med pa bzhin /
NK030(a)001:16008: rig pa mi g.yo ba'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pas /
NK030(a)001:16009: ting 'dzin bying rgod kyi skyon gyis mi gnod par mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16011: skyes bu khyad gyad kyi rtsal 'chang zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16012: rig pa mi g.yo rgya mtsho bzhin du gnas /
NK030(a)001:16015: chos thams cad rig pa chen por gsal bas re dog ngang gi med do //
NK030(a)001:16016: de bas na rig pa 'od gsal /
NK030(a)001:16017: bar gnas pa'i rig med nam mkha' dang 'dra ste /
NK030(a)001:16018: phyogs bcu gar yang nam mkha' las ma 'das pa dang 'dra bar /
NK030(a)001:16019: rtogs pa'i rig pa dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK030(a)001:16020: dus gsum du rig pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16021: de nyid rgya mtsho chen por gsal bas mi g.yo ba dang 'dra'o //
NK030(a)001:16024: chu phran thams cad rgya mtshor dang ro gcig bar /
NK030(a)001:16025: chos thams cad rig pa 'od gsal bar ro gcig pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16026: des ni rnam rtog thams cad ye shes su ro gcig pas mi spong ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16027: de yang rgya lung chen po las /
NK030(a)001:16028: sems nyid mi rtog nam mkha'i ngang du gsal //
NK030(a)001:16029: des na ma bcos rtogs med ngang du shar //
NK030(a)001:16032: bde ba 'phra bkod kyis dgongs pa 'phrin las klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:16035: o rgyan gyi mkhan po d+ha he 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:16036: h+aum sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa las //
NK030(a)001:16037: sems las sangs rgyas logs na med //
NK030(a)001:16038: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK030(a)001:16039: rig pa mi 'gyur rang bzhin med pa 'di //
NK030(a)001:16040: zab mo chos dbyings mi brjod don dam gsal //
NK030(a)001:16041: rgya mtsho che ltar chos dbyings zab mo las //
NK030(a)001:16042: rig pa bzod cing nang nas 'char //
NK030(a)001:16043: kun gzhi gtan nas sbyong ba'i nyi chen po //
NK030(a)001:16044: mkha' ltar dag pas yongs la khyab bar brdal /
NK030(a)001:16045: chos nyid ye nas dag pas sbyangs du med pa la /
NK030(a)001:16046: rig pa mi 'gyur gdod nas gsal bar gnas //
NK030(a)001:16047: phyin ci log gi ma slad gsal bar gnas //
NK030(a)001:16048: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa 'di las med par mjal /
NK030(a)001:16049: chos nyid nam mkha' chen po la //
NK030(a)001:16050: rnal 'byor khyung chen gshog pa lding //
NK030(a)001:16051: rkarma ko la sha a ho //
NK030(a)001:16052: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16054: rjes su 'brel pa dbang bcu gsum pa bskur thabs dgu las /
NK030(a)001:16056: sems rdzogs pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba /
NK030(a)001:16057: nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16058: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16059: snang srid ye shes su rtogs te //
NK030(a)001:16060: de nyid gdod nas bcos su med pa'i gdeng /
NK030(a)001:16061: mkha' la nyi ma shar pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16062: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16063: sgo gsum chig chod gsal ba'i spyod pa //
NK030(a)001:16064: rig pa dus gcig tu gsal ba ste /
NK030(a)001:16065: de gsum ma 'dres pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16067: lnga pa sems rdzogs pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:16069: 'jam rlung bum pa can sgom du bzhugs /
NK030(a)001:16071: pad 'dab bcu gcig pa'i a 'od du zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16072: 'khor ba ye brdal gyi dgongs pas lus kyi 'od rdzing du rdo skyur ba'i gnyer ma ltar /
NK030(a)001:16073: mched nas yul khams 'od kyis dkar mer khengs pa la rig pa gtad la /
NK030(a)001:16074: bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'gree /
NK030(a)001:16076: 'khor ba ye brdal gyi dgongs pa la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16077: drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:16078: nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16080: nor bu rin po che la ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:16081: bsod nams kyi dbang gis dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin /
NK030(a)001:16082: sems rdzogs pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi
NK030(a)001:16083: dbang thob pa'i stobs kyi 'khor ba ye brdal gyi
NK030(a)001:16084: dgongs pa las ma g.yos par dngos grub gnyis lhun
NK030(a)001:16088: lha mo nam mkha' lding zhes bya ba'i man ngag
NK030(a)001:16089: las 'khor 'das sems la rdzogs pas lhun gyis grub
NK030(a)001:16092: sems kyi de kho na nyid la snang srid 'khor
NK030(a)001:16093: 'das thams cad lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa chen
NK030(a)001:16094: po zhes bya'o // dper na ri bo lhun po'i kha ru phyin pas /
NK030(a)001:16095: gser gyi ri bdun nas phyi'i lcags ri'i bar rtsal
NK030(a)001:16096: ba med par gsal ba dang 'dra bar sems kyi
NK030(a)001:16097: de kho na nyid rtogs nas /
NK030(a)001:16098: chos thams cad rtsal ba med par rtogs pas yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:16099: dper na nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16100: des na 'dod pa thams cad 'byung ba ces bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16101: lhun gyis grub ces pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16102: bying rgod ye shes su lhun grub tu gnas pas mi 'gal ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16103: de yang klong chen 'khyil ba ces bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16104: sems las thams cad rdzogs par lhun grub ste /
NK030(a)001:16105: bcos slad dgag sgrub med pas ye shes gsal zhes pas gsal lo //
NK030(a)001:16107: srog gis 'khor lo'i dgongs par rang 'byung klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:16110: drang srong b+hi sha ti 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:16111: h+aum ma bcos ngang la gza' skar kun 'phyo bas //
NK030(a)001:16112: gdod nas dag pas mkha' ni mi brjod de //
NK030(a)001:16113: byang chub sems ni mkha' ltar dag pa la //
NK030(a)001:16114: mtshan ma'i rnam rtog sgyu mas ci slad kyang //
NK030(a)001:16115: rnam dag sems nyid dbyings la 'pho 'gyur med //
NK030(a)001:16116: chos dbyings brdal ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK030(a)001:16117: rig pa ye shes dur sa btab pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16118: gsang ba'i 'od kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar 'char //
NK030(a)001:16119: shar pa nyid kyi don de ma yengs las //
NK030(a)001:16120: sangs rgyas rnams la dgongs pa 'di las med //
NK030(a)001:16121: rig pa ye shes rlung chen gyis //
NK030(a)001:16122: rnam par rtog pa'i mun pa yengs //
NK030(a)001:16123: e ka sha ko la ma a ho /
NK030(a)001:16124: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16125: rin po che kun 'dus dang rjes su 'brel pa /
NK030(a)001:16126: dbang bcu bzhi pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:16128: gnyis med ngang gis man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba mar me'i 'od lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16129: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16130: 'bras bu dus gcig la rtogs pas //
NK030(a)001:16131: rgyu la ltos pa med pa'i gdeng //
NK030(a)001:16132: yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16133: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16134: rtogs pa rang sar sbyod pa ji ltar gnas pa ltar bde ba ste /
NK030(a)001:16135: nam mkha' la char babs pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16137: lnga pa gnyis med ngang gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:16141: pad 'dab bcu gnyis pa'i a bzhi bskor gyi dmigs pa sgoms zhing /
NK030(a)001:16142: 'khor ba ye brdal gyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16143: lus kyi 'od rdzing la rdor skyur ba ltar mchod pa de cher mched nas /
NK030(a)001:16144: 'jig rten gyi khams 'od kyis dkar mer khengs pa la sems gtad la /
NK030(a)001:16145: bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'gree /
NK030(a)001:16147: 'khor ba ye brdal gyi dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:16148: gsal la rtog med kyi ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16149: drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:16151: zhes pas mar me rang gis rang gsal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:16152: gnyis su med pa'i man ngag gis rang gsal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:16153: gnyis su med pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pa'i stobs kyis /
NK030(a)001:16154: sems nyid rang gsal rtogs pa med pa mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16156: man ngag ye shes 'khyil ba las /
NK030(a)001:16157: gnyis med ye shes ngang du ro gcig pas /
NK030(a)001:16160: chos thams cad gnyis su med par gsal ba rtog pas thag chod par byas la /
NK030(a)001:16161: de nas nyams gsum la bcos thabs dang bcas ba gnas par bya ste /
NK030(a)001:16162: gnyis med ngang las ma rtogs pa'i chos til 'bru
NK030(a)001:16163: tsam zhig ma rnyed pas gsal la rtog pa med
NK030(a)001:16164: pas / mar me rlung med pa ltar gnas par byas la /
NK030(a)001:16165: de nyid gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16166: ro gcig pas shes pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16167: bying rgod gnyis med du ro gcig pas dgag sgrub dang bral ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16168: de yang bdud rtsi 'khyil pa las /
NK030(a)001:16169: thams cad gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems /
NK030(a)001:16170: yin par bdag cag rnams kyis rtogs //
NK030(a)001:16173: rin po che kun 'dus kyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16174: skye med klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:16177: sras mo go ma di wis 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:16178: h+aum sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yi ge a yin te /
NK030(a)001:16179: a'i rang bzhin ye nas dngos po med //
NK030(a)001:16180: bde gshegs kun gyis 'byung gnas a yin te //
NK030(a)001:16181: bden gnyis la sogs snang srid cir snang yang //
NK030(a)001:16182: a'i dngos gzhi ye nas byang chub sems /
NK030(a)001:16185: smra bsam yul las 'das pa'i byang chub dbyings nyid la /
NK030(a)001:16186: a ltar skye ba med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK030(a)001:16187: ma bcos ma yengs mnyam par bzhag pa las //
NK030(a)001:16188: bdag gi sgom pa 'di las med par 'jal //
NK030(a)001:16189: chos nyid dbye thang chen po la //
NK030(a)001:16190: rig pa ye shes rta pho rgyug /
NK030(a)001:16191: ka pa la ka ma pa sha a ho /
NK030(a)001:16192: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16193: skye med rang rig dang rjes su 'brel ba /
NK030(a)001:16194: dbang bac+wa lnga pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:16196: rdo rje rang 'khrungs kyi man ngag gis rig pa brtsal gyi dbang bskur ba /
NK030(a)001:16197: chu bo chen po'i gzhung lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16198: gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16199: snang srid skye med du gsal bas 'khrul ma 'khrul
NK030(a)001:16200: blang dor med pa'i gdeng rmi lam gyi sgra snyan
NK030(a)001:16202: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16203: sgoo gsum rlung zhugs kyi spyod pa'i dam la mi 'da' ste /
NK030(a)001:16204: rin po che gser gling du phyin pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16206: lnga pa rdo rje rang 'khrungs rtag kyi man ngag
NK030(a)001:16207: gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni
NK030(a)001:16210: tsit+ta'i pad ma a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:16211: pad 'dab bcu gsum pa'i a zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16212: 'khor ba ye brdal gyis dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:16213: lus 'od shin tu cher mched pas //
NK030(a)001:16214: nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa 'od kyi rang bzhin du gyur nas /
NK030(a)001:16215: gzhan pa'i sems med par la rig pa gtad la /
NK030(a)001:16216: bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'gre /
NK030(a)001:16217: rjes kyi shes pa 'khor ba ye brdal gyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16218: gsal la rtog med kyi 'dzin pa'ang rang dag gi
NK030(a)001:16219: ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi gnas par
NK030(a)001:16220: bya'o // drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:16221: chu bo chen po'i gzhung lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16223: chu bo chen po'i gzhung la rgyun chad med pa bzhin du //
NK030(a)001:16224: rdo rje rang 'khrungs kyi man ngag gis rig pa
NK030(a)001:16225: rtsal gyis dbang thob pa'i stobs kyis gsal la rtog
NK030(a)001:16226: med kyi shes pa der 'dzin dang bral ba de
NK030(a)001:16230: thig le nyi shar zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16231: gnyis med rdo rje ye shes gsal //
NK030(a)001:16234: chos thams cad rdo rje rang 'a khrungs su sangs rgyas pas /
NK030(a)001:16235: sangs ma rgyas pa'i chos ni gcig kyang yod pa ma yin pas /
NK030(a)001:16236: thams cad rig pa'i ye shes su gsal zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:16237: des na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye shes nyi ma shar ba ces bya te /
NK030(a)001:16238: de las gzhan pa ngang gis med do //
NK030(a)001:16239: de ltar rtogs na sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16240: de bas na chu bo'i gzhung chen po mi 'gyur ba dang 'dra'o //
NK030(a)001:16241: rin chen gsal ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:16242: mnyam pa'i ngang bzang ngan kyi 'du shes dang bral ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16243: de'i phyir ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor la blo'i rig pa ma bcos par 'char de /
NK030(a)001:16245: gnyis med bde chen ngang gis gsal //
NK030(a)001:16246: de bzhin ma bcos rnal mar bzhag /
NK030(a)001:16249: skye med rang rig gi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16250: chos sku klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan //
NK030(a)001:16251: tsan dan sdong po'i rtsar gung thun la /
NK030(a)001:16252: kha che'i mkhan po rab snang 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:16253: h+aum byang chub sems ni ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK030(a)001:16254: mkha' dang 'dra ba kun la khyab par snang //
NK030(a)001:16255: snang ba nyid kyang stong pa ste //
NK030(a)001:16256: stong pa'i rdzu 'phrul cir snang la //
NK030(a)001:16257: bsam du brdul yang med pa la //
NK030(a)001:16258: brjod bral med par ma yengs zhog /
NK030(a)001:16259: chos nyid sems kyi bdud rtsi yis //
NK030(a)001:16260: khams gsum 'khor ba'i nad pa sos //
NK030(a)001:16261: ka pa la ko sha a ho //
NK030(a)001:16262: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16264: dbang bcu drug pa bskur ba la dgu las dang po dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:16265: btang snyoms chen po'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal
NK030(a)001:16266: gyis dbang bskur ba 'dun ma la mos pa'i slob
NK030(a)001:16267: ma lta bu'o // gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16268: gnyis snang gi ngo bo gnyis med du rtogs pas /
NK030(a)001:16269: gnyis 'dzin kun dang bral ba'i gdeng /
NK030(a)001:16270: rang sor gnas pa'i shes pa lta bu thob po /
NK030(a)001:16271: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16272: 'gyur ba med pa'i spyod pa rkyen gyi mi 'phrog pa ste /
NK030(a)001:16273: ma h+aa de ba'i gdeng lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16275: lnga pa btang snyoms chen po'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyis dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:16278: tsit+ta'i pad 'dab a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:16279: pad 'dab bcu bzhi pa'i a zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16280: khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dgongs pa 'jigs rten gyi khams 'od kyi khyab pa thams cad kyang /
NK030(a)001:16281: me long la has btab pa bzhin du slar 'dus
NK030(a)001:16282: na thig le chen mo'i rang bzhin gsal ba yul
NK030(a)001:16283: gyi mi 'phrogs pa la rig pa gtad la /
NK030(a)001:16284: sgo gsum khong nas klod du bcug la /
NK030(a)001:16285: dbang rten byed kyi bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa'ang 'gre /
NK030(a)001:16286: rjes kyi shes pa khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:16287: phyi rol yul gyi snang ba blo'i yul las 'das nas ji ltar snang yang /
NK030(a)001:16288: snang la ngos gzung med pa'i ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16289: drug pa dbang gi dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:16290: 'dun ma la mos pa'i skyes bu lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16292: gtso bo gzu bor gnas pa'i blo can zhal lce
NK030(a)001:16293: drang por spyod pa bzhin btang snyoms chen po'i man
NK030(a)001:16294: ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob ba'i stobs
NK030(a)001:16295: kyis rig pa 'khrul phyir du mi 'brang bar phyogs
NK030(a)001:16296: ris kyi 'dzin pa las grol lo zhes mtshon pa'o
NK030(a)001:16298: chos nyid nam mkha' ltar yangs pa //
NK030(a)001:16299: zhes bya ba'i don ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16300: blang dor med cing mnyam pa'i ngang du gsal //
NK030(a)001:16303: snang srid thams cad mnyams pa'i ngang du gsal ba /
NK030(a)001:16304: de yang rang 'byung gi ye shes lnga ru byung thems la /
NK030(a)001:16305: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsum thugs su sangs rgyas pas /
NK030(a)001:16306: sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du med do //
NK030(a)001:16307: de nas dgra zin mnyam pa'i skyes bu lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16308: ngang du gsal ces pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16309: rtog pa thams cad mnyam pa'i ngang du ro gcig
NK030(a)001:16310: pas dug lnga ma spangs bar rang sar dag go
NK030(a)001:16311: / de'i phyir mnyam pa'i ngang la blo ma bcos bar gnas so //
NK030(a)001:16312: de yang dri med bshes nyen gyi man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16313: dug lnga ye shes lnga ru gsal de ltar rtogs na rig mchog yin /
NK030(a)001:16317: sku gsum klong brdol glu'i bsam btan /
NK030(a)001:16320: rgyal bo de ba r+aa dza 'di skad do //
NK030(a)001:16321: h+aum snang srid chos rnams sngon du ltos pa rnams //
NK030(a)001:16322: yang dag nyid du 'di ltar bsgom par bya //
NK030(a)001:16323: snang srid thams cad ye shes kun tu bzang po'i ngang /
NK030(a)001:16324: 'di las gzhan med ma yengs mnyam zhag bas /
NK030(a)001:16325: sgom par bya ba 'di las med par rtogs //
NK030(a)001:16326: lus 'di sgyu ma'i phung po ming tsam te //
NK030(a)001:16327: sems ni ye shes chen por ston /
NK030(a)001:16328: tsan+t+ra de ba ko sa la a ho /
NK030(a)001:16329: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16330: nam mkha' rgyal po dang rjes su 'brel /
NK030(a)001:16331: dbang bcu bdun pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:16333: rtse gcig pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi
NK030(a)001:16334: dbang bskur ba skyes bu 'dod chags kyi gdung ba
NK030(a)001:16335: lta bu'o // gnyis pa dbang de bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16336: rang 'byung dam tshig gsal bas nyams pa'i rtogs pa
NK030(a)001:16337: mi 'jig pa'i gdeng 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK030(a)001:16338: bran gyis chad pas mi 'jigs pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16339: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16340: dmigs pa med pa'i sbyod pa gang du yang mi rtogs pa de //
NK030(a)001:16341: nam mkha' la lta ba'i skyes bu lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16343: lnga pa rtse gcig pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:16346: tsit+ta'i pad+ma a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:16347: pad+ma bac+wa lnga pa'i a zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16348: khams gsum dong sbrugs kyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16349: 'jig rten gyi khams 'od kyi khyab pa thams cad
NK030(a)001:16350: kyang me long la has btab pa bzhin du slar
NK030(a)001:16351: 'dus nas thig le chen po'i rang bzhin shin tu
NK030(a)001:16352: phra zhing gsal ba la rig pa gtad la sgo
NK030(a)001:16353: gsum khong nas klod du gzhugs /
NK030(a)001:16354: dbang brtan byed bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'gre /
NK030(a)001:16355: rjes kyi shes pa khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16356: nang yid kyi rtogs pa snga phyi blo'i yul las
NK030(a)001:16357: 'das nas ji ltar 'gyur la ngos bzung las 'das
NK030(a)001:16358: pa'i ngang las gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas
NK030(a)001:16359: par bya'o // drug pa dbang gis dpe ni /
NK030(a)001:16360: skyes bu 'dod chags kyi gdungs ba lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16361: zhes pas 'dod chags kyis gdungs pa'i skyes bu de /
NK030(a)001:16362: 'dod zhen las gzhan du mi g.yo ba bzhin sems
NK030(a)001:16363: rtse gcig pa'i man ngag gis rig pa rtsal gyi
NK030(a)001:16364: dbang thob pa'i stobs kyis blo bral gyi rig pa
NK030(a)001:16365: yul gyis phyir du mi 'brang bar mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16367: ye shes phyi mo zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16368: gang nas bltas kyang ye shes rtse gcig 'char ces so //
NK030(a)001:16370: chos thams cad kyi phyi nas bltas na nang gsal /
NK030(a)001:16371: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal bas ye shes zang thal ste /
NK030(a)001:16372: phyi nang sgo phugs med par gsal la rtog pa
NK030(a)001:16373: med par 'char ro des na gang ltar bltas kyang
NK030(a)001:16374: ye shes rtse gcig pa zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)001:16375: skyes bu 'dod pas gdungs pas sems gzhan du mi g.yo ba bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:16377: bying rgod nyid ye shes rtse gcig pa'i bskul ma yin te /
NK030(a)001:16378: shing mnan pa'i me bzhin no /
NK030(a)001:16380: / 'phags pa drang srong mig gi man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16381: g.yeng med rtse gcig bsam dang bral //
NK030(a)001:16382: des na ye shes zang thal yin //
NK030(a)001:16385: nam mkha' rgyal po'i dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16386: grol ba klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan me tog gi tshal du nam gyi cha stod la /
NK030(a)001:16388: h+aum sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas mdzod chen la /
NK030(a)001:16389: gang ltar rtogs shing ji ltar snang ba na /
NK030(a)001:16390: 'byung 'jug 'byung ba thams cad med na kun tu bzang /
NK030(a)001:16391: gnyis su med pa'i rig pa ste //
NK030(a)001:16392: kun tu bzang po'i sems la gnas //
NK030(a)001:16393: rig pa'i dbyings las ma slad pas //
NK030(a)001:16394: sgom zhing gnas pa 'di las med /
NK030(a)001:16395: kye ma ma rtogs snying re rje /
NK030(a)001:16396: bdag nyid rang sar grol ba a la la /
NK030(a)001:16397: rdo ha ko sa sha a ho /
NK030(a)001:16398: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16399: rje btsun dam pa dang rjes su 'brel pa dbang bac+wa brgyad pa bskur ba la dgu las /
NK030(a)001:16401: ma bcos lhun gyi grub pa'i man ngag gis rig
NK030(a)001:16402: pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba g.yo rgyu dang bral
NK030(a)001:16404: gnyis pa dbang bskur bas gdeng ci thob na /
NK030(a)001:16405: bdag nyid 'bras bur shar bas 'bras bu gzhan nas
NK030(a)001:16406: mi 'tshol ba'i gdeng nor bu rin po che'i gter
NK030(a)001:16407: rnyed pa lta bu'i gdeng thob bo //
NK030(a)001:16408: gsum pa gdeng de lam du slong ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16409: gnyen po med pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16410: gang ltar spyad kyang skyon gyis mi sel ba ste /
NK030(a)001:16411: 'phrul gyi skyes bu'i mdzad pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16413: lnga pa ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK030(a)001:16416: tsit+ta'i pad+ma a dang bcas pa gsal gdab /
NK030(a)001:16417: pad+ma bcu drug pa'i a 'od du zhu ba'i dmigs pa bzhi bskor bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)001:16418: khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16420: / 'jig rten gyis khams 'od kyis khyab pa thams cad kyang /
NK030(a)001:16421: me long la has btab pa bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:16422: slar 'dus nas thig le chen po'i rang bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:16423: gsal ba de thig le shin tu phra ba la
NK030(a)001:16424: 'dus nas de yang yal gyis yal pa la rig
NK030(a)001:16425: pa gtad la / cir yang yid la mi byed pa'i ngang la rang lugs su glod la /
NK030(a)001:16426: dbang rten byed bum dbang smon lam dang bcas pa 'gre /
NK030(a)001:16427: rjes kyi shes pa khams gsum dong sprugs kyi dgongs
NK030(a)001:16428: pa gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma mtha' dag bral nas
NK030(a)001:16429: / 'gag med kyi rang rtsal 'khor 'das kyi snang ba /
NK030(a)001:16432: cir shar yang ngos bzung las 'das pa'i rang rig
NK030(a)001:16433: yul med rang gsal gyi ngang la gnas pa med
NK030(a)001:16434: pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16436: g.yo sgyu dang bral ba'i mi lta bu'o //
NK030(a)001:16438: dper na mi zol med g.yo dang bral bas mi ba slu nges pa bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:16439: ma bcos lhun grub kyi man ngag gis /
NK030(a)001:16440: rig pa brtsal gyis dbang thob pa'i stobs kyi slu mi srid de /
NK030(a)001:16443: rang sar grol ba mtshon pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16445: nam mkha' sprin dang ldan pa zhes bya ba'i man ngag las /
NK030(a)001:16446: chos rnams ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang //
NK030(a)001:16447: zhes tshig phyi ma lan gsum brjod //
NK030(a)001:16448: brgyad pa gdam ngag gi dgongs 'grel bshad pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16449: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad
NK030(a)001:16450: bcos slad dang bral ba rnal la ma bcos pa
NK030(a)001:16451: blo de bzhin rnal mar ma gnas pas /
NK030(a)001:16452: chos thams cad lhun gyis grub par bstan pas gsal ba la /
NK030(a)001:16453: thams cad kyi dngos gzhi pa zhes bya'i de nyid
NK030(a)001:16454: g.yo sgyu dang bral ba'i mi ma bcos pa dang
NK030(a)001:16456: chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi ngang las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16457: des na byang chub sems kyi klong la gnas shes bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16458: de yang bsgom lung chen po las /
NK030(a)001:16459: bcos slad med par ka nas dag pa la //
NK030(a)001:16460: gnyis su 'dzin pa yongs ye ngang gis med //
NK030(a)001:16463: rje btsun dam pa'i dgongs pa /
NK030(a)001:16464: shes rab klong brdol glu'i bsam gtan /
NK030(a)001:16465: dben pa chen po'i gnas su /
NK030(a)001:16467: h+aum chos rnams ma bcos kun tu bzang po la /
NK030(a)001:16468: gsal la 'gyur ba med pa byang chub sems ngang de la //
NK030(a)001:16469: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtogs pas mi slad de /
NK030(a)001:16470: rnam rtog rang 'byung rang bzhin gnas pa las /
NK030(a)001:16471: sgom pa 'di las gud na med par 'khums //
NK030(a)001:16472: sems kyi me long ma ltas na //
NK030(a)001:16473: rnam rtog gi dri mas gos ta re /
NK030(a)001:16474: pra dz+nya ko sa la a ho //
NK030(a)001:16475: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so /
NK030(a)001:16477: / 'di lta dbang bac+wa brgyad po yang /
NK030(a)001:16478: sems 'dzin gyi dmigs pa lnga la brten nas ngo sprad pa yin te /
NK030(a)001:16480: a dkar po 'od 'phro ba la sems bzung /
NK030(a)001:16481: gnyis pa snying 'od gong bu la sems bzang ste /
NK030(a)001:16482: rlung ro bus nas 'jam rlung brtsol med du 'dzin pa yin no //
NK030(a)001:16484: lus 'od kyi gong bu la sems bzung ste /
NK030(a)001:16485: dbang gsum nas bcu gnyis kyi bar du /
NK030(a)001:16486: drag rlung bum pa can bsgom zhing //
NK030(a)001:16487: de yang dbang lnga'i bar du thun gyi ngo bo dang grangs gnyis kar 'phel /
NK030(a)001:16488: de nas dbang lnga'i bar du thun gyi ngo bo 'phel grangs 'grib po //
NK030(a)001:16489: de nas dmigs pa bzhi pa 'khor ba ye brdal la sems bzung ste /
NK030(a)001:16493: 'jam rlung bum pa can du byas la thun gyi grangs mi bzung /
NK030(a)001:16495: de nas dmigs pa lnga pa khams gsum dong sprugs la sems bzung ste /
NK030(a)001:16498: bac+wa brgyad pa gsum la 'jam rlung brtsol med thun mtshams med par nyams su blangs te /
NK030(a)001:16499: chu bo rgyun gyis rnal 'byor du bya'o //
NK030(a)001:16500: de ltar bsgom bya sgom byed bral ba'i ngang la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi gnas pas /
NK030(a)001:16501: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK030(a)001:16502: lus la gnas pa'i rtsal stong phrag bdun bcu rtsa
NK030(a)001:16503: gnyis su gnas pa'i rang bzhin gyi kun tu bzang
NK030(a)001:16504: po stong phrag bdun bcu rtsa gnyis 'dus /
NK030(a)001:16505: de yang mtshan dang dpe byad brgyad bcu rtsa gnyis
NK030(a)001:16506: kyi rang bzhin du kun tu bzang po brgyad bcu
NK030(a)001:16508: de yang ye shes kyi rtsa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK030(a)001:16509: la gnas pa'i rang bzhin gyis kun tu bzang po
NK030(a)001:16510: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la 'dus /
NK030(a)001:16511: de yang snying gi rtsa 'dab bcu drug /
NK030(a)001:16512: lte ba dang bcas pa la gnas pa'i rang bzhin gyis kun tu bzang po bac+wa brgyad du 'dus /
NK030(a)001:16513: de yang rgyu rkyen med par rang byung zhing byed pa po med par lhun gyis grub pas /
NK030(a)001:16516: kun tu bzang po zhes tha rnyad du btags te /
NK030(a)001:16517: rang 'byung ye shes thig le nyag gcig sgra ji bzhin pa min pa /
NK030(a)001:16518: don thun mong ma yin pa /
NK030(a)001:16519: dgos ched kyi dbang gi ji ltar btags kyang /
NK030(a)001:16520: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de bzhin nyid dang
NK030(a)001:16521: gzhan du brjod du med par thag chod na dbang
NK030(a)001:16522: thams cad rdzogs pa yin no //
NK030(a)001:16523: rten gyi gang zag las dang po pa rtogs pa'i ngang la /
NK030(a)001:16524: mi gnas par bying rgod kyi skyon gang byung yang bcos pa'i thabs gnyis te /
NK030(a)001:16525: seng ge sgra ltar bcos pa dang //
NK030(a)001:16526: seng pa brdal ltar bcos ba'o //
NK030(a)001:16527: seng ge'i sgra ltar bcos pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16528: gcan gzan gyi rgyal po seng ge nags na nyal ba la /
NK030(a)001:16529: gcan gzan gzhan gyis mtho mtshams par rtsoms na /
NK030(a)001:16530: seng ge rang skad ston pa tsam gyis /
NK030(a)001:16531: gcan gzan thams cad zil gyis non nas 'thab pa'i rtsol ba mi dgos pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:16532: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bac+wa brgyad gyi don dran
NK030(a)001:16533: pa tsam gyi bying rgod dbyings su yal nas thabs
NK030(a)001:16534: sam rten 'brel la rag ma lus par shes bar
NK030(a)001:16536: gnyis pa seng pa gal ltar bcos pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16537: seng pa gal la'i yan lag la mdun rgyab med cing /
NK030(a)001:16538: lus kyi mtha' yan lag gis 'khor bas /
NK030(a)001:16539: mgo 'phongs g.yas g.yon gang gis kyang 'gro shes pa bzhin //
NK030(a)001:16540: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bac+wa brgyad kyi don dran
NK030(a)001:16541: pa tsam gyis lam du ma gyur pa gang yang
NK030(a)001:16542: med de / 'gal rkyen ltar snang ba thams cad kyang /
NK030(a)001:16543: rang 'byung gi ye shes rang la rang chas su gnas pa de /
NK030(a)001:16544: rang snang ba las gzhan pa'i sems med par thag chod pas /
NK030(a)001:16545: bying rgod dbyings su yal cing /
NK030(a)001:16546: 'khrul snang rang sar grol nas 'gal rkyen grogs su 'char ro //
NK030(a)001:16547: spyi don gsum pa rjes kyi bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:16548: thog mar btang rag gtang ste /
NK030(a)001:16549: spyi'i dbang bac+wa brgya po re re'i rjes su yang /
NK030(a)001:16550: bsod nams kyi tshogs kyi don du ci 'byor ba'i yon dngos su 'bul ba'am /
NK030(a)001:16551: man+dala 'grem bsdud byas nas yid kyis lus longs spyod thams cad 'bul bar bya zhing /
NK030(a)001:16552: skabs 'dir tshogs kyi mchod pa rgya chen po bya /
NK030(a)001:16553: chos skyong la btang rag btang /
NK030(a)001:16555: bla mas 'khor gsum yangs dag gi btang rag gis mnyes par byas la /
NK030(a)001:16556: slob ma rnams kyis rtog pa 'bul zhing //
NK030(a)001:16557: de'i lan du bla mas kyang sems sde spyi'i dgongs pa //
NK030(a)001:16558: rin chen klong brdol glu'i bsam btan //
NK030(a)001:16559: sh+r+ai sing d+has bsam gtan gyi khang par //
NK030(a)001:16560: tshogs kyi mchod pa'i dus su glu blangs pa bzhin du rdo rje'i glu blangs par bya'o /
NK030(a)001:16563: h+aum ji ltar bsam kyang sgom du med //
NK030(a)001:16564: ji ltar smras kyang dpyad du med //
NK030(a)001:16565: ye shes chen po'i dbyings nyid la //
NK030(a)001:16566: btsal ba med par 'od shar ste //
NK030(a)001:16567: bsam du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK030(a)001:16568: yengs ba med par mnyam par bzhag /
NK030(a)001:16569: sgom pa 'di las med par khums //
NK030(a)001:16570: rig pa ye shes mdung rtse yi //
NK030(a)001:16571: rnam rtogs dgra bo rdul du rlog /
NK030(a)001:16572: rad na ko pa la a ho //
NK030(a)001:16573: zhes rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK030(a)001:16574: de nas bum pa dang rdul tshon rnams bsdu zhing /
NK030(a)001:16575: bum chu dang rdul tshon don du gnyer ba yod na sbyin /
NK030(a)001:16576: med na ri bo chen po'i rtse'am chu bo chen po'i rgyun la skyal bas /
NK030(a)001:16577: rlung dang chu rgyun phog pa'i sems can rnams 'bad med du grol bar bsam /
NK030(a)001:16578: bsngo ba dang smon lam rgya chen po btab la 'jug bkra shis kyi bsdu /
NK030(a)001:16579: zhag gcig gnas bsrungs pa'i cho ga bya zhing nyams dang rtog pa ci 'phel du skyang ngo //
NK030(a)001:16580: sems sde ma bu bac+wa brgyad kyis dgongs pa ngo sprad pa'i thabs /
NK030(a)001:16581: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bac+wa brgyad bskur ba'i chog sgrig 'di //
NK030(a)001:16582: snga rabs pa 'ga' zhig la phyag len cung zad mi 'dra bar snang yang /
NK030(a)001:16583: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gcig rim par ba rgyud pa'i man ngag dang /
NK030(a)001:16584: lo ts+wa ba chen po bee ro tsa na'i 'dra 'bag dang /
NK030(a)001:16585: bod kyi bla ma gong ma rnams kyis phyag bzhes kyi yi ge'i ris rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:16586: drin chen zur mo'i phyag bzhes rnams gung sgrigs nas //
NK030(a)001:16588: sems sde'i rgyud 'grel man ngag rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:16590: bya btang gi sprang po rdo rje dpal bzang pos //
NK030(a)001:16591: chu bo chen po pa shu'i g.yas 'gram chos sde'i zhes bya ba'i ri khrod du /
NK030(a)001:16592: mtshan ldan zhig po rin po che'i chos rgyud dri
NK030(a)001:16593: ma med pa 'dzin pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen ra
NK030(a)001:16594: dung brag pas sbyin bdag bgyis nas /
NK030(a)001:16596: dbyar zla tha chung kyi yar ngo la yi ger btab ba'o /
NK030(a)001:16598: / 'dis sems can dpag tu med pa rtsol bral rdzogs
NK030(a)001:16599: pa chen po'i don rtogs nas 'khrul snang rang sar
NK030(a)001:16600: grol ba'i rkyen byed par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16601: nges don mthar thug rdzogs chen gyi //
NK030(a)001:16602: snyan brgyud zhal gyi gdam ngag 'di //
NK030(a)001:16603: yi ger bkod pa mi 'os kyang //
NK030(a)001:16604: brda' don rgyud pa'i don ched du //
NK030(a)001:16605: ston pa bzhi yis rjes 'brangs nas //
NK030(a)001:16606: rig pa'i rtsal dbang bac+wa brgyad kyis //
NK030(a)001:16607: ngo sprod dbang gi phyag len 'di //
NK030(a)001:16608: lhag pa'i bsam pas ye ger bkod /
NK030(a)001:16610: / 'di la nongs pa'i tshogs mchis na //
NK030(a)001:16611: bla ma yid dam bka' bsrungs gis //
NK030(a)001:16612: rang bzhin don la dgongs mdzad nas //
NK030(a)001:16613: thugs rjes nye bar bzung par rigs /
NK030(a)001:16614: gal te bdag gis ngal ba 'dis //
NK030(a)001:16615: don yod srid na dge ba des //
NK030(a)001:16616: ma lus sems can thams cad kun //
NK030(a)001:16617: bla med byang chub thob par smon //
NK030(a)001:16618: ma bcos rang snang rol pa dang /
NK030(a)001:16619: 'khrul shes yul dang bcas pa dag //
NK030(a)001:16620: bye brag ma phyed gti mug blos //
NK030(a)001:16621: nyams la rtogs pa rloms pa dang //
NK030(a)001:16622: mkhas pa mngon pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK030(a)001:16623: nges pa'i don la skur 'debs shing //
NK030(a)001:16624: chos spong las kyi khur khur nas /
NK030(a)001:16625: mnar med gnas su snyeg pa dang //
NK030(a)001:16626: kha 'byam lta ba'i rdzong gzung nas /
NK030(a)001:16627: bslu med rgyu 'bras khyad gsod cing //
NK030(a)001:16628: bzu bor gnas pa'i blo bor nas //
NK030(a)001:16629: bdag stod gzhan la smad pa dang //
NK030(a)001:16630: mkhas pa'i bla ma ma rten cing //
NK030(a)001:16631: rnam dag gzhung lugs ma sbyangs pas //
NK030(a)001:16632: gnas lugs dri med rtogs dka' yang //
NK030(a)001:16633: mu cor smra ba'i blun po rnams //
NK030(a)001:16634: reng shig thugs rje'i yul min yang //
NK030(a)001:16635: rang 'byung rig pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:16636: rtsol bral theg pa'i snod gyur nas //
NK030(a)001:16637: yang dag don la 'jug par shog /
NK030(a)001:16638: phyogs dang dus dang gnas skabs thams cad du bkra shis bde legs kyis khyab par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16644: dngos grub blangs pa'i cho ga bzhugs soha&a&a&a //
NK030(a)001:16645: gnyis pa dngos grub len pa la gnyis te /
NK030(a)001:16646: 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub len pa dang /
NK030(a)001:16647: dam rdzas la rten nas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub len pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16649: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK030(a)001:16653: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la /
NK030(a)001:16655: thig skud rab gnas dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:16658: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)001:16659: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK030(a)001:16660: gsum pa bzhi pa phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)001:16661: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK030(a)001:16662: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)001:16663: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK030(a)001:16664: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK030(a)001:16665: cha chen gcig nas lte ba skor //
NK030(a)001:16666: cha chen gnyis nas rtsibs bzhi bskor //
NK030(a)001:16667: cha chen gsum nas rtsib bzhi bskor //
NK030(a)001:16668: cha chen bzhi nas rtsibs bcu bskor //
NK030(a)001:16669: cha chen bdun du glang gur dang rdo ra bskor /
NK030(a)001:16670: cha chen brgyad kyi phyir rol pad+ma dang /
NK030(a)001:16675: de'i rgyab tu yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK030(a)001:16676: de rgyab tu 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gru chad sgo la sogs dal spyi dang mthun par bri'o //
NK030(a)001:16677: de nas tshon rtsi rab gnas dang ldan bas /
NK030(a)001:16686: sgo la sogs dkyil 'khor spyi dang mthun par mdzes shing /
NK030(a)001:16688: de nas lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i tshom bu dang /
NK030(a)001:16689: tsa ka li rnams lha rang gnas su dgod /
NK030(a)001:16691: las bum rnams gang bder bgod /
NK030(a)001:16695: tshe chang rnams gang bder bshams /
NK030(a)001:16696: byang shar du mtshams 'dzin gyi me tog /
NK030(a)001:16703: byang du zhal zas rnams bshams /
NK030(a)001:16704: de nas shar lhor bla ma'i gtor ma /
NK030(a)001:16705: shar du yi dam tshe dpag med kyi gtor ma /
NK030(a)001:16709: byang shar du mkha' 'gro ma'i gtor ma /
NK030(a)001:16710: byang du chos skyong ma mo nub byang du mgon po /
NK030(a)001:16714: gtor ma rnams la chab dang /
NK030(a)001:16716: de nas dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs la rab gnas kyi dod du /
NK030(a)001:16719: mdun bskyed gsum gyi dang po ni /
NK030(a)001:16720: mdun gyi nam mkhar dkon mchog drug po sgom la /
NK030(a)001:16721: bdag dang 'gro ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems thams cad /
NK030(a)001:16722: dus 'di nas bzung ste byang chub ma thob kyi bar du /
NK030(a)001:16723: bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK030(a)001:16724: sangs rgyas la skyabs su chos la skyabs dge 'dun
NK030(a)001:16725: la yi dam gyi lha tshogs rnams la skyabs su
NK030(a)001:16726: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK030(a)001:16730: sems can thams cad kyi don du bdag sangs rgyas thob par bya /
NK030(a)001:16731: de'i ched du mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa'i bsgom bzlas kyi rim pa la 'jug /
NK030(a)001:16732: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16733: sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16734: sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16735: nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16736: nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:16737: de nas rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16738: swa b+ha wa shud d+ha sarba d+harma swa b+ha wa shu d+ho ham /
NK030(a)001:16739: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las /
NK030(a)001:16740: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)001:16742: nang pad+ma ra ga las grub pa gru bzhi /
NK030(a)001:16749: dril bu dang dril bu chen po'i sgra 'khrol ba /
NK030(a)001:16757: zhing khams rnam par dag pa'i dbus su /
NK030(a)001:16758: gser las grub pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi nyis rim /
NK030(a)001:16759: de'i rgyab tsakra rtsibs bcu dkar po /
NK030(a)001:16760: dbus kyi lte bar rin chen khri rma bya brgyad kyi nye bar bteg pa /
NK030(a)001:16761: dar ljang khu'i khri khebs de'i steng du pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan /
NK030(a)001:16762: rtsibs phyi nang brgyad la zla ba'i gdan /
NK030(a)001:16763: rtsib bcu la nyi ma bcu /
NK030(a)001:16764: sgo bzhi la zla ba'i gdan no /
NK030(a)001:16765: de nas brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:16766: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du /
NK030(a)001:16767: rang gi sems kyi ngo bo h+aum dmar ser /
NK030(a)001:16771: byin rlabs dngos grub nus mthu thams cad tshur 'dus h+aum la thim /
NK030(a)001:16775: bdag nyid tshe dpag tu med pa //
NK030(a)001:16776: sku mdog dmar ser zhal gcig phyag gnyis //
NK030(a)001:16778: phyag g.yas skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya thugs kar mdzad pa /
NK030(a)001:16779: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag gi steng du /
NK030(a)001:16780: gser las grub pa'i bum pa /
NK030(a)001:16781: 'chi med bdud rtsi bkang nas 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)001:16782: dar dmar po'i mgul chings dang /
NK030(a)001:16783: dpag bsam shing ljang khu'i kha brgyan can //
NK030(a)001:16784: zhabs rdo rje skyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:16785: dar ser po'i stod g.yogs kha dog lnga'i smad dkris /
NK030(a)001:16786: rin po che'i dbu brgyan dang /
NK030(a)001:16794: sku la mtshan bzang po sum bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK030(a)001:16795: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu dang ldan pa /
NK030(a)001:16797: / 'od zer stong phrag du ma dang ldan pa //
NK030(a)001:16799: yum sangs rgyas spyan ma sku mdog dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:16800: phyag g.yas pa tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)001:16801: g.yon pas tshe'i bum pa bsnam pa /
NK030(a)001:16802: de ni sku mchog nyid kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16803: de nas yab kyi thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram gyi gur khang /
NK030(a)001:16804: de'i nang du nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi gur khang /
NK030(a)001:16805: de gnyis ni thabs shes kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16806: de'i nang du 'khor lo dkar po gyis 'a khrigs pa'i gur /
NK030(a)001:16807: de'i nang du pad+ma dmar po as 'khrigs pa'i gur /
NK030(a)001:16808: de'i nang du rdo rje sngon po h+aum gis 'a khrigs pa'i gur khang /
NK030(a)001:16809: de ni sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16810: de'i nang du 'od zer dkar po gyis 'khrigs pa /
NK030(a)001:16813: dmar po am 'od zer ljang khus has 'khrigs pa'i gur khang /
NK030(a)001:16814: de ni ye shes lnga'i phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16815: de'i nang du gser las grub pa'i tsakra rtsibs brgyad
NK030(a)001:16816: pa mgo ma'i ri'u mig brgyad la gser gyi zor
NK030(a)001:16818: yu ba la yi ge tram gyis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)001:16820: de ni gser gyi zor pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16821: de'i nang pad nyi'i gdan la /
NK030(a)001:16822: hrihdamara po zung gcig 'od du zhu //
NK030(a)001:16824: dpal rta mgrin sku mdog dmar ser //
NK030(a)001:16827: phyag g.yas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:16828: g.yon pas tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:16829: zhabs gnyis rkyang brkum gyis 'gying bzhin bzhugs pa rta
NK030(a)001:16830: mgo ljang khu rngog ma leb rgan nam mkha'i dbyings
NK030(a)001:16831: su 'tsher ba // de'i pang du yum rdo rje phag mo sku mdog dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:16832: phyag g.yas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)001:16833: g.yon pa tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa yab yum gnyis ka dpal chas dang /
NK030(a)001:16834: dur khrod kyichasa kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)001:16835: 'tshams rngam gzi byin dang bcas nas bskal pa'i me dpung gi nang du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)001:16836: de ni rta mchog dbang gi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)001:16837: yab rta mgrin gyi thugs kar /
NK030(a)001:16838: bdag gi bkrag mdangs kyi ngo bo 'od phung dkar
NK030(a)001:16839: po tshon gang tsam gcig mar me rlung gi ma
NK030(a)001:16840: skyod pa lta bu gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:16841: de'i nang du rnam shes kyi ngo bo h+aum dmar ser 'bur du langs pa gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:16843: tshe'i ngo bo a dkar po gcig bsam /
NK030(a)001:16844: de'i dpung ba g.yas kyi nang du /
NK030(a)001:16845: srog gi sa bon n+ri dkar ljang re krangs kyis bsam /
NK030(a)001:16846: dpung pa g.yon du ming yig dang po krangs kyi bsam /
NK030(a)001:16847: bar du bla'i ngo bo spu dmar ser krangs kyis bsam /
NK030(a)001:16848: de rnams kyi steng du dkar po /
NK030(a)001:16853: de rnams kyi rgyab du a yu b+hi ru dz+nya na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:16854: tshe b+h+rum ni dzah pun+ye pun+ye ma h+aa pun+ye //
NK030(a)001:16855: a pa ra mi ta a yuhpun+ye dz+nya na ro pa tsit+ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)001:16858: b+h+rum ka ba tsa rak+sha rak+sha h+aum //
NK030(a)001:16860: de ni chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgya'o /
NK030(a)001:16861: gtso bo tshe dpag med yab yum gyi phyi rol
NK030(a)001:16862: du pad nyi'i gdan la rta mgrin gong du bsgom
NK030(a)001:16863: pa lta bu gshog rtse bsnol ba'i gur khang gcig
NK030(a)001:16864: sgom pa ni gtso bo yum bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16865: de'i rgyab rtsibs nang ma bzhi la //
NK030(a)001:16866: h+aum dkar ser dmar ljang bzhi las 'od zer 'phros /
NK030(a)001:16870: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK030(a)001:16871: shar du tshe'i lha mo dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:16872: phyag g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:16873: g.yon shel gyi tshe bum bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:16874: lhor tshe'i lha mor ser mo /
NK030(a)001:16876: g.yon pas bee d+aur+ya'i tshe yi bum pa bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:16877: nub du tshe'i lha mor dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:16878: g.yas pa tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu /
NK030(a)001:16879: g.yon pas byi ru'i tshe yi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)001:16880: byang du tshe'i lha mo ljang khu //
NK030(a)001:16881: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:16882: g.yon pas in+t+ra ni la'i tshe bum bsnam pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16887: ho ljang khu bzhi la 'od 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur ba las /
NK030(a)001:16888: shar du dbyings kyi lha mo dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:16889: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:16890: lhor dbyings kyi lha mo ser mo //
NK030(a)001:16891: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i zhags pa //
NK030(a)001:16892: nub du dbyings kyi lha mo dmar mo //
NK030(a)001:16893: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags sgrogs //
NK030(a)001:16894: byang du dbyings kyi lha mo ljang khu //
NK030(a)001:16895: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i dril bu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:16896: g.yon pa bzhi na tshe'i bum ba bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16898: h+aum dkar po bcu las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK030(a)001:16900: phyag g.yas pa bcu na tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:16903: spyan gsum stag sham sprul brgyan dang //
NK030(a)001:16904: rin po che rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16909: ho ljang khu bzhi las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK030(a)001:16910: shar sgor stag gdong ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)001:16911: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin ba'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:16912: lho sgor phag gdong ma ser mo //
NK030(a)001:16913: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i zhags pa //
NK030(a)001:16914: nub sgor kha gdong ma dmar mo nyi zla'i spyan can //
NK030(a)001:16916: byang sgor 'ug gdong ma ljang khu //
NK030(a)001:16918: g.yon ba bzhi na bum pa bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16919: lha mo bcu gnyis po de dag rnams ni //
NK030(a)001:16921: zhabs gnyis rkyang skum gar thabs //
NK030(a)001:16925: gzhal yas khang de'i rgyab phyi bum pa'i nang du //
NK030(a)001:16930: g.yon pa bcus lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)001:16931: spyan gsum 'jigs pa'i 'tshams rngam me ri dang bcas pa //
NK030(a)001:16932: zhal phyir gyur nas tshe'i bar chad kyi bgegs bskrad pas bsgom mo //
NK030(a)001:16933: de rnams ni 'khor lo bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)001:16934: de nas dngos grub kyi bcud bsdu ba ni //
NK030(a)001:16935: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros //
NK030(a)001:16936: rta mgrin gyi mgrin pa nas //
NK030(a)001:16937: shangs khung nas tshe dpag med kyi mgrin pa nas shangs khung nas 'phros /
NK030(a)001:16938: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten la phog /
NK030(a)001:16939: sa zhom pa yang spang sngo kad kyi gyur /
NK030(a)001:16940: r+ts+wa skam yang me tog bkra kad kyi gyur /
NK030(a)001:16941: shing skam po yang lo 'dab sngo dpar gyis gyur /
NK030(a)001:16942: chu skam po yang dkar nar gyis gyur //
NK030(a)001:16944: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad 'od zer tsha ler gyur par bsam /
NK030(a)001:16946: / 'od zer snga ma des sbrang mas sbrang rtsi bsdud pa ltar //
NK030(a)001:16947: shing dang sa chu me rlung gi snod 'byung ba
NK030(a)001:16948: chen po'i bcud bkrag mdangs rnams 'ub kyi bsdus nas
NK030(a)001:16949: / rang tshe dpag med kyi shangs khung nas rim
NK030(a)001:16950: bzhi sngar yar rgyud pa ltar brgyud nas thugs ka'i
NK030(a)001:16951: h+aum a n+ri la sogs thim pas tshe bsod nams
NK030(a)001:16952: thams cad bkrag gzi mdangs la sogs pa rgyas shing
NK030(a)001:16953: / / tshe'i dngos grub thob bar bsam la //
NK030(a)001:16954: a yu b+hi ru dza na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:16955: tshe b+h+rum n+rii dza bgrang ngo //
NK030(a)001:16956: yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer snga ma bzhin spros //
NK030(a)001:16957: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad la phog pas //
NK030(a)001:16958: sems can thams cad tshe nyams pa thams cad sor chud /
NK030(a)001:16961: mi dang mi ma yin pa /
NK030(a)001:16962: lha klu sde brgyad la sogs pa /
NK030(a)001:16963: tshe bkrag mdangs dang ldan par bsam //
NK030(a)001:16964: de nas 'od zer snga ma des //
NK030(a)001:16966: lha klu sde brgyad khyad par du yang byad ma
NK030(a)001:16967: lha dang bcas pa'i tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang
NK030(a)001:16968: 'byor pa bkrag mdangs thams cad bkug nas /
NK030(a)001:16969: rang gi shangs khungs nas yar brgyud pa bzhin bkug nas /
NK030(a)001:16970: thugs kha'i 'od phung dang h+aum a n+ri yig 'bru rnams la thim pas //
NK030(a)001:16971: tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang 'byor pa nyams pa sor chud pa dang //
NK030(a)001:16972: rtogs pa sku dang ye shes thams cad rgyas par bsam la /
NK030(a)001:16973: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:16975: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs nas chos spyod byed pa ni //
NK030(a)001:16976: lha tshogs thams cad kyi spyi bor /
NK030(a)001:16979: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad la phog /
NK030(a)001:16981: chos kyi sku rnams gzungs kyi skur bzhengs //
NK030(a)001:16982: de rnams yang tshe dpag med 'khor dang bcas par gyur nas mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK030(a)001:16983: hrih nub phyogs bde ba chen po'i pho brang nas //
NK030(a)001:16984: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:16985: tshe'i lha mo rnams kyis 'khor gyi bskor //
NK030(a)001:16986: ye shes khro bo chen po bcu //
NK030(a)001:16987: sgo ma bzhi po 'khor dang bcas //
NK030(a)001:16989: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah dzahh+aum bam hohganyisa su med par bstim /
NK030(a)001:16990: slar yang dbang gi lha tshogs rnams spyan drangs bas dbang bskur bar bsam la //
NK030(a)001:16991: h+aum bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:16992: thugs rje'i sku mchog yon tan rgya mtsho'i gter //
NK030(a)001:16993: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)001:16994: tshe'i lha mo ye shes g.yung drung dpal gyi sku //
NK030(a)001:16995: gnyis med byang chub bde mchog rol pa thabs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)001:16996: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:16997: byang chub sems rgyun ye shes bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK030(a)001:16998: skal ldan rnams la tshe'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17000: zhes byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis dbang bskur //
NK030(a)001:17001: dri ma dag chu lhag ma yar lud pas rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)001:17002: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngas byin gyis rlabs //
NK030(a)001:17003: de nas rang gis thugs ka nas h+aum dkar dmar ljang gi tshogs spros //
NK030(a)001:17004: mchod yon ma sogs la phog 'od du zhu ba las /
NK030(a)001:17005: mchod yon ma dkar mo phyag na mchod yon //
NK030(a)001:17006: bsnams pa'i tshogs dpag tu med pa spros nas //
NK030(a)001:17007: lha tshogs rnams la mchod par phul bar bsam //
NK030(a)001:17008: me tog la sogs kyang des 'gre /
NK030(a)001:17009: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17010: lha rdzas bzang po'i mchod yon rnams //
NK030(a)001:17011: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17012: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17013: bzhes na tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:17016: gtsang zhing gtsang mar spyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17017: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog rnams //
NK030(a)001:17018: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17019: tshe sring srog skyobs lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17020: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:17021: badz+ra push+pe gtsang zhing gtsang mar spyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17022: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK030(a)001:17023: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17024: tshe sring srog skyobs lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17025: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:17026: badz+ra d+hupe gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17027: lha rdzas bzang po'i snang gsal 'di //
NK030(a)001:17028: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17029: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17030: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17031: badz+ra a lo ke gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17032: lhas rdzas bzang po'i dri chab rnams //
NK030(a)001:17033: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17034: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17035: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17036: badz+ra g+han+he gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi /
NK030(a)001:17037: lha rdzas bzang po'i zhal zas rnams //
NK030(a)001:17038: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17039: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17040: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17041: badz+ra ne wi te gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17042: lha rdzas bzang po'i sgra snyan rnams //
NK030(a)001:17043: bcon ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17044: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul /
NK030(a)001:17045: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17046: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra shab+ta pu
NK030(a)001:17047: tsa me ga sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa
NK030(a)001:17048: ma ye h+aum / de nas b+h+rum las b+han d+ha'i nang du //
NK030(a)001:17050: lnga las rigs lnga yab yum bsam //
NK030(a)001:17052: zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bsam /
NK030(a)001:17053: +aahh+aum mah+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aii th+aa /
NK030(a)001:17054: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK030(a)001:17055: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yis dngos //
NK030(a)001:17056: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK030(a)001:17057: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK030(a)001:17058: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med /
NK030(a)001:17059: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bum /
NK030(a)001:17060: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17061: ma h+aa a mri ta la kha hi //
NK030(a)001:17062: gtor snod b+h+rum las b+han d+ha'i snod //
NK030(a)001:17063: bcud yig 'bru lnga la rigs lnga //
NK030(a)001:17065: gtor ma dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag bdud rtsi rgya mtsho bcud 'dod yon gyi lha mor bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17066: +aah h+aum ma h+aa b+ha ling ta te dz+wa b+ha
NK030(a)001:17067: ling ta b+ha la ling ta b+ha la b+ha ti
NK030(a)001:17068: gu h+ya sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17069: gtor snod b+han d+ha'i gzhal yas khang //
NK030(a)001:17070: bcud ni sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga //
NK030(a)001:17071: bdud rtsi 'dod yon lha mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17072: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17073: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17074: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17075: ma h+aa b+ha li ta kha hi //
NK030(a)001:17076: de nas rak+ta'a snod b+h+rum las ka p+aa la //
NK030(a)001:17077: bcud ra las rak+ta'a rgya mtsho chen por bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17078: +aah h+aum ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17079: snod ni b+han d+ha ka p+aa la //
NK030(a)001:17081: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17082: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:17083: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17084: ma h+aa rak+ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)001:17086: dri med rnam dag pad+ma ra ga'i mdog /
NK030(a)001:17087: mtshan dang dpe byad rin chen brgyan gyis spras //
NK030(a)001:17088: phyag ni skyabs sbyin bdud rtsi bum pa ba snams //
NK030(a)001:17089: tshe dpag med pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17090: theg mchog ston pa yan lag drug cu'i dbyangs /
NK030(a)001:17091: seng ge sgra yis bdud dang gshin rje'i tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17092: kun tu 'joms byed gdul bya'i tshogs skyong ba //
NK030(a)001:17093: tshe mgon rgyal ba'i gsung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17094: rnam par mi rtogs mkhyen pa nam mkha'i thugs //
NK030(a)001:17095: thugs rjes 'gro ba kun la khyab mdzad cing //
NK030(a)001:17096: dbyings dang ye shes kun tu ro gcig pa'i //
NK030(a)001:17097: ye shes lnga'i thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17098: yon tan rgya mtsho'i gting dpag mtha' yas cing //
NK030(a)001:17099: mi 'gag 'gyur med ri rab lhun po ltar //
NK030(a)001:17100: dngos grub sna tshogs rin chen gter ldan pa'i //
NK030(a)001:17101: yon tan dpag med ldan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17102: rang bzhin chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK030(a)001:17103: sna tshogs 'phrin las 'od zer rab tu 'gyed //
NK030(a)001:17104: ma rig mun sel tshe dang ye shes kyi //
NK030(a)001:17105: snang ba thams cad bskyed par mdzad la bstod //
NK030(a)001:17106: dngos su bsham dang yid kyis sprul pa yis //
NK030(a)001:17107: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhes mdzod la /
NK030(a)001:17109: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17110: yang sangs rgyas kun gyis ye shes tshe //
NK030(a)001:17111: dpag tu med pa'i 'od dang ldan /
NK030(a)001:17116: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)001:17118: phyag na shel gyi tshe bum bsnams //
NK030(a)001:17119: gsang ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17120: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)001:17122: phyag na bee d+aur+ya'i tshe bum bsnams //
NK030(a)001:17123: gsang ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17124: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)001:17126: phyag na byi ru'i tshe bum bsnams //
NK030(a)001:17127: gsang ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17128: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK030(a)001:17130: phyag na bee d+au r+ya'i tshe bum bsnams //
NK030(a)001:17131: gsang ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17132: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK030(a)001:17133: rdo rje lha mo lcags kyu ma //
NK030(a)001:17134: lha mo dkar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17135: khams gsum sgrol la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17136: rin chen dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK030(a)001:17137: rin chen lha mo zhags pa ma //
NK030(a)001:17138: lha mo ser mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17141: pad+ma'i lha mo lcags sgrogs ma //
NK030(a)001:17142: lha mo dmar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17144: las kyi dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK030(a)001:17145: las kyi lha mo dril 'khril ma //
NK030(a)001:17146: lha mo ljang mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17147: srid gsum sgrol la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17148: mi dge bcu po tshar gcod cing //
NK030(a)001:17149: phyogs skyong bcu po 'dul bar mdzad //
NK030(a)001:17150: phyogs bcu'i tshe la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK030(a)001:17151: khro bo bcu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17152: zhi rgyas dbang gis las mdzad pa //
NK030(a)001:17153: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril //
NK030(a)001:17154: phyogs bzhi tshe dbang 'gug mdzad la //
NK030(a)001:17155: sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:17156: de nas bsnyen pa'i tshe 'gug bstim byed pa ni /
NK030(a)001:17157: tshe dpag tu med pa'i lha tshogs rnams sku che
NK030(a)001:17158: ba'i yon tan mthu stobs chos kyi dbyings gyi khyab
NK030(a)001:17160: snang srid thams cad zer ma g.yel mdor bcar ba bzhin du byas pas //
NK030(a)001:17162: sa 'og sar bla gar yod kyang //
NK030(a)001:17163: sa steng du skar ma spa ba sangs thang la bud pa ltar //
NK030(a)001:17164: bkra kad kyis gyur par bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17165: h+aum spo ta bam bam bam /
NK030(a)001:17166: rdo rje nang bsdam dang bcas pas brjod //
NK030(a)001:17167: de nas rang gi thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)001:17168: lha mo dkar ser dmar ljang gi tshogs dpag tu med pa g.yas lcags kyu //
NK030(a)001:17169: g.yon bum pa bsnams pa'i tshogs spros nas //
NK030(a)001:17170: tshe'i ngo bo skar ma lta bu de rnams //
NK030(a)001:17173: lha mo dang bcas pa thugs ka thim pa tsam gyis //
NK030(a)001:17174: tshe dang bsod nams bkrag gzi mdangs mthu byin rlabs thams cad rgyas par bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17175: h+aum 'gro ba yongs gyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17176: dkar mo 'gyogs byed zhi ba'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17177: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad la //
NK030(a)001:17178: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig  /
NK030(a)001:17179: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17180: ser mo 'gyogs byed rgyas pa'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17181: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17182: rin chen tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig  /
NK030(a)001:17183: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17184: dmar mo 'gyogs byed dbang gi las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17185: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17186: pad+ma tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig  /
NK030(a)001:17187: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17188: ljang mo 'gyogs byed drag po'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17189: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17190: las kyi tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod gcig /
NK030(a)001:17191: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum //
NK030(a)001:17192: tshe b+h+rum n+ri dza brgya bzla //
NK030(a)001:17193: de nas tshe'i lha mo bzhi la tshe'i lha mo
NK030(a)001:17194: dkar ser dmar ljang gi tshogs lcags kyu dang bum
NK030(a)001:17199: byang gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i lag du tshe 'khyams pa /
NK030(a)001:17202: spas pa rnams rang dbang med par lcags kyus blangs //
NK030(a)001:17204: rang gi thugs khar thim pas //
NK030(a)001:17205: tshe bsod nams shin tu rgyas par bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17206: h+aum shar gyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17207: tshe dang ye shes 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17208: shar phyogs dri za pho mo'i lag nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17209: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17211: / 'chi med tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17212: h+aum lho'i phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17213: tshe dang gzi brjod 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17214: lho phyogs gshin rje pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17215: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17217: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17218: h+aum nub kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17219: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17220: nub phyogs klu gdon pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17221: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yod bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17223: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17224: h+aum byang gi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17225: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17226: byang phyogs gnod sbyin pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17227: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17229: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17230: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17231: tshe b+h+rum n+ri dzah brgya bzlas /
NK030(a)001:17232: de nas dbyings kyi lha mo bzhi la sprul pa gong bzhin mang du spros nas /
NK030(a)001:17237: klu mchog gtsug na rin chen gsum dang /
NK030(a)001:17238: srid pa gsum gyi gnas nas sngar bzhin tshe 'gugs bstim gyi dmigs pa byed la //
