NK030(a)001:17239: h+aum shar gyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17240: rdo rje lha mo lcags kyu ma //
NK030(a)001:17242: khams gsum gnas nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17243: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17245: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17247: rin chen lha mo zhags pa ma //
NK030(a)001:17249: dug gsum gnas nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17250: ba dag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17252: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17253: nub kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17254: pad+ma'i lha mor lcags sgrogs ma //
NK030(a)001:17256: mchog gsum gnas nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17257: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17259: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17260: byang gi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17261: las kyi lha po dril 'khrol ma //
NK030(a)001:17263: srid gsum gnas nas tshe drongs la //
NK030(a)001:17264: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17266: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17267: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17270: de nas khro bo bcu la /
NK030(a)001:17272: phyogs skyong bcu'i lag nas sngar bzhin tshe bkug la /
NK030(a)001:17274: gal te shar kyi phyogs su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17275: khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17276: dri za'i lag nas tshe khugs la //
NK030(a)001:17277: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17279: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17280: gal te shar lho'i mtshams su tshe nyams na /
NK030(a)001:17281: khro bo chen po dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK030(a)001:17282: me lha pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17283: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17284: 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol /
NK030(a)001:17285: gal te lho'i phyogs su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17286: khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po yis //
NK030(a)001:17287: gshin rje pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug nas //
NK030(a)001:17288: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17291: gal te lho nub mtshams su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17292: khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon po yis //
NK030(a)001:17293: srin po pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17294: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17296: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17297: gal te nub kyi phyogs kyi tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17298: khro bo chen po rta mgrin rgyal po yis //
NK030(a)001:17299: klu gdon pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17300: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17302: / 'chi med dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17303: gal te nub byang mtshams nas tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17304: khro bo chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NK030(a)001:17305: rlung lha pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17306: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17308: / 'chi med tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17309: gal te byang gi phyogs nas tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17310: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yis //
NK030(a)001:17311: gnod sbyin pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17312: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17314: / 'chi med tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17315: gal te byang shar mtshams su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17316: khro bo chen po khams gsum rnam rgyal gyis //
NK030(a)001:17317: dbang ldan pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17318: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon 'chi med tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17319: gal te steng gi phyogs su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17320: khro bo chen po h+aum chen ka ra yis /
NK030(a)001:17321: nyi zla pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la /
NK030(a)001:17322: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17323: 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17324: gal te 'og gi phyogs su tshe nyams na //
NK030(a)001:17325: khro bo chen po stobs po chen po yis //
NK030(a)001:17326: sa bdag pho mo'i lag gnas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17327: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17329: / 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17330: +aahyu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17332: h+aa de nas sgo ba bzhi la sprul pa mang
NK030(a)001:17333: du spros nas tshe bkug bstim byed par bsam la
NK030(a)001:17334: / h+aum shar gyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17335: rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu ma //
NK030(a)001:17336: dri za pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug shig /
NK030(a)001:17338: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17340: / 'chi med tshe yi dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:17341: lho yi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17342: phag gdong ser mo zhags pa ma //
NK030(a)001:17343: gshin rje pho mo'i lag nas tshe khugs shig /
NK030(a)001:17345: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17347: / 'chi med tshe yi dngos grub stsool //
NK030(a)001:17348: nub kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NK030(a)001:17349: kha gdong dmar mo lcags sgrogs ma /
NK030(a)001:17350: klu gdon pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17351: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yin bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17353: / 'chi med tshe yi dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17354: byang gi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma /
NK030(a)001:17356: / 'ug gdong ljang khu dril khrol ma //
NK030(a)001:17357: gnod sbyin pho mo'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK030(a)001:17358: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17360: / 'chi med tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17361: khugs shig drongs shig badz+ra g+han d+he ho //
NK030(a)001:17362: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum //
NK030(a)001:17364: zhar la khro bo nag po bcu'i 'phro 'du byed la /
NK030(a)001:17367: bsnyen pa 'di rnams la tshe khugs pa'i rtags byung na //
NK030(a)001:17368: pu n+ye ci rigs par bzla //
NK030(a)001:17369: mthar sbas sngags kyang bdun tsam bzlas de nas mchod bstod bsdus pa bya'o //
NK030(a)001:17370: spyi don gnyis pa bum bskyed ni /
NK030(a)001:17371: swa b+ha wa shud+ha bum pa mi dmigs stong ba'i ngang las //
NK030(a)001:17373: b+h+r+aum gcig spros pa 'od du zhu ba las //
NK030(a)001:17374: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)001:17377: bsnyen pa yan chod bdag bskyed dang mtshungs pa la /
NK030(a)001:17378: bar skabs kyi tshig kha bsgyur ro //
NK030(a)001:17386: bum bskyed dang mthun par bya'o //
NK030(a)001:17387: spyi don gsum pa mdun bskyed ni /
NK030(a)001:17388: swa b+ha wa rdul tshon mi dmigs pa stong pa'i ngang las /
NK030(a)001:17389: rang gi thugs kha nas b+h+r+aum gcig 'phros pa 'od du zhu //
NK030(a)001:17391: rin che po sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)001:17394: bsnyen pa yan bdag bskyed dang mtshungs pa la //
NK030(a)001:17395: bar skabs su 'dod pa kha bsgyur ro //
NK030(a)001:17396: gnyis pa 'jug gi dbang gi rim pa la gnyis ste /
NK030(a)001:17397: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK030(a)001:17398: slob ma bzhug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK030(a)001:17400: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK030(a)001:17402: slob ma dkyil 'khor bzhugs cing dbang bskur ba ltar
NK030(a)001:17403: slob dpon bdag gis kyang 'jug cing dbang len no
NK030(a)001:17404: // gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhugs cing dbang bskur ba la /
NK030(a)001:17405: khrus dag ba dri dang lus 'bul dang //
NK030(a)001:17406: bgegs bskrad lhar rlabs dam tshig spyin //
NK030(a)001:17407: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK030(a)001:17408: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK030(a)001:17409: lha dbab ba dang nan tan dang //
NK030(a)001:17410: spyan dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK030(a)001:17413: bcu drug dang po khrus ni /
NK030(a)001:17415: las bum gyis slob ma rnams bkru zhing //
NK030(a)001:17416: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyi ni sogs kyis lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig pa dag nas //
NK030(a)001:17417: lus shel gong phyis pa ltar bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:17418: gnyis pa mig dar dgab pa ni /
NK030(a)001:17419: dar dmar pos mig dgab la /
NK030(a)001:17420: de snga phan chad dkyil 'khor mi mthong ba'i barda'o //
NK030(a)001:17422: bla mas bu dga' ci la dga' /
NK030(a)001:17424: / bu khyod spro ba ci la spro //
NK030(a)001:17426: slob mas bdag ni tshe dpag med pa yi //
NK030(a)001:17427: dkyil 'khor bzhugs cing dbang zhu spro //
NK030(a)001:17430: rgyal thebs kyis slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi lho sgo'i nang phyogs su khrid de /
NK030(a)001:17431: phyag 'tshal zhing lus 'bul bar bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17432: dkyil 'khor grong khyer dam pa'i sa //
NK030(a)001:17433: lho'i phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)001:17434: sku'i dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:17436: nub sgo'i nang du khrid la //
NK030(a)001:17437: dkyil 'khor dam pa grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)001:17438: nub kyi phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)001:17439: gsung gi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:17441: byang sgo'i nang du khrid la //
NK030(a)001:17442: dkyil 'khor dam pa'i grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)001:17443: byang gi phyogs su brten nas ni /
NK030(a)001:17445: / 'phrin las dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:17448: dkyil 'khor dam pa grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)001:17449: shar gyis phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)001:17450: thugs kyi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:17452: lnga pa bgegs bskrad pa ni //
NK030(a)001:17453: slob ma la yungs dkar gtor zhing bgegs bskrad par bsam la //
NK030(a)001:17454: h+r+aiihpad+ma ta kri ta badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK030(a)001:17456: drug pa lhar brlabs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:17458: / 'od khyed rang rnams tshe dpag tu med pa //
NK030(a)001:17459: sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa re
NK030(a)001:17460: re gsal ba'i spyi bo dkar po mgrin par +aahdamara
NK030(a)001:17461: po // thugs kar h+aum sngon po re rer bsgoms
NK030(a)001:17462: gnas gsum du dri bzang gi thig le re re
NK030(a)001:17463: po // byed do // bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni //
NK030(a)001:17466: gsang sngags theg pa 'dir bzhugs na //
NK030(a)001:17467: dam med 'di phyi gnyis khar lhung //
NK030(a)001:17468: dam tshig tshul bzhin bsrungs nus sam //
NK030(a)001:17470: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK030(a)001:17471: ma grub bar du ma ltung na //
NK030(a)001:17472: yang nas yang du bcas pa bzhin //
NK030(a)001:17473: lus dang srog la babs kyang bsrungs //
NK030(a)001:17475: brgyad pa dam tshig dbog ba ni //
NK030(a)001:17476: snying khar rdo rje bzung la //
NK030(a)001:17477: dus gsum bde gshegs rnams kyi snying po ni /
NK030(a)001:17479: / 'das dang ma byung da ltar gsum gyi lha //
NK030(a)001:17480: rnal 'byor pa'i bsnyen cing bsgrub pa 'di //
NK030(a)001:17481: da lta nyid du khyod la 'bogs par bya //
NK030(a)001:17482: badz+ra sarba sa ma ya h+aum //
NK030(a)001:17483: dgu pa dam chu blud pa ni //
NK030(a)001:17484: bdud rtsi lce la bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17487: skal ldan khyod kyis gsang ba'i mchog /
NK030(a)001:17488: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i /
NK030(a)001:17489: bdag gi bka' la ma 'da' bsrungs //
NK030(a)001:17490: i tan ti na ra kan /
NK030(a)001:17491: yang de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)001:17492: gsang cher nga yin brnyas pa spongs //
NK030(a)001:17493: brnyas na sangs rgyas kun brnyas pas //
NK030(a)001:17494: tshe'i dus byas dmyal bar skye //
NK030(a)001:17496: bcu pa dam tshig bsgrag pa ni //
NK030(a)001:17497: bu khyod bla med sems kyi sangs rgyas rigs //
NK030(a)001:17498: sangs rgyas lha'i sa la gnas gyur gyi //
NK030(a)001:17499: mos pas zhugs la bla med sgrubs pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:17500: rgyal ba'i dam tshig gnyis med sems kyi spyod //
NK030(a)001:17502: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba ni //
NK030(a)001:17503: me tog cod pan thal mo'i bar du gzung la /
NK030(a)001:17506: tshe dpag med pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:17507: rin chen byang chub sems kyi me tog 'di //
NK030(a)001:17508: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyibs su bdag 'bul na //
NK030(a)001:17509: dngos grub rnam gsum bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17511: ces dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su gtad cing 'phang ngo //
NK030(a)001:17512: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab ni /
NK030(a)001:17514: me tog phog pa'i lha dbyer med gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK030(a)001:17515: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:17516: me tog dor ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:17517: sku gsung thugs la thim nas kyang /
NK030(a)001:17518: dngos grub rnams gsum khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)001:17519: ka ya wa k+ka tsit+ta sid+d+hii h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17520: bcu gsum pa lha bsgoms par nan tan bya ba ni /
NK030(a)001:17522: kye dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i gsang mtshan btags //
NK030(a)001:17523: mo thams cad kun tu bzang mo la sogs pa'i gsang mtshan btags la /
NK030(a)001:17525: / 'o khyeer rang rnams kyi me tog phog pa'i lha mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa yin pas //
NK030(a)001:17526: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku snang la rang bzhin med pa //
NK030(a)001:17527: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin du bsgom zhing bsgrub pa la nan tan mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17528: bcu bzhi pa spyan dbye ba ni //
NK030(a)001:17529: thur mas spyan dar bsal la //
NK030(a)001:17531: bu khyod kyi ni shes pa yi //
NK030(a)001:17532: ma rig mig gis ling tog rnams //
NK030(a)001:17533: bde gshegs dgongs pas gsal bar bgyi //
NK030(a)001:17535: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni //
NK030(a)001:17537: ho dkyil 'khor lha tshogs 'di la ltos //
NK030(a)001:17538: sngon chad ma brnyed de ring rnyed //
NK030(a)001:17539: sngags dang phyag rgya'i dngos grub thob //
NK030(a)001:17540: rtag tu dam tshig thub par bsrungs /
NK030(a)001:17541: 'o rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyis //
NK030(a)001:17542: skye ba bdun tshun chod du /
NK030(a)001:17543: ma bsgom kyang sangs rgyas thob pa la sogs pa phan yon du ma yod do //
NK030(a)001:17544: bcu drug pa tshogs mchod yon 'bul ba ni //
NK030(a)001:17545: tshogs mchod rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa byas shing //
NK030(a)001:17546: lha tshogs dang mi la byas shing //
NK030(a)001:17547: lha tshogs dang mi la 'bul lo //
NK030(a)001:17548: yon ni ci 'byor pa'i yon phul la //
NK030(a)001:17549: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus /
NK030(a)001:17550: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK030(a)001:17552: rtag du thugs rjes gzung du gsol /
NK030(a)001:17554: de ltar dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK030(a)001:17555: las dang po ba bzhugs yin kyang /
NK030(a)001:17557: / 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa dang bskal ba mnyams pa'i yon tan no //
NK030(a)001:17558: dbang gi dngos gzhi la gsum gyi dang po sngon 'gro ni //
NK030(a)001:17560: gsol ba gdab pa'i rjes bzlos mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17561: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17562: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas kyi /
NK030(a)001:17563: rdo rje tshe dbang rin po che //
NK030(a)001:17564: deng 'dir bdag la bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17566: de nas slob dpon gyi dbu brgyan la sogs pa'i chas gos rnams brnab /
NK030(a)001:17567: bum pa phyag tu thogs la /
NK030(a)001:17568: 'o khyed rang rnams dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod //
NK030(a)001:17569: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer spros //
NK030(a)001:17570: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgya la phog /
NK030(a)001:17571: de yang chos kyi sku rnams gzugs kyi skur bzhengs //
NK030(a)001:17572: gzugs kyi sku rnams yang mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa 'khor bcas kyi skur bzhengs nas /
NK030(a)001:17573: mdun bskyed dang gnyis su med par nam mkhar sgom la //
NK030(a)001:17574: de yang tshe dpag med la sogs rigs lngas bkra shis pa'i dgongs pa mdzad /
NK030(a)001:17575: sangs rgyas spyan ma la sogs yum lngas //
NK030(a)001:17576: rin po che'i bum pa byang chub sems kyis chus
NK030(a)001:17577: gang ba thogs nas dbang bskur tshe'i lha mo dang
NK030(a)001:17578: dbyings kyi lha mos bkra shis brjod cing glu len
NK030(a)001:17579: / khro bo bcus bar chad kyi bgegs bskrad //
NK030(a)001:17580: sgo ma bzhi phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul bar bsgom mdzod //
NK030(a)001:17581: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra //
NK030(a)001:17584: rdzogs sangs rgyas nas da lta'i bar //
NK030(a)001:17585: bum pa gcig nas gcig byo dang //
NK030(a)001:17586: mar me gcig nas gcig spar ltar //
NK030(a)001:17587: dus rgyun chad med pa'i bkra shis brjod //
NK030(a)001:17590: gsang ba'i dbang gi dod dang /
NK030(a)001:17591: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi dod dang /
NK030(a)001:17592: dbang bzhi pa tshig dbang rin po che de'i dod do //
NK030(a)001:17594: dmigs pa bsam rgyud gong bzhin la bsgrag tshig ni //
NK030(a)001:17595: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las byung //
NK030(a)001:17596: kha dog dbyibs su ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)001:17597: shes rab yum gyis bum pa 'dis //
NK030(a)001:17598: spyi bo'i gtsug tu dbang bskur ba //
NK030(a)001:17599: dbang mchog dam pa thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:17600: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17602: bum pa'i chus dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17603: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:17604: tshe dpag med yab yum gyi tsa ka li spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17605: 'o bde ba can dang mdun bskyed dang /
NK030(a)001:17606: bla ma'i thugs ka nas tshe dpag med yab yum byon nas /
NK030(a)001:17607: 'chi med tshe yi bdud rtsis bkang ba'i bum pas
NK030(a)001:17608: spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas thugs kar thim par
NK030(a)001:17609: bsgoms mdzod cig / bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)001:17610: thugs rje'i sku mchog yon tan rgya mtsho'i gter //
NK030(a)001:17611: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)001:17612: rdo rje tshe'i lha mo ye shes g.yung drung dpal gyis sku //
NK030(a)001:17613: byang chub bde mchog rol pa thabs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)001:17614: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17615: byang chub sems kyi ye shes bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK030(a)001:17616: skal ldan rnams la tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17617: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17618: tshe b+h+r+aum n+ri dzaha b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17619: gtso bo yab yum kyi sku las sprul ba'i lha mo bzhi'i sku sbyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17622: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung pa'i sprul pa'i lha
NK030(a)001:17623: mor bzhis 'chi med bdud rtsis gang pa'i bum pa
NK030(a)001:17625: lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par bsgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17626: h+aum 'gro ba yongs la tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17627: dkar mo 'gyogs byed zhi ba'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17628: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17629: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:17630: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17631: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17632: ser mo 'gyogs byed rgyas pa'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17633: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17634: rin chen tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:17635: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17636: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17637: dmar mo 'gyogs byed dbang gi las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17638: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17639: pad+ma tshe mchog thob pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:17641: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17642: ljang mo 'gyogs byed drag po'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)001:17643: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:17644: las kyi tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:17646: tshe'i lha mo bzhi'i sku spyi bor bzhags la /
NK030(a)001:17648: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung ba'i tshe'i lha mo bzhi /
NK030(a)001:17650: / 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum ba spyi bor nas dbang bskur /
NK030(a)001:17651: tshe'i lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par bsgoms mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17652: h+aum shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17654: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17656: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17657: +aahyu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17659: lho phyogs 'khor lo rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17661: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17663: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17664: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17665: h+aum nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17667: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17670: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK030(a)001:17671: h+aum byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17673: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17675: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob bar shog /
NK030(a)001:17676: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17677: dbyings kyi lha mo bzhi'i sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17681: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung ba'i dbyings kyi lha
NK030(a)001:17682: mo bzhis 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum pa
NK030(a)001:17684: dbyings kyi lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par sgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17685: h+aum rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17686: lha mo dkar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17687: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17689: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17690: +aahyu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum rin chen dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17691: lha mo ser mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17692: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17694: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17696: h+aum pad+ma dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17697: lha mo dmar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17698: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17700: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17701: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17702: h+aum las kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor nas /
NK030(a)001:17703: lha mo ljang mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)001:17704: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17706: / 'chi med rig 'dzin tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17708: khro bo bcu'i sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17711: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byon pa'i /
NK030(a)001:17712: khro bo bcu'i phyag nas 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis
NK030(a)001:17713: gang ba'i bum pa thogs nas spyi bo nas dbang
NK030(a)001:17714: bskur / khro bo bcu'i thugs kar thim par sgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17715: h+aum shar phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17716: khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17717: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17719: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17720: +aa yu b+hi ti dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17722: h+aum shar lho 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas /
NK030(a)001:17723: khro bo chen po dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK030(a)001:17724: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17726: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17728: h+aum lho phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs steng nas //
NK030(a)001:17729: khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po yis //
NK030(a)001:17730: skal ldan bu mchog rnam la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17732: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17734: h+aum lho nub 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas /
NK030(a)001:17735: khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon po yis //
NK030(a)001:17736: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17738: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17739: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17740: h+aum nub phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17741: khro bo chen po rta mgrin rgyal po yis /
NK030(a)001:17742: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17744: / 'chi ba med pa'i tshe dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17746: h+aum nub byang 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17747: khro bo chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa /
NK030(a)001:17748: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17750: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17752: h+aum byang phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17753: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17754: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17756: / 'chi ba med pa tshe yi dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17758: h+aum byang shar 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs steng nas /
NK030(a)001:17759: khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba yis //
NK030(a)001:17760: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17762: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17764: h+aum 'khor lo dkar po'i stengs phyogs nas /
NK030(a)001:17765: 'khor lo chen po h+aum chen ka ra yis //
NK030(a)001:17766: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur ba /
NK030(a)001:17768: / 'chi ba med pa tshe yis dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17769: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17770: h+aum 'khor lo dkar po'i 'og phyogs nas //
NK030(a)001:17771: khro bo chen po stobs po chen po yis //
NK030(a)001:17772: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:17773: 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)001:17774: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17775: sgo ma bzhi'i sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17778: bla ma'i thugs ka phyogs nas byon pa'i sgo ma
NK030(a)001:17779: bzhi'i phyag na 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsis dkang
NK030(a)001:17780: ba'i bum bas spyi bor nas dbang bskur //
NK030(a)001:17781: sgo ma bzhi thugs khar thim par sgoms mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17783: shar sgo zla ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17784: stag gdong dkar mo lcags kyu mas //
NK030(a)001:17785: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17787: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17788: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na tshe b+h+ru ni dzah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17789: h+aum lho sgo zla ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17790: phag gdong ser mo tshe zhags mas //
NK030(a)001:17791: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17793: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17794: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum nub sgo zla ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK030(a)001:17795: kha gdong dmar mo lcags sgrogs mas //
NK030(a)001:17796: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17798: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17799: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17800: h+aum byang sgo zla ba'i gdan stengs nas /
NK030(a)001:17803: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17805: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:17806: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17808: lam bskyed rim b+hemem pa la dbang //
NK030(a)001:17809: sprul sku'i sa bon rgyud la skye ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:17810: des bum pa'i dbang de song nas //
NK030(a)001:17811: rdo rje rtse mo'i rgyud las /
NK030(a)001:17812: ni bkra shis dpal dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:17813: dam bca' ba dang mchog gter dang /
NK030(a)001:17815: rig byed kyi gzhung las kyang /
NK030(a)001:17816: thig le a tha yi ge //
NK030(a)001:17817: yi ge gnyis po sngon tshang ba'i //
NK030(a)001:17818: khur tshos brdol las byung bas na //
NK030(a)001:17819: des na de dag bkra shis brjod /
NK030(a)001:17822: bdun rtsi lce la bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:17823: 'o khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor dkar po re re b+hee /
NK030(a)001:17828: byin gyis brlab nus mthu thams cad tshur 'dus //
NK030(a)001:17829: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bo'i la thim /
NK030(a)001:17831: / 'od du zhu ba las rnam par snang mdzad yab yum du gyur pas sku'i gsang dbang bsgom cig /
NK030(a)001:17832: spyi gtsug zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du yi ge ni rab tu bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17834: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum b+hee //
NK030(a)001:17835: de yi che ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:17836: tshe yang rab tu brtan pa dang //
NK030(a)001:17837: dbang yang rab du bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:17839: khyed rang rnams kyi mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du a dmar po re re bsgom /
NK030(a)001:17844: byin rlabs nus mthu thams cad tshur 'dus //
NK030(a)001:17845: khyed rang rnams kyi mgrin pa'i a la thim /
NK030(a)001:17847: / 'od du zhu ba las snang ba mtha' yas yab yum du gyur pas /
NK030(a)001:17848: gsung gi gsang dbang thob par bsgoms cig /
NK030(a)001:17849: lce pad+ma 'dab brgyad la yi ge a ni rab tu bsgom /
NK030(a)001:17851: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum bsgoms //
NK030(a)001:17852: de yi che ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:17853: tshe yang rab tu brtan pa dang //
NK030(a)001:17854: dbang yang rab tu bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:17855: a b+h+r+aum pad+ma a yu a /
NK030(a)001:17857: / 'o khyed rang rnams kyi thugs kar //
NK030(a)001:17858: nyi ma'i steng du h+aum sngon po re re b+hee /
NK030(a)001:17863: byin rlabs nus mthu thams cad bsdus nas khyed rang rnams kyis /
NK030(a)001:17866: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum du gyur pa las thugs kyi gsang dbang thob par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:17867: thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:17868: yi ge h+aum ni rab tu bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17870: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17871: de'i che ba'i byin rlabs gyis //
NK030(a)001:17872: tshe yang rab tu brtan pa dang //
NK030(a)001:17873: dbang yang rab du bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:17874: h+aum b+h+rum badz+ra a yu h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17875: khyed rang rnams kyi lte ba tram ser po re re bsgom de las 'od zer 'phro bas /
NK030(a)001:17879: byin rlabs nus mthu thams cad bsdus nas /
NK030(a)001:17880: khyed rang rnams kyi lte ba'i tram la thim /
NK030(a)001:17882: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum du gyur pas yon tan gyi gsang dbang thob par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:17883: lte ba rin chen zur brgyad la //
NK030(a)001:17884: yi ge tram ni rab tu bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17886: rin chen 'byung gnas yab yum bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17887: de yi che ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:17888: tshe yang rab du brtan pa dang //
NK030(a)001:17889: dbang yang rab tu bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:17894: 'o byang sems bdud rtsi'i lhag ma yar lud pa las //
NK030(a)001:17895: rna ltag g.yon du don yod grub pas dbu brgyan //
NK030(a)001:17896: de'i sku lus la ral gri'i char bab pas //
NK030(a)001:17897: lus ral gri'i go khrab dang zhu lugs su gyur par bsgoms //
NK030(a)001:17898: in tra ni la'i mdog 'dra las //
NK030(a)001:17899: g.yon du don yod grub pa ha //
NK030(a)001:17900: cis kyang mi chod mi shig pa'i //
NK030(a)001:17901: ral gri'i go cha bla na med //
NK030(a)001:17902: ral gri'i go chas bsrungs du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17903: lus la go skon sems la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:17904: bla na med par bsrungs par shog /
NK030(a)001:17905: ral gri bskor ba lta bu /
NK030(a)001:17906: phrin las kyi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:17908: / 'o khyed rang rnams kyi gsang gnas su ha ljang khu re re bsgoms /
NK030(a)001:17913: bla ma'i gsang gnas su phog /
NK030(a)001:17914: byin rlabs nus mthu thams cad bsdus nas //
NK030(a)001:17915: khyed rang rnams kyi gsang gnas kyi ha la thim /
NK030(a)001:17918: don yod grub pa yab yum du gyur pas /
NK030(a)001:17920: / 'phrin las kyi gsang dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:17921: gsang gnas rgya gram dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:17922: yi ge ha ni rab tu bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17924: don yod grub pa yab yum bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17925: de'i che ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:17926: tshe yang rab tu brtan pa dang //
NK030(a)001:17927: dbang yang rab tu bskur bar bya //
NK030(a)001:17928: ha b+h+r+aum kar ma a yu ha /
NK030(a)001:17929: de nas gsang ba'i dbang thob //
NK030(a)001:17931: mthar thug longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob //
NK030(a)001:17932: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK030(a)001:17933: 'o khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor rnam par snang
NK030(a)001:17934: mdzad yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems
NK030(a)001:17935: kyi bdud rtsis lus phyi nang gi sdig pa dag
NK030(a)001:17936: / lus kyi phyi nang 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis gang la /
NK030(a)001:17937: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad du /
NK030(a)001:17938: 'khor lo zil pa phrom gyis gyur par bsgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17939: spyi gtsug zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:17940: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK030(a)001:17941: kun tu bzang mo gnyis med 'khril //
NK030(a)001:17942: gnyis med thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17943: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la /
NK030(a)001:17948: 'o byang chub bdud rtsi'i chu yar lud pa las /
NK030(a)001:17949: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor /
NK030(a)001:17950: rnam par snang mdzad kyi dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)001:17951: de'i sku lus las 'khor lo'i tshogs 'phros pas /
NK030(a)001:17952: lus 'khor lo'i go khrab zhu labs dang //
NK030(a)001:17953: zhu lubs su gyur par bsgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:17954: gser gyi ri bo lta bu la //
NK030(a)001:17955: spyi bor rnam par snang mdzad //
NK030(a)001:17956: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i /
NK030(a)001:17958: / 'khor lo'i go cha bla na med /
NK030(a)001:17960: / 'khor lo'i go cha bsrungs du gsol //
NK030(a)001:17961: lus la go skon sems la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:17962: bla na med par bsrungs bar shog  /
NK030(a)001:17963: 'khor lo bskor ba lta bu'i sku tshe dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:17964: 'o khyer rang rnams kyi mgrin pa'i snang ba mtha'
NK030(a)001:17965: yas yab yum sbyor ba mdzad ba'i byang chub sems
NK030(a)001:17966: kyi bdud rtsis / lus phyi nang gi sdig pa dang /
NK030(a)001:17968: lus nang 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis gang /
NK030(a)001:17969: phyir ba spu'i bu ga thams cad pad+ma'i zil pa phrom par gyur par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:17970: lce yi pad ma 'dab brgyad la //
NK030(a)001:17971: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas dang //
NK030(a)001:17972: na bza' dkar mo gnyis med 'khril //
NK030(a)001:17973: gnyis med thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17974: bdag dang yon gyi bdag po la /
NK030(a)001:17976: / 'chi med tshe yi dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:17977: pad+ma a mi d+he wa h+r+aiih a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:17978: 'o byang sems bdud rtsi'i lhag ma yar lud pa las //
NK030(a)001:17979: khyed rang rnams kyi ltag par snang ba mtha' yas kyi dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)001:17980: de'i sku lus la pad+ma'i char babs pas /
NK030(a)001:17982: zhu lubs su gyur par bsgoms cig /
NK030(a)001:17983: byi ru'i sdong po lta bu la //
NK030(a)001:17984: rgyab du snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK030(a)001:17985: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:17986: pad+ma'i go cha bla na med //
NK030(a)001:17987: pad+ma'i go cha bsrungs du sol //
NK030(a)001:17988: lus la go skon sems la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:17989: bla na med par bsrungs bar shog /
NK030(a)001:17990: pad+ma brtsegs pa lta bu gsung gi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:17991: 'o khyed rang rnams thugs ka'i rdo rje sems dpa'
NK030(a)001:17992: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK030(a)001:17993: bdud rtsis lus phyi nang gi sdig sgrib dang tshe'i
NK030(a)001:17995: lus kyi nang 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis gang /
NK030(a)001:17996: phyi ba spu'i bu ga thams cad rdo rje zil pas khrom gyis gyur par bsgom //
NK030(a)001:17997: thugs kha nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:17998: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK030(a)001:17999: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnyis med 'khril //
NK030(a)001:18000: gnyis med thugs gyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18001: bdag dang yon gyi bdag po la /
NK030(a)001:18006: 'o byang sems bdud rtsi de'i lhag ma yar lud pa las /
NK030(a)001:18007: dpral bar rdo rje sems dpas dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)001:18008: de'i sku lus la rdo rje'i char babs pas /
NK030(a)001:18009: lus rdo rje'i go khrab zha lubs dang zhu lubs su gyur par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:18010: skar ma rgyal shar lta bu la //
NK030(a)001:18011: dpral bar rdo rje sems dpa' h+aum //
NK030(a)001:18012: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18013: rdo rje'i go cha bla na med //
NK030(a)001:18014: rdo rje'i go chas bsrung du gsol //
NK030(a)001:18015: lus la go bskon sems la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:18016: bla na med par bsrungs bar shog /
NK030(a)001:18017: rdo rje gsor ba lta bu thugs kyi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:18018: 'o khyed rang rnams kyi lte ba'i rin chen 'byung gnas yab yum sbyor pa mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18019: byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis lus phyi nang gi sdig sgrib dag /
NK030(a)001:18021: lus kyi nang bdud rtsis gang //
NK030(a)001:18022: lus kyi phyi ba spu'i bu ga thams cad rin
NK030(a)001:18023: po che'i zil ba phrom gyi gyur par bsgoms shig
NK030(a)001:18024: / lte ba rin chen zur brgyad la //
NK030(a)001:18025: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK030(a)001:18026: ma ma ki dang gnyis med 'khril //
NK030(a)001:18027: gnyis med thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18028: bdag dang yon gyis bdag po la /
NK030(a)001:18030: / 'chi med tshe yi dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:18031: rata na swa b+ha wa tram /
NK030(a)001:18033: 'o byang sems bdud rtsi'i lhag ma yar lud pa las /
NK030(a)001:18035: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)001:18036: de'i sku lus la rin po che'i char babs pas /
NK030(a)001:18037: lus rin po che'i zha lubs dang //
NK030(a)001:18038: zhu lubs su gyur par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:18040: g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan tram //
NK030(a)001:18041: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18042: rin chen go cha bla na med //
NK030(a)001:18043: rin chen go cha bsrungs du gsol //
NK030(a)001:18044: lus la go bskon sems la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:18045: bla na med pa bsrungs bar shog /
NK030(a)001:18046: rin chen 'bar ba lta bu yon tan gyi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:18047: 'o khyed rang rnams kyi gsang gnas don yod grub
NK030(a)001:18048: pa yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang sems kyis
NK030(a)001:18049: bdud rtsis / lus phyi nang gi sdig sgrib dang //
NK030(a)001:18050: tshe yi bar chad thams cad dag nas //
NK030(a)001:18051: lus kyi nang bdud rtsis gang //
NK030(a)001:18052: lus kyi phyi ba spu'i bu ga thams cad du //
NK030(a)001:18053: rgya gram zil pa phrom gyis gyur par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:18054: gsang gnas rgya gram dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:18055: bcom ldan don yod grub pa dang //
NK030(a)001:18056: lha mo sgrol ma gnyis med 'khril //
NK030(a)001:18057: gnyis med thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18058: bdag dang yon gyi bdag po la /
NK030(a)001:18061: kar ma a mo ga sid+d+hi ha /
NK030(a)001:18063: de nas gtor ma spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:18064: 'o gtor ma 'di dang gnyis su med par /
NK030(a)001:18065: mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa'i lha tshogs bzhugs par bsgoms cig /
NK030(a)001:18066: de'i sku lus la zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'byung /
NK030(a)001:18067: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bo nas babs /
NK030(a)001:18068: lus phyi nang gi sdig sgrib dag nas /
NK030(a)001:18069: rang gi lus kyi nang zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsis gang ba /
NK030(a)001:18070: gang nas 'chi med tshe yi dngos grub thob par bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)001:18071: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes tshe dpag du med pa'i 'od dang ldan /
NK030(a)001:18072: rigs mchog phyag rgya lnga ldan pa'i /
NK030(a)001:18073: khams gsum bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:18074: b+ha ling ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK030(a)001:18075: me tog gtor zhing ye d+harma brjod /
NK030(a)001:18077: skyod pas mi thub mi g.yo tshe'i rang bzhin la //
NK030(a)001:18078: spros pas khams gsum kun gyi bkrag dang ldan //
NK030(a)001:18079: brtan pas mi g.yo rdo rje lhun po 'dra //
NK030(a)001:18080: bcings pas mi shig rdo rje lu gu rgyud /
NK030(a)001:18081: tshe bum rin chen gzhal yas khang du byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18082: thugs kyi dpal be'u lta bur 'grub bar shog /
NK030(a)001:18083: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK030(a)001:18088: rigs lnga'i mgon po nas byin gyis brlabs kyi ye shes tshe'i rang bzhin gso byed tshe'i bcud /
NK030(a)001:18089: yon tan srog gi 'khor lo lus sems mthun pa'i dbyings /
NK030(a)001:18091: bdud rtsi sman gyi ril bu /
NK030(a)001:18092: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel bar byed pa /
NK030(a)001:18093: las dang nyon mongs pa'i gnas nas 'dren par byed ba'i /
NK030(a)001:18094: 'chi med tshe yi dngos grub 'di gsol bas /
NK030(a)001:18095: 'khor lo bskor ba lta bu'i sku'i tshe dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18096: pad+ma brtsegs pa lta bu gsung gi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18097: rdo rje gsor ba lta bu thugs kyi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18098: rin chen 'bar pa lta bur yon tan gyi tshe dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18099: ral gri bskor ba lta bur 'phrin las kyi tshe
NK030(a)001:18100: dang ldan par skye shi med pa tshe'i g.yung drung
NK030(a)001:18102: bgegs dang log 'dren gang gis kyang mi tshugs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18103: tshe dbang rdo rje bzhin mi 'gyur bar gyur lus
NK030(a)001:18104: ngag yid gsum rdo rje mi phyed pa'i dbang dam
NK030(a)001:18106: rdo rje snying po ltar sra zhing 'khreg par gyur cig tshe la mun pa dang /
NK030(a)001:18112: gnod byed gang gis kyang mi tshugs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18113: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na /
NK030(a)001:18115: rak+sha rak+sha s+w+aa h+aa brjod bla ma'i sku gsal bar bsgom du bzhugs la /
NK030(a)001:18116: spyod pas mi thub tshe'i rang bzhin la //
NK030(a)001:18118: rdo rje slob dpon phyag rgya gsal bsgoms pas //
NK030(a)001:18119: mi 'gyur g.yung drung lta bur 'grub bar shog /
NK030(a)001:18120: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang la sogs brjod /
NK030(a)001:18121: phyag mtshan 'khor lo la sogs pa lnga spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)001:18122: skyod pas mi thub mi g.yo la sogs dang //
NK030(a)001:18123: phyag mtshan rdo rje lta bur byin brlabs pas /
NK030(a)001:18125: / 'chi med rdo rje lta bur 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18128: bskyod pas mi thub mi g.yo zhes sogs dang //
NK030(a)001:18129: tshe nas ye shes lha tshogs lta bur byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18130: mi nub rgyal mtshan lta bur 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18133: spyod pa mi thub la sogs dang //
NK030(a)001:18135: bskyod pas tshe zan 'byung ba lnga ru byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18136: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18139: skyood pas mi thub sogs dang //
NK030(a)001:18140: tshe 'bras ye shes lnga ru byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18141: rig lnga'i sangs rgyas lnga ru 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18144: skyood pa mi thub mi g.yo tshe'i rang bzhin la sogs dang /
NK030(a)001:18145: tshe chang bdud rtsi lta bur byin rlabs pas /
NK030(a)001:18146: 'gyur med byang chub sems su 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18148: bkra shis rdzas brgyad spyi'am bye brag tu 'grim la /
NK030(a)001:18149: bskyood pas mi thub mi g.yo la sogs dang //
NK030(a)001:18150: yo byad bkra shis rdzas su byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18151: bkra shis lha mo brgyad du 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18152: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK030(a)001:18154: de dag rgyas par byed na //
NK030(a)001:18155: bkra shis rdzas brgyad las sngags kyi gsang la //
NK030(a)001:18157: dang po yungs dkar sbyin la /
NK030(a)001:18158: sngon bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)001:18159: gsang sngags rigs sngags bdag po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK030(a)001:18160: sgrub pa'i rdzas brgyad yungs dkar phyag du phul te /
NK030(a)001:18161: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa /
NK030(a)001:18164: yungs dkar du rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18165: yungs dkar rdo rje'i rigs te thams cad du //
NK030(a)001:18166: bgegs rnams ma lus dag par byed pa ste //
NK030(a)001:18167: mthu stobs yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK030(a)001:18168: bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams zhi byed shog /
NK030(a)001:18171: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)001:18172: r+ts+wa 'tshong gi khye'u bkra shis kyi r+ts+wa dur ba phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)001:18173: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa //
NK030(a)001:18176: dur wa'i rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18177: dur bas tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK030(a)001:18178: rdo rje sems dpa' tshe ni rab bsgrub phyir //
NK030(a)001:18179: nyon mongs skye shi rgyun chad gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)001:18180: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni 'phel bar shog /
NK030(a)001:18183: shing thog bil ba gtad la /
NK030(a)001:18184: sngon bcom ldan 'das shwakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)001:18185: lha tshangs pas shing thog bil ba phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)001:18186: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin //
NK030(a)001:18188: bil ba rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18189: bil bas rgyu rkyen 'bras ldan pa yis /
NK030(a)001:18191: / 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa rnams //
NK030(a)001:18192: snying rje byang chub mchog tu dag gyur bas //
NK030(a)001:18193: bkra shis des kyang don kun grub par shog /
NK030(a)001:18194: bil ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK030(a)001:18195: g+hi wam phyag du gtad la /
NK030(a)001:18196: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)001:18197: glang po che nor skyong gi bus //
NK030(a)001:18198: g+hi wam phyag du phul ba ste //
NK030(a)001:18199: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:18201: g+hi wam gi rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18202: g+hi wam dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK030(a)001:18203: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas //
NK030(a)001:18204: nyon mongs zung ngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)001:18205: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal zhi gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18206: g+hi wam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18208: sngon bcom ldan nas sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)001:18209: bram ze skal rgyal gyi bus /
NK030(a)001:18210: sman li khri phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)001:18211: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:18213: li khri rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18214: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK030(a)001:18215: chos rnams ma lus yongs su gyur nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:18216: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18217: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid brtan gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18218: li khri a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18220: sngon gcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)001:18221: zhing pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas //
NK030(a)001:18223: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du //
NK030(a)001:18225: zho'i rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18226: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)001:18227: snying po chos nyid ye shes rnams rtogs nas //
NK030(a)001:18228: yon tan kun gyi dbyings su gyur ba yis //
NK030(a)001:18229: bkra shis des kyang dug gsum zhi byed shog /
NK030(a)001:18230: d+ha ra ti ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18232: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)001:18233: gzugs kyi lha mo 'od 'chang mas me long phyag du phul te /
NK030(a)001:18234: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)001:18236: me long gi rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18237: me long ye shes rgya mtsho chen po yis //
NK030(a)001:18238: ye shes rgya mtsho mchog tu dag gyur ste //
NK030(a)001:18239: rnam dag chos la thogs med lung ston pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18240: bkra shis des kyang sgribs pa dag gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18241: a dar sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18243: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)001:18244: lha'i dbang po brgya sbyin gyis /
NK030(a)001:18245: dung g.yas su 'khyil ba phyag du phul ste //
NK030(a)001:18246: bkra shis ba'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du //
NK030(a)001:18247: deng 'dir slob ma 'di rnams la dung gi rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18248: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK030(a)001:18249: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du dag gyur te //
NK030(a)001:18250: chos rnams ma nor yongs su ston pa yi //
NK030(a)001:18251: bkra shis des kyang tshig dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)001:18254: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang sogs bardzoda do //
NK030(a)001:18255: des shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob /
NK030(a)001:18257: rdzogs rim bde stong bsgoms pa la dbang /
NK030(a)001:18258: mthar thug chos kyi sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18261: de kho na nyid kyis dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18262: phyi snod kyi rang bzhin 'od du zhu nas //
NK030(a)001:18263: nang bcud kyi sems can la thim /
NK030(a)001:18264: nang bcud kyi sems can 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)001:18266: khyed rang rnams kyang 'od du zhu nas mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du dar gcig bsgom /
NK030(a)001:18267: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i dbyings nyid la /
NK030(a)001:18268: rnal 'byor a yu dmar pos tshe sbas pas /
NK030(a)001:18269: de las phyag rgya bdun gyis brgyas ni gdab bar bya /
NK030(a)001:18270: dang po sku mchog nyid kyi rgya //
NK030(a)001:18271: gnyis pa thabs dang shes rab rgya //
NK030(a)001:18272: gsum pa sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK030(a)001:18273: bzhi pa ye shes lnga'i rgya //
NK030(a)001:18274: lnga pa gser gyi 'khor lo'i rgya //
NK030(a)001:18275: drug pa rta mchog dbang gi rgya //
NK030(a)001:18276: bdun pa chos nyid dbyings kyi rgya //
NK030(a)001:18277: chos nyid dbyings su tshe spas pas //
NK030(a)001:18278: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgrar langs kyang //
NK030(a)001:18279: de la gzung zhing gcad du med //
NK030(a)001:18280: brgyas 'debs mas ni rgyas gdabs pas //
NK030(a)001:18281: bran gyis 'gal bar mi byed cing //
NK030(a)001:18282: bde ba mos ni tshe bsrung bas //
NK030(a)001:18283: bdud dang mu ge gang gis kyang /
NK030(a)001:18285: / 'di la gnod par mi nus so //
NK030(a)001:18286: gsang ba mos ni tshe spas pas //
NK030(a)001:18287: mi shor bas ni dam du bsdoms //
NK030(a)001:18288: tshe 'phel mas ni tshe bsrungs bas //
NK030(a)001:18290: na mo b+ha ga wa te a pa ra mi ta /
NK030(a)001:18292: su b+hi ni tsi ta te dz+wa ra tsa ya /
NK030(a)001:18294: ar+ha ha te sam mya k+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK030(a)001:18300: a pa ra mi ta pu pun+yee /
NK030(a)001:18301: dz+ny+aa na sam b+ha ro pa tsi te /
NK030(a)001:18302: sarba sam ska ri pa ri shu d+ha /
NK030(a)001:18304: sa mud ga te swa b+ha wa b+hi shud d+he
NK030(a)001:18305: ma h+aa ya na ba ri wa re s+w+aa h+aa
NK030(a)001:18306: / zhes man+dala dang bsngo ba smon lam bkra shis brjod //
NK030(a)001:18307: des dbang bzhi pa de kho na nyid tshig dbang rin po che thob //
NK030(a)001:18308: sgo gsum tha dad du 'dzin ba'i sgribs pa dag /
NK030(a)001:18309: rdzogs rim phyag rgya chen po sgom pa la dbang //
NK030(a)001:18310: mthar thug ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18312: de'i gong du shes rab ye shes //
NK030(a)001:18315: de bzhis dngos gzhi de song nas /
NK030(a)001:18317: de nas mchod pa gong bzhin byed //
NK030(a)001:18318: bsngo ba smon lam spyi dang mthun par bya //
NK030(a)001:18319: gang yang bdag blo gti mug sogs kyis nyes pa bzod par gsol //
NK030(a)001:18320: khyed kyi sems can don kun mdzad //
NK030(a)001:18323: mdun bskyed kyi ye shes pa gshegs //
NK030(a)001:18324: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu //
NK030(a)001:18326: tshe dang ye shes rgya mtsho'i gter /
NK030(a)001:18328: / 'od dpag med pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18329: ye shes bzhi'i rang bzhin can /
NK030(a)001:18330: rigs kyi yum bzhi'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18331: gsang ba yum gyi lha mo bzhi //
NK030(a)001:18332: dbyings kyi lha mo'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18333: mi dge bcu po tshar gcod phyir //
NK030(a)001:18334: khro bo bcu yis bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18335: zhi rgyas dbang drag rang bzhin can //
NK030(a)001:18336: sgo ma bzhi'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18337: dngos grub ma lus bstsol ba yi //
NK030(a)001:18338: rdo rje lha mo'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:18342: de nas rdul tshon bsdus la chu chen nang du dor ro //
NK030(a)001:18343: bdag bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor rim pa bzhin du bsdu //
NK030(a)001:18345: slar tshe dpag med du gsal bas spyod lam bya'o //
NK030(a)001:18346: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med pa yis //
NK030(a)001:18347: thugs kyi dgongs pa rgyud sde'i don rnams rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:18348: thugs rje'i chu rgyun rim par legs brgyud nas //
NK030(a)001:18349: bdag nyid smin cing grol ba'i byin rlabs ni //
NK030(a)001:18350: tshe bsgrub dbang mchog bdud rtsi'i char rgyun gyi //
NK030(a)001:18351: gdul bya las dang skal ba ldan pa rnams //
NK030(a)001:18352: tshe dpal bsod nams rgya chen rgyas par byas //
NK030(a)001:18353: legs bshad 'di ni rdo rje bzang po yis //
NK030(a)001:18354: gnas mchog bsgrub sde bzang po mngon dga' ru /
NK030(a)001:18355: bris pa'i dge bas phan thog dar rgyas shog /
NK030(a)001:18360: / / / bkra shis dpal 'bar 'dzam gling brgyan gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:18361: des 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub len pa de song nas //
NK030(a)001:18362: gnyis pa dam rdzas la brten nas sku gsung thugs
NK030(a)001:18363: yon tan 'phrin las kyi dngos grub len pa ni
NK030(a)001:18365: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub kyi //
NK030(a)001:18366: gzugs zan la gzo zhing mar gyi brgyan cha can dang /
NK030(a)001:18368: la sogs dngos grub kyi rdzas sna tshogs //
NK030(a)001:18370: btung ba'i rigs sna tshogs bshams la //
NK030(a)001:18372: 'dus pa mdo'i lha tshogs la sogs bsgom la mchod bstod bya zhing /
NK030(a)001:18374: nye bsnyen gyi sgrub pa dang /
NK030(a)001:18375: bsgrub pa chen po'i sgo nas bzlas brjod kyi //
NK030(a)001:18376: bsnyen pa brgya 'am stong la sogs 'bul gzungs thag
NK030(a)001:18377: la brten nas dngos grub kyi dmigs pa'i 'phro 'dus
NK030(a)001:18383: kar ma sid+d+hi ha ha la bsnyen no //
NK030(a)001:18385: h+aum chos nyid bde ba chen po'i skur byung ba //
NK030(a)001:18386: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:18387: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)001:18388: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:18389: ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18390: ko ri khro mo brgyad kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18391: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18392: sing ha phra med brgyad kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18393: tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18394: rta gdong sgo ma tshogs bcas dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)001:18396: / 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang ga shed nas //
NK030(a)001:18397: spor ma gsang yum tshogs bcas dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:18398: dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18399: dbang phyug ma sring tshogs kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18400: dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18401: mkha' gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)001:18403: / 'phrin las myur 'gyogs chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18404: ma bdun sring mo bzhi yis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18405: sgrol byed 'bar ba'i chen pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18406: rdo rje ging chen bac+wo brgyad dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18407: zhing chen 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18408: khro rgyal yab yum drug bcus dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18409: ci bgyis bka' nyan las kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18410: pho nya drug bcu rtsa bzhis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18411: las rnams yongs su gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18412: ma mo drug bcu'i tshogs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)001:18413: sdom pa'i sa la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)001:18414: rig 'dzin rtsal chang tshogs kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18415: gnas mchog yang dag don gyi 'og min nas //
NK030(a)001:18416: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)001:18418: / 'og min dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK030(a)001:18419: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK030(a)001:18420: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga yum dang bcas //
NK030(a)001:18421: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18422: lha klu gnod sbyin so so'i gnas mchog nas //
NK030(a)001:18423: bacomaldana rigs gsum mgon pos dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)001:18424: o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu /
NK030(a)001:18425: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs sprul dga' rdor dang //
NK030(a)001:18426: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron la //
NK030(a)001:18427: rdo rje sems dang gsang bdag dngos byon nas //
NK030(a)001:18428: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtogs tshogs lha ngo sprad //
NK030(a)001:18429: dbang rtags chags shing me long rnam gnyis sbyin //
NK030(a)001:18430: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas nas //
NK030(a)001:18431: de'i dngos grub dam pa cha gcig kyang //
NK030(a)001:18432: de ring gsang ba'i gnas mchog chen po 'dir //

NK030(a)001:18694: 'dus pa mdo'i dngos grub gsal zhing len pa'i dbang
NK030(a)001:18695: du gsungs te zhi ba'i lha khro bo la gnas
NK030(a)001:18697: khro bo la blangs pa de ka zhi ba la blangs pa yin pas /

NK030(a)001:18701: gsal bar byas pa de la ye shes lha dang
NK030(a)001:18702: / mtshan ma rdzas gnyis ka 'byung bar byas pa yin te /

NK030(a)001:18713: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs nyid spyan drangs /

NK030(a)001:18720: a khra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /

NK030(a)001:18724: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18725: badz+ra ang gu sha dza dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /

NK030(a)001:18737: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dang //
NK030(a)001:18738: dbang mchog he ru yab yum dang //
NK030(a)001:18739: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum dang //
