NK030(a)001:18748: ru lu sarba ta th+aa ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18749: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18750: ru lu badz+ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18751: ru lu gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18753: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)001:18754: bla med yum chen khro mo rgyal //
NK030(a)001:18756: nyi shu rtsa gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NK030(a)001:18757: zhabs brgyad ting 'dzin dbyings su sbyor //
NK030(a)001:18758: brgyan rnams ma lus sku la rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:18759: khro rgyal sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18760: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK030(a)001:18761: dbu dgu phyag ni bac+wa brgyad de //
NK030(a)001:18762: stong pa bac+wa brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:18763: mthing nag dgyes pa chen po'i sku //
NK030(a)001:18764: zhabs brgyad ru tra pho mo mnan /
NK030(a)001:18766: h+aum rdo rje rigs mchog bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK030(a)001:18767: gdug pa chen po thabs kyi btul nas ni //
NK030(a)001:18768: bdud kyi rigs rnams rdul du rlag mdzad pa //
NK030(a)001:18769: dpal chen yab yum sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18770: ru lu g+hu lnga pa smon lam gdab ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18771: ho bcom ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka yab yum dang /
NK030(a)001:18772: dbang mchog chen po yab yum dang /
NK030(a)001:18773: dpal chen po he ru ka yab yum la sogs pa rnams la /
NK030(a)001:18774: dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:18775: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK030(a)001:18776: shes bya'i chos thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes pa'i shes rab /
NK030(a)001:18784: rdo rje spyan la sogs pa'i dngos grub thob pa dang /
NK030(a)001:18792: zas dang nor la sogs pa 'byor pa'i yo byad thams cad rgyas shing 'phel nas /
NK030(a)001:18793: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod pa dang /
NK030(a)001:18794: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar shing rgyas pa dang /
NK030(a)001:18795: 'khor dang longs spyod 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:18796: khyad par gyis rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan yongs su
NK030(a)001:18797: rdzogs pa'i dngos grub kyi sku thob par bstsal du
NK030(a)001:18798: gsol // drug pa bsdu ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18799: badz+ra ad+gu sha dza dz+aahzhesa pa lan gsum brjod pas /
NK030(a)001:18800: dang po 'od dang sprul pa gnyis pas yig 'bru
NK030(a)001:18801: gsum pa 'od du zhu nas bdag nyid la thim
NK030(a)001:18802: pas / bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK030(a)001:18803: de nas gsal shing gis rim ba gnyis pa la
NK030(a)001:18804: rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blangs te
NK030(a)001:18805: / de la yang don drug gi dang po spyan drangs ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18806: pho brang gis mar me la /
NK030(a)001:18807: rigs bzhi he ru ka phyogs bzhi nas bskyed pa ste /
NK030(a)001:18808: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas ste //
NK030(a)001:18809: bud+d+ha sh+ri he ru ka bu d+ha shi he ru kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18811: ru lu rad na yab yum /
NK030(a)001:18812: ad+gu sha dz+aah ru pad+ma yab yum /
NK030(a)001:18813: ad+gu ru karma yab yum ad+gu ru lu zhes bzhes brjod la gsal shing gnyis pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:18814: me 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:18815: gnyis pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18816: rigs bzhi he ru ka la zhes pas /
NK030(a)001:18821: rigs bzhi'i he ru ka'i thugs kha nas /
NK030(a)001:18822: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar /
NK030(a)001:18823: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)001:18825: phar 'phros dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)001:18826: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)001:18832: kar+m+aa yab yum sngags la ru lu re re dang /
NK030(a)001:18833: g+hu h+ya re re gdags so //
NK030(a)001:18838: nan dbang drag shul bzhis bstod //
NK030(a)001:18840: ho bcom ldan rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum
NK030(a)001:18841: la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni bdag cag
NK030(a)001:18842: rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir
NK030(a)001:18843: 'tshogs pa rnams / shes bya'i chos thams cad la ces pa man chad 'agre'o //
NK030(a)001:18844: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin bya'o //
NK030(a)001:18845: de nas gsal shing rim pa gsum pa la lung
NK030(a)001:18846: gi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blangs pa la'ang
NK030(a)001:18847: don drug gis ston pa'i dang po spyan drangs ba
NK030(a)001:18848: ni / pho brang gi mar me la lung gi he ru ka yab yum /
NK030(a)001:18849: mtshams bzhi'i rtsibs la bskyed pa de lta bu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs ste /
NK030(a)001:18850: raka sha sh+ri he ru ka /
NK030(a)001:18851: rak+sha kro ti sh+aa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)001:18852: ru lu g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na sa nu yab yum /
NK030(a)001:18862: gsal shing gsum pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:18864: / 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:18865: de nas gnyis pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18866: lung gi he ru ka yab yum rnams la gtor ma /
NK030(a)001:18869: gsum pa bskul tshig dang 'dzab gnyis kyi dang po bskul ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18870: lung gi he ru ka'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)001:18871: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK030(a)001:18872: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)001:18873: g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od zer ni //
NK030(a)001:18874: phar 'phros pas ni thugs ka thims /
NK030(a)001:18875: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub gsol /
NK030(a)001:18881: ru lu re re dang gu h+ya re re spel gyis gdags so //
NK030(a)001:18883: h+aum spyor ba dam tshig gsang ba'i sgrol ma'i dbyings //
NK030(a)001:18884: log lta myang byed skye gnas reg bya 'joms /
NK030(a)001:18885: ga na nyams pa mtshan ma sgrol /
NK030(a)001:18886: lung gi khro rgyal tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18888: ho bcom ldan lung gi he ru ka yab yum
NK030(a)001:18889: gyi tshogs la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni
NK030(a)001:18890: / bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK030(a)001:18891: shes bya'i chos thams cad la zhes pa man chad gang gis shes so //
NK030(a)001:18892: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:18893: gsal shing gi rim pa bzhi pa la khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub blangs pa la /
NK030(a)001:18894: drug gi dang po sbyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:18895: mar me la khro mo brgyad bskyed pa /
NK030(a)001:18896: de lta bu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs ba ni /
NK030(a)001:18897: ke ri brgyad po'i rtsa sngags rdzogs pa ra brjod la /
NK030(a)001:18900: ru lu dang g+hu ya bzlas /
NK030(a)001:18902: ki ri brgyad kyi thugs ka'i /
NK030(a)001:18903: snying po'i g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od 'phros bas /
NK030(a)001:18908: ke'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni /
NK030(a)001:18909: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul pa'i drag shul can //
NK030(a)001:18910: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang stod //
NK030(a)001:18911: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18912: khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:18913: zhes pa la sogs pa dang bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:18914: gsal shing gi rim pa lnga pa la phra men
NK030(a)001:18915: brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi'i dngos grub blangs la drug
NK030(a)001:18916: gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:18917: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams dang po la sing+ha brgyad dang /
NK030(a)001:18918: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa lta bu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)001:18923: yang sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags /
NK030(a)001:18924: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dzah la sogs pa bzhi brjod /
NK030(a)001:18926: la sogs gsal shing lnga pa la me spar /
NK030(a)001:18927: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:18928: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum gyis dbul /
NK030(a)001:18931: sing ha phra med brgyad rnams dang //
NK030(a)001:18932: sgo ma bzhi'i thugs kha nas /
NK030(a)001:18933: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na' phar 'phros pas ni mchod /
NK030(a)001:18934: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos bzlas pa ni sing+ha brgyad po'i rtsa sngags dang //
NK030(a)001:18935: sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags ru lu spel mar bzlas so //
NK030(a)001:18938: h+aum sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)001:18939: stag gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams ni //
NK030(a)001:18940: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)001:18941: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrungs //
NK030(a)001:18942: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18944: phra men brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:18945: shes bya'i chos zhes pa dang //
NK030(a)001:18946: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:18947: gsal shing gi rim pa drug pa las /
NK030(a)001:18949: gsang yum bzhi'i dngos grub blangs pa la drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:18950: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams gnyis pa la bskyed pa ste /
NK030(a)001:18952: badz+ra a pra ti ha ar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)001:18953: a rag mo h+aum zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK030(a)001:18954: sh+ri badz+ra mud ka ra sha ra lu sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK030(a)001:18955: ru lu sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra dz+wa la ru lu /
NK030(a)001:18958: zhes brjod la gsal shing drug pa la me spar /
NK030(a)001:18959: 'od dang bcas de byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:18960: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul /
NK030(a)001:18961: gsum pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)001:18962: spor byed chen mo brgyad rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:18963: gsang ba yum bzhi'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)001:18964: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar 'phros pas mchod /
NK030(a)001:18966: a rag mo h+aum zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK030(a)001:18968: g+hu h+ya spel ma bzlas so //
NK030(a)001:18970: h+aum chos nyid rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK030(a)001:18971: sna tshogs cir snang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK030(a)001:18972: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK030(a)001:18973: spor byed chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18974: bar 'khyams de'i shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK030(a)001:18975: dgyes pa bskyed ba gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK030(a)001:18976: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK030(a)001:18977: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:18979: ho spor ma chen mo brgyad dang bzhi la gsang
NK030(a)001:18980: ba'i yum chen po dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo
NK030(a)001:18982: drug pa bsdu ba la gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)001:18983: yang gsal shing gi rim bdun pa la dbang phyug
NK030(a)001:18984: ma nyer brgyad kyi dngos grub blangs pas don drug
NK030(a)001:18985: gi dang po spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK030(a)001:18986: pho brang gi mar me bar 'khyam gsum pa la dbang mo bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)001:18987: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)001:18988: b+h+yo badz+ra ma nu rag sha si b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:18989: la sogs pa'i rtsa sngags tshang par brjod la /
NK030(a)001:18992: zhes brjod la gsal shing bdun ba la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:18993: 'od zer dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:18994: gnyis pa mchod sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyis dbul /
NK030(a)001:18995: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)001:18996: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)001:18997: snying po ru lu g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od 'phros //
NK030(a)001:18998: phar 'phros dpal tshur 'dus bdag rtsa sngags nyer brgyad bzlas la //
NK030(a)001:18999: ru lu dang g+hu h+ya spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)001:19001: h+aum srin mo la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK030(a)001:19002: dregs pa'i lha chen rnams kyi chung ma de //
NK030(a)001:19003: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK030(a)001:19004: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19006: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:19010: mkha' 'gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dngos grub blangs
NK030(a)001:19011: pa la drug gi dang po ni spyan drangs pa
NK030(a)001:19012: ni / pho brang gi mar me la /
NK030(a)001:19013: bar 'khyams bzhi'i mkha' 'gro ma sum cu so gnyis bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)001:19014: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)001:19015: e a ra li h+aum zhes pa so gnyis brjod /
NK030(a)001:19018: zhes brjod la gsal shing brgyad pa la mar me spar /
NK030(a)001:19019: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)001:19020: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags /
NK030(a)001:19021: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)001:19022: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)001:19028: ru lu g+hu ya rnams spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)001:19030: h+aum nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing /
NK030(a)001:19032: / 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK030(a)001:19033: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)001:19034: mkha' 'gro sum bcu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19036: mkha' 'gro sum bcu gnyis la dngos grub gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:19039: gsal shing dgu ba la ma mo bdun dang sring mo bzhi'i dngos grub blangs la /
NK030(a)001:19040: drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19041: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams lnga pa la ma mo bdun dang //
NK030(a)001:19042: sring mo bzhi bskyed nas yod pa de //
NK030(a)001:19043: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la //
NK030(a)001:19044: ma ma d+h+aa du h+aum bdun dang ru lu spel //
NK030(a)001:19045: badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo zhes pa bzhi dang ru lu spel la //
NK030(a)001:19046: badz+ra ang+gu sha dz+aa dz+aa zhes brjod la gsal shing dgu pa la me spar /
NK030(a)001:19047: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)001:19048: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum pa bzlas pa'i bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)001:19049: ma bdun sring mo'i snying po ru lu g+hu h+ya /
NK030(a)001:19052: ma ma d+ha du h+aum bdun dang //
NK030(a)001:19053: ru lu badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo bzhi dang //
NK030(a)001:19054: ru lu spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)001:19056: h+aum 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)001:19057: phyi 'khor 'dul zhing nang 'khor skyongs mdzad pa //
NK030(a)001:19058: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK030(a)001:19059: bgegs bsrungs ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19061: ma sring bzhi la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)001:19063: drug pa bsdu ba ni gong dang 'adre'o //
NK030(a)001:19064: gsal shing bcu pa la ging bac+wa brgyad kyi dngos
NK030(a)001:19065: grub blangs pa la drug gi dang po spyan drangs
NK030(a)001:19066: pa ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams drug pa la ging bac+wa brgyad bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)001:19067: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)001:19068: king ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u dang /
NK030(a)001:19071: gsal shing rim pa bcu pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:19073: / 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)001:19074: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor /
NK030(a)001:19075: gsum pa bzlas pa'i bskul tshig ni //
NK030(a)001:19081: king ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK030(a)001:19085: h+aum khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bac+wa brgyad ni //
NK030(a)001:19086: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)001:19087: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas rlags par byed //
NK030(a)001:19088: ging chen ging lcags tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19090: ging chen bac+wa brgyad la zhes pa dang //
NK030(a)001:19092: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu drug pa la //
NK030(a)001:19093: steng phyogs kyi khro bo khro mo drug bcu'i dngos
NK030(a)001:19094: grub blangs ba la drug gis spyan drangs ba ni
NK030(a)001:19095: // pho brang gi mar me'i 'khyams bdun pa la /
NK030(a)001:19096: khro bo khro mo drug bcu bskyed de /
NK030(a)001:19100: ru lu'i spel ba bcu drug bzla /
NK030(a)001:19102: zhes brjod la gsal shing bcu gcig pa la me spar /
NK030(a)001:19103: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor gsum sngags kyis mchod do /
NK030(a)001:19104: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)001:19105: khro bo khro mo drug bcu'i thugs kha nas /
NK030(a)001:19109: tshul 'dus kro d+ha kro ti h'u /
NK030(a)001:19113: bcom ldan h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK030(a)001:19114: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha'i lha /
NK030(a)001:19116: / 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK030(a)001:19117: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag mtshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19119: khro bo khro mo drug bcu la dngos grub ces pa dang //
NK030(a)001:19120: drug pa bsdu ba gong dang mthun no //
NK030(a)001:19121: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gnyis pa la phyogs
NK030(a)001:19122: bzhi'i pho nya nyis ba rgya dang bzhi bcu dngos
NK030(a)001:19123: grub blangs pa la drug gis dang po spyan drangs
NK030(a)001:19124: pa ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams brgyad pa la //
NK030(a)001:19125: shar du b+ha na b+ha na //
NK030(a)001:19126: ad+gu sha ja zhes pa drug bcus //
NK030(a)001:19127: dung gi pho nya drug bcu //
NK030(a)001:19128: lhor ha la ha la pa sha h+aum zhes pa drug cus //
NK030(a)001:19129: lcags dang gser gyi pho nya drug cu //
NK030(a)001:19130: nub phyogs su gardza gardza po ta bam //
NK030(a)001:19131: zhes bse'i pho nya drug cu //
NK030(a)001:19132: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de ho //
NK030(a)001:19133: zhes g.yu'i pho nya drug cu /
NK030(a)001:19134: badz+ra ad+gu sha dz+aa dz+aa zhes //
NK030(a)001:19135: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs //
NK030(a)001:19136: gsal shing bcu gnyis pa la me spar /
NK030(a)001:19138: / 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)001:19139: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul //
NK030(a)001:19140: gsum pa bzlas pa la bskul tshig /
NK030(a)001:19141: sngags gnyis kyi bskul tshig brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19142: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)001:19143: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i /
NK030(a)001:19146: b+ha na b+ha na ad+gu sha dza /
NK030(a)001:19148: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum ru lu /
NK030(a)001:19150: ru lu pa tsa pa tsa gan+de ho /
NK030(a)001:19153: h+aum ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yis /
NK030(a)001:19154: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med /
NK030(a)001:19155: ci bgyis bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i /
NK030(a)001:19156: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19158: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya gnyis brgya bzhi bcu la dngos grub du gsol ba'i zhes la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19160: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gsum pa la 'og
NK030(a)001:19161: phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu'i dngos grub blangs la
NK030(a)001:19162: drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19163: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams dgu pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19164: ma mo shwa ra h+aum zhes /
NK030(a)001:19165: ma mo drug bcu bskyed pa de //
NK030(a)001:19167: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs //
NK030(a)001:19168: gsal shing bcu gsum pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:19170: / 'od dang bcas nas gsal shing rtser byon par bsam //
NK030(a)001:19171: gnyis sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul //
NK030(a)001:19172: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19173: ma mo drug bcu'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)001:19174: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i /
NK030(a)001:19178: ru lu g+hu ya bzhi pa bstod pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19179: h+aum stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK030(a)001:19180: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK030(a)001:19181: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)001:19182: ma mo drug bcu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)001:19184: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu la dngos grub du gsol ba ni /
NK030(a)001:19185: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19187: de nas gsal shing rim pa bcu bzhi pa la
NK030(a)001:19188: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dngos grub blangs pa la'ang
NK030(a)001:19189: don drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19190: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams bcu pa na //
NK030(a)001:19191: ma h+aa g+hu ru shwa ri ram //
NK030(a)001:19193: yo ki ni gu ru sa ma ye dzah zhes
NK030(a)001:19194: rig 'dzin rig pa 'dzin tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK030(a)001:19196: gsal shing gi rim bcu bzhi pa la /
NK030(a)001:19198: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la spyan 'dren /
NK030(a)001:19199: gsal shing bcu bzhi pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)001:19200: 'od dang bcas nas gsal zhing gi rtse la byon par bsam /
NK030(a)001:19203: ma h+aa pany+tsa a smri ta kha hi /
NK030(a)001:19205: mah+aa b+ha ling ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)001:19207: gsum pa bzlas pa bskul tshig dang /
NK030(a)001:19210: man ngag mdo lung rgyud dang bcas pa yis //
NK030(a)001:19211: ting 'dzin bla ma rnams kyi thugs kha nas //
NK030(a)001:19212: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)001:19215: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub gsol //
NK030(a)001:19217: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram gyi li h+aum //
NK030(a)001:19218: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ma ya dza //
NK030(a)001:19219: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK030(a)001:19220: g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na b+ho d+he tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum /
NK030(a)001:19222: h+aum rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK030(a)001:19223: lhun grub phyag chen tshe rnam smin //
NK030(a)001:19224: rgya gar bod kyi grub thob tshogs bcas pa'i //
NK030(a)001:19225: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsool cig /
NK030(a)001:19227: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang ba'i lha
NK030(a)001:19228: tshogs rnams la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni
NK030(a)001:19229: / zhes pa la sogs pa rnams gong ji lta ba bzhin bya'o //
NK030(a)001:19235: gsum pas 'od du zhu nas bdag nyid la thim pas /
NK030(a)001:19236: bdag la sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyis gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK030(a)001:19237: de ltar cho ga'i rim pa rnams tshar ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19239: dpon slob rnam grangs mnyam par bkram la //
NK030(a)001:19240: de'i bar la slob bu rnams khrus rim zhig bya nang du sleb pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19244: rnal 'byor pa rnams rol la dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)001:19246: de nas zhal zas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)001:19247: las mkhan gyi tshogs mchod zur tsam byas la //
NK030(a)001:19248: zla kham zhabs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:19249: rang rig ye shes mngon snang ba'i /
NK030(a)001:19251: / 'dod yon gsal ba'i longs spyod brgyan //
NK030(a)001:19252: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sid+d+hii bstsol //
NK030(a)001:19253: bdag nyid rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral
NK030(a)001:19254: rnams kyis rdo rje tshe gsol bas tshe dbang phun
NK030(a)001:19255: sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig
NK030(a)001:19256: / mah+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyis dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:19259: / 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'du bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19260: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19261: gal phye gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19262: zla phrom gsol bas gsang ba chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)001:19263: 'jam des gsol bas byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19267: ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19268: thugs rje chen pos dgongs zhing bzhes nas bdag nyid la /
NK030(a)001:19269: sku gsung thugs kyi sid d+hi dus da lta nyid du thob par bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:19270: zhes brjod la sid+d+hi'i zhal zas rnams kun gyi rim par bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)001:19271: zhes brjod la sid d+hi'i zhal zas kun gyi rim pa gsol lo //
NK030(a)001:19272: de nas dngos grub kyi lhag ma gsum la //
NK030(a)001:19273: yid dam lha'i skal ba rdo rje slob dpon gyis rol //
NK030(a)001:19274: dal lha'i skal ba rgyas theb la byin //
NK030(a)001:19275: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi skal ba de //
NK030(a)001:19276: de na yod pa'i slob bu las can cig la sbyin no //
NK030(a)001:19277: de nas gzhan rnams ci rigs par sbyin la spyad /
NK030(a)001:19278: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK030(a)001:19280: sid+hi brtan par bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK030(a)001:19281: sems can gyi don bya ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:19282: me tog lag tu 'grim la rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas byed do //
NK030(a)001:19283: de nas mar me blangs la /
NK030(a)001:19284: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK030(a)001:19286: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19287: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19288: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19289: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK030(a)001:19290: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19291: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19292: dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19293: ma 'gags thugs kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)001:19294: thugs ye shes dgu'i nang nas 'char ba'i sid+d+hi bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK030(a)001:19296: lcam dral rnams kyis thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)001:19299: de nas mar me'i smon lam gdab ba ni /
NK030(a)001:19300: kun gyi srin lag sbrel zhing mar me 'dzin la /
NK030(a)001:19301: h+aum dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)001:19302: rdo rje slob dpon gnyen gyi dbu gzung nas //
NK030(a)001:19303: rgyal ba'i gdung tshob mched dang lcam dral rnams //
NK030(a)001:19304: nam zhig byang chub lam du zhugs ba'i tshe /
NK030(a)001:19306: / 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen po'i mi gtung zhing //
NK030(a)001:19307: gcan ga zan gdug pa'i sgra skad mi grags dang //
NK030(a)001:19308: ma rig mun pa'i nang du mi btang zhing //
NK030(a)001:19309: gcong rong zab mo'i nang du mi skye dang //
NK030(a)001:19310: dmyal ba'i zangs khar nang du mi ltung zhing //
NK030(a)001:19311: mtshon rnon gdug pa'i dbal gyis mi 'phog shog /
NK030(a)001:19312: dge ba'i bshes gnyen sku drin che ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19313: dam tshig gcig pa'i rdo rje mched lcam rnams //
NK030(a)001:19314: dam tshig dbang gis 'brel ba'i gzungs ma gsum //
NK030(a)001:19315: tshe rabs 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK030(a)001:19316: mi 'bral 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin rtse gcig gis //
NK030(a)001:19317: sa bcu khyad par rim gyi bsgrod gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19318: nam zhig tshe 'phos lus barjesa dus byung tshe //
NK030(a)001:19319: ma rig gti mug mun pa'i sdug bsngal rnams /
NK030(a)001:19321: / 'khor pa'i g.yang sa chen por ltung srid na //
NK030(a)001:19322: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)001:19323: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)001:19324: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po'i shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)001:19325: zhe sdang 'bar ba las kyi sdug bsngal gyis /
NK030(a)001:19326: dmyal ba'i zangs khang lam du ltung srid na //
NK030(a)001:19327: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)001:19328: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)001:19329: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)001:19330: nga rgyal khro gtum khengs pa'i sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)001:19331: gcan gzan gdug pa'i sgra skad thos srid kyis //
NK030(a)001:19332: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)001:19333: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)001:19334: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig  /
NK030(a)001:19335: 'dod chags 'dzin pa las kyi sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)001:19336: gcong rong zab mo'i gnas su ltung srid kyis //
NK030(a)001:19337: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)001:19338: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)001:19339: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)001:19340: phrag dog zug rngu'i las kyi sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)001:19341: mtshon rno gdug pa'i spal gyi phog srid kyis //
NK030(a)001:19342: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)001:19343: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)001:19344: rig 'dzin bsgrub pa po yi shul mtshon nas //
NK030(a)001:19345: sa bcu khyad par rim gyis bsgrod pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19346: nyon mongs bag chags ma lus byang nas ni /
NK030(a)001:19348: / 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis //
NK030(a)001:19349: sa bcu khyad par rdzogs gyur nas //
NK030(a)001:19350: byang chub sems ma rnams kyis mdun bsus cig /
NK030(a)001:19351: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)001:19352: khro bo khro mo rnams kyis rgyab brten cig /
NK030(a)001:19353: sa bcu'i khyad par rtse mor phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19354: phyir mi zlog pa'i dngos grub de thob po //
NK030(a)001:19355: kun tu 'od kyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19356: yi dam lha'i sngon nas shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)001:19357: bkra shis lha mo brgyad kyi mtha' rten cig /
NK030(a)001:19358: ma tshogs dbang phyug ma'i mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)001:19359: stug po bkod pa'i sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19360: rdo rje khro rgyal rnams kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK030(a)001:19361: rig 'dzin rnams kyis zhabs drung skyes nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:19362: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par smon //
NK030(a)001:19363: shes bya'i sgrib pa phra mo spangs nas ni //
NK030(a)001:19364: yi ge gsum gyi gol sa der bskod de //
NK030(a)001:19365: de bas kun tu 'od kyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19366: che mchog he ru ka yi mdun bsus shig /
NK030(a)001:19367: gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi'i mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)001:19368: yi dam lha'i rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)001:19369: kun bzang dbyer med sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19370: kun tu bzang po yab kyi mdun bsus shig /
NK030(a)001:19371: kun tu bzang mo yum gyis mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)001:19372: yi dam lha yis rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)001:19373: rdo rje sems dpa'i rig 'dzin sar phyin tshe //
NK030(a)001:19374: rgyal ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis shul mtshon nas //
NK030(a)001:19375: mnyam pa'i ting 'dzin gyis mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)001:19376: yid dam lha'i rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)001:19377: lcang lo can gyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19378: dbyer med ting nge 'dzin gyi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)001:19379: bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)001:19380: rdzogs pa bla ma'i sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19381: khyab brdal rig 'dzin rnams kyi shul mtshon cig  /
NK030(a)001:19382: 'ub chub ting nge 'dzin gyi mtha' bsdus shig /
NK030(a)001:19383: srid gsum ngang rdzogs sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19384: thig le chen po'i ngang du lhun grub nas //
NK030(a)001:19385: bya brtsol gnyis kyi mtha' las der 'das tshe /
NK030(a)001:19386: chos sku skye ba med pa'i don thob nas //
NK030(a)001:19387: longs sku sprul skus 'gro don byed par shog /
NK030(a)001:19388: ces smon lam rgya chen po btab bo //
NK030(a)001:19389: de nas dngos grub kyi drin lan gso ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)001:19390: tshogs la sogs pa yon phul ste /
NK030(a)001:19391: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK030(a)001:19393: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung las kyang //
NK030(a)001:19394: che ba rgyal srid dang yul 'khor //
NK030(a)001:19395: gces pa bu smad dang phyag rgya ma /
NK030(a)001:19396: 'phangs pa nor dang dbyig dka' ba lus dang srog /
NK030(a)001:19398: rgyun du zas dang gos yun du dad pa dang dam tshig /
NK030(a)001:19399: zhu khar srid zhu dang gus pa //
NK030(a)001:19400: mchog du brtse sems dang gdung ba la sogs pa mnyes pa /
NK030(a)001:19401: sna tshogs chu bo'i gzhung bzhin 'bul lo //
NK030(a)001:19402: de nas gu ru'i zhabs slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK030(a)001:19403: de ring phan chod bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)001:19404: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin gyis //
NK030(a)001:19405: nga yi bsgo ba ci ltar bzhin //
NK030(a)001:19406: bu khyod kyi ni bya dgos so //
NK030(a)001:19408: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po la //
NK030(a)001:19409: dad mos gus pa'i sems ldan pas /
NK030(a)001:19410: bka' yis ci ltar bsgo ba bzhin /
NK030(a)001:19411: lus ngag yid gsum gnyen gyis blangs /
NK030(a)001:19415: lhag ma btang las mkhan dang /
NK030(a)001:19416: mched lcam gyis phyir bstan ma skyongs //
NK030(a)001:19417: slob dpon dang rgyal thebs kyi nang du /
NK030(a)001:19418: dug gsum gyis sbyin bsregs bya /
NK030(a)001:19420: rgyal thebs kyi tho rgyal chen la ya hi ga tshas gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)001:19422: ye shes lha yi sgo byang la /
NK030(a)001:19424: bar chad bgegs kyi sgo byang /
NK030(a)001:19425: mchog phur dar gyi cod pan gcig bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed /
NK030(a)001:19426: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs la sgo byang de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og du bcug /
NK030(a)001:19427: phur ba de g+ha tas dril nas sgo byang la gdab /
NK030(a)001:19428: der bdud rtsi thig pa blug nas //
NK030(a)001:19429: byang chub kyi sems ma skyes kyi bar du thar pa med par bsam ste /
NK030(a)001:19430: des ni las rjes shis par bya ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK030(a)001:19431: de nas slob dpon kun 'dus las bkra shis bya /
NK030(a)001:19434: spyi don gnyis pa grol byed kyi gdams pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19435: thos bsam sgom gsum la rten nas khrid 'debs pa ste /
NK030(a)001:19436: bla ma'i zhal las shes par gyis shig /
NK030(a)001:19437: spyi don gsum pa rtsis che bas /
NK030(a)001:19440: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK030(a)001:19441: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK030(a)001:19444: yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa'i ston pa rdo rje
NK030(a)001:19445: rgyal po rdo rje rin chen dpal bzang pos gdams
NK030(a)001:19446: shing gtad / gang la gtad na /
NK030(a)001:19448: gang zag chos kyi mig can dang //
NK030(a)001:19449: mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams la gtad //
NK030(a)001:19450: dgos phyed gang gi ched du gtad na /
NK030(a)001:19451: chos 'di mi nub par bya ba'i phyir bsdud pa po la gtad /
NK030(a)001:19452: chos 'di dar zhing rgyas pa'i phyir gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan la gtad /
NK030(a)001:19453: chos 'di bka' btsan byin rlabs che ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)001:19454: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong rnams la gtad dgos so //
NK030(a)001:19455: tshul ji ltar du gtad na /
NK030(a)001:19456: de ni de yis thugs skyes phyir /
NK030(a)001:19457: de yi don ni des bsdus rigs ces gsungs pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:19458: rdo rje slob dpon gyis thugs las skyes pa'i //
NK030(a)001:19460: mtho brten myur rno rgya che yangs //
NK030(a)001:19461: zab yod rgyu'i gang zag gis /
NK030(a)001:19463: blo yi mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa'i bsdud pa po badz+ra b+ha tra la /
NK030(a)001:19466: ston pa rdo rje rgyal pos ci ltar gsungs pa'i don rnams /
NK030(a)001:19468: gzungs dang ldan pas bsdud pa po mdzad de /
NK030(a)001:19469: de yang thog mar klad don la /
NK030(a)001:19472: bshad par dam bca' ba dang gsum du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19474: yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)001:19476: sgyu 'phrul dbang gi rgyud pa rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:19477: lung a nu yo ga mdo dbang gi rgyud rim rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:19478: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga
NK030(a)001:19479: sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang gi rgyud pa'i rim
NK030(a)001:19481: de las byung ba'i gdams ngag la /
NK030(a)001:19483: ma smin pa smin par byed pa /
NK030(a)001:19485: smin pa grol bar byed pa'i gdam ngag dang gsum /
NK030(a)001:19488: drug gis bsgrubs pa'i gzhi gzung ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19489: bsnyen sgrub rnams pa bzhis sgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang ba'i tshul du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19493: nub gsum pa dngos gzhi dang gsum /
NK030(a)001:19495: sa gzhi spyi'i mtshan nyid brtags pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19496: rang gi mtshan nyid brtags pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19498: sa dbang du bya ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19500: sa byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19502: sa gzungs ba dang brgyad du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19503: nub gnyis pa sta gon la bca' bkod legs par tshar nas /
NK030(a)001:19506: ka p+aa la sta gon dang //
NK030(a)001:19510: rdo rje dril bu la sogs phyag cha sta gon dang /
NK030(a)001:19511: tsa ka li la sogs dbang rdzas sta gon dang /
NK030(a)001:19512: yo byad sta gon dang bcu gcig du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19513: nub gsum pa dngos gzhi la /
NK030(a)001:19514: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo dang /
NK030(a)001:19515: nang dbang 'byung pa'i chu bo dang /
NK030(a)001:19516: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo dang /
NK030(a)001:19517: gsang dbang man ngag gi chu bo dang bzhi /
NK030(a)001:19518: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo la /
NK030(a)001:19521: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang dang bzhi /
NK030(a)001:19522: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19526: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19527: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19528: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa la /
NK030(a)001:19536: bdun bdun gyi tshul du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19537: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la /
NK030(a)001:19538: slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19539: slob ma bzhug cing dbang bskur ba dang gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19541: 'jug chos bac+wa brgyad yon dang bcas pa drug drug dang /
NK030(a)001:19545: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum gyis dod dang bcas pa drug tu bsdus //
NK030(a)001:19546: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo la yang /
NK030(a)001:19547: zhi ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19548: khro bo'i dbang bskur ba la gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19550: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19551: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19552: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa la /
NK030(a)001:19553: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad dang /
NK030(a)001:19554: dkyil 'khor gyi thig gdab pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19557: dkyil 'khor la rab gnas byed pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19560: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la //
NK030(a)001:19561: slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19562: slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19563: de re re la'ang 'jug pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19567: spyan dar dgab pa dang dri ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19577: lha sgom par nan tan bya ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19582: bzod par gsol ba dang bac+wa brgyad bac+wa brgyad du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19583: dbang la yang phyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19595: phyag rgya'i dbang dang bcu bcur bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19601: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dang lnga lngar bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19604: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19605: tshig dbang rin po che dang gsum gsum du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19606: gsum pa bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo la'ang /
NK030(a)001:19607: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19609: / 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa dang gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19611: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad dang /
NK030(a)001:19612: dkyil 'khor la thig gdab pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19617: sbyin sreg dang bdun bdun du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19618: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la //
NK030(a)001:19619: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang //
NK030(a)001:19620: slob ma dkyil 'khor zhugs cing dbang bskur ba dang gnyis /
NK030(a)001:19622: dpon slob gnyis ka la khrus la sogs pa don
NK030(a)001:19623: bco brgyad bco brgyad yon tan dang bcas pa la
NK030(a)001:19624: gnyis su bsdus / dbang la'ang phyi dbang /
NK030(a)001:19629: zhi ba phyag rgya'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19633: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19634: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19636: brgyan chas rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19637: rdo rje ming gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19638: dbang phyug 'khor lo'i dbang bcur bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19643: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19645: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19648: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19649: bkra shis rtags brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19650: thig le ming gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19653: shes rab rigs pa gtan tshig gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19654: snying rje rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19656: dug ga sum sprugs pa'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19657: srid gsum sgrol ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19659: las rnams rdzogs pa'i dbang dang gnyis med 'khril ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19660: gsang ba sbyor ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19661: kun la dbang ba 'dod yon gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19663: thams cad bsgrub pa rdzas kyi dbang dang //
NK030(a)001:19664: gnyis su med pa rdo rje ming gi dbang dang bcu gsum du bsdus /
NK030(a)001:19667: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gnyis su bsdus so //
NK030(a)001:19668: bzhi pa gsang ba man ngag gi chu bo la 'ang //
NK030(a)001:19669: rdzogs chen sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)001:19670: zhar la 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dngos grub len pa'i cho ga dang /
NK030(a)001:19671: rdzas la brten nas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin
NK030(a)001:19672: las kyi dngos grub len pa'i cho ga rjes chog
NK030(a)001:19674: gnyis pa grol byed kyi gdams pa la /
NK030(a)001:19675: rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po /
NK030(a)001:19676: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad la sogs pa'i rgyud dang //
NK030(a)001:19678: man ngag phra mo drug bcu /
NK030(a)001:19679: bu lnga la sogs rnams pa dang /
NK030(a)001:19680: mdo' dgongs pa 'dus pa la sogs pa'i mdo snga ma bdun /
NK030(a)001:19685: smad 'grel mun pa'i go cha la sogs rgyud rgya gzhung man ngag rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:19689: kun byed ma bu dgu bskor la sogs rgyud rgya
NK030(a)001:19690: gzhung man nga ga dang bcas pa la thos bsam
NK030(a)001:19692: sgom pa rim pa gcig char gyis tshul du sgom pa /
NK030(a)001:19693: sbyod pa sbyod lam rnam bzhi lta b+hee la mi 'da' bar spyod /
NK030(a)001:19700: 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga thob pa'i thabs zab mor bsdus so //
NK030(a)001:19701: gsum pa rtsis che ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)001:19702: bka' rgyas gdab pa 'di dag go /
NK030(a)001:19703: zhabs don la brtsam pa ji ltar bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK030(a)001:19704: brtsam pa'i dge ba bsngo zhing //
NK030(a)001:19706: brtsams pa mthar phyir pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum du bsdus so //
NK030(a)001:19707: gnyis pa gang zag gi spyan ldan la tshul ji ltar gtad na /
NK030(a)001:19708: rdo rje'i slob ma che ge mo dang che ge /
NK030(a)001:19709: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i brtsam dus su //
NK030(a)001:19710: rdo rje 'chang chen po gnyis pa kun bzang rtse ba //
NK030(a)001:19711: bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po ba //
NK030(a)001:19712: drung ye shes dbang po'i sde //
NK030(a)001:19713: lhun sde rab 'byams pa dpal 'byor rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)001:19714: lo ts+aa ba chen po grags pa mtha' yas //
NK030(a)001:19715: dang po rab 'byams ba don 'grub rgyal mtshan pa //
NK030(a)001:19716: ltar ba kun dga' dpal ldan rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)001:19717: rab 'byams pa'i rin chen rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)001:19718: bka' bcu pa kun dga' rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)001:19719: sman gcig pa sku skye ba la sogs pa'i dge
NK030(a)001:19720: ba'i bshes gnyen chos kyi spyan can khyed rnams la
NK030(a)001:19721: / rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis dbang bskur //
NK030(a)001:19723: man ngag gnang ba brten nas khyed rnams kyis //
NK030(a)001:19724: spyir rgyud rgya gzhung man nga ga bye brag tu
NK030(a)001:19725: mdo rgyu sems gsum gyi dbang don zab mo 'di
NK030(a)001:19731: gzhan la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK030(a)001:19734: spel ba la sogs dar zhing rgyas par mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:19737: de ltar du mdzad pa zhal gyi bzhes shing da lan yang tshe dang che ge zhes dgos so //
NK030(a)001:19738: bye brag du phyag dpe yang /
NK030(a)001:19739: chos rje kun bzang rtse pa /
NK030(a)001:19740: drung ye shes dbang po'i sde /
NK030(a)001:19754: blo gros pa rnams kyis dbang dpe cha tshang cha bac+wa lnga bri bar zhal gyis bzhes so //
NK030(a)001:19755: gsum pa mkha' 'gro chos skyong la tshul ci ltar gtad na /
NK030(a)001:19756: rje btsun ma khros ma nag mo la sogs pa'i dkar mo sku yi mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)001:19759: ser mo yon tan gyi mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)001:19760: ljang mo 'phrin las kyi mkha' 'gro la sogs pa mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs //
NK030(a)001:19761: khyad par bdag cag la ma ltar byams pa'i mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)001:19763: gzungs ltar gdung pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK030(a)001:19764: bran ltar myur ba'i mkha' 'gro ma 'khor dang bcas
NK030(a)001:19765: pa khyed rnams gyi zhal du pany+tsa a mri ta
NK030(a)001:19766: kha hi / b+ha ling ta kha hi /
NK030(a)001:19768: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes shing tshims nas //
NK030(a)001:19769: bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK030(a)001:19771: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dbang dpe 'di /
NK030(a)001:19773: / 'dzin skyong spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis
NK030(a)001:19774: bsrung skyob dang 'phrin las dam pa mdzad du gsol
NK030(a)001:19775: // gal te chos 'di la gnod pa byed pa ste /
NK030(a)001:19779: 'khu ba la sogs pa'i bstan dgra rnams kyi srog chod /
NK030(a)001:19782: thal ba'i rdul du barloga cig /
NK030(a)001:19784: chos skyong la gtad pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19785: ru ru ro ru pa tsa la a shug me //
NK030(a)001:19786: dpal ldan ma lha mo nag mo rang byung gi rgyal mo //
NK030(a)001:19787: bdud kyi yul gshin rje'i sring /
NK030(a)001:19789: / 'khor ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)001:19793: sku gsung thugs mnyes shing tshim nas chos 'di 'dzin
NK030(a)001:19794: skyongs spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyi bsrungs
NK030(a)001:19795: ma dang sdong grogs rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:19796: chos 'di bka' btsan byin che dar zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)001:19797: chos 'di'i bstan dgra thams cad bsgral ba'i 'phrin las rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:19799: bur gur mah+aa pad+ma rdo bur //
NK030(a)001:19802: e ho shwa mo kro ta h+aum h+aum h+aum phata phata phata //
NK030(a)001:19803: dpal ldan mgon po nag po //
NK030(a)001:19806: lha dmag bye ba dung phyur gyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)001:19807: pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK030(a)001:19810: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyi rgyud mnyes nas //
NK030(a)001:19811: sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar chos 'di'i rgyud pa
NK030(a)001:19812: 'dzin pa rnams kyi bsrungs ma dang 'phrin las mdzad
NK030(a)001:19813: par khas blangs pa bzhin du bsrung ba dang 'phrin
NK030(a)001:19814: las mdzod gcig / ces gnyer gtad do //
NK030(a)001:19816: rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)001:19817: pan tsa a mri ta kha hi //
NK030(a)001:19820: khyed rnam kyis chos 'di 'dzin skyong spel ba la sogs byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis /
NK030(a)001:19821: bsrung ma dang mthun pa'i sgo nas 'byor ba phun
NK030(a)001:19822: sum tshogs pa la longs spyod pa'i skal ba ldan
NK030(a)001:19823: par gyur cig / ces gnyer gtad do //
NK030(a)001:19824: badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma y+aa /
NK030(a)001:19825: pan tsa a mri ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)001:19830: bu dam can 'gar ba nag po sha med gangs dkar ma /
NK030(a)001:19834: yang 'khor bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi tshogs dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis //
NK030(a)001:19835: chos 'di 'dzin skyong spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis bsrungs skyobs rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)001:19836: bstan dgra sdig can rnams thal ba rdul bzhin brlag pa'i 'phrin las mdzod gcig /
NK030(a)001:19837: ces tshul de ltar du gtad do //
NK030(a)001:19839: ci ltar brtsam pa'i tshul dang /
NK030(a)001:19840: brtsams pa'i dge rtsa byang chub tu bsngo zhing //
NK030(a)001:19842: brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK030(a)001:19843: dang po ci ltar brtsam pa'i tshul ni /
NK030(a)001:19845: chos kyi rgyal po spyan snga rin chen dpal //
NK030(a)001:19846: ngag dbang grags pa phyogs las rnams par rgyal //
NK030(a)001:19847: mthun rkyen bzang legs rgya che phun sum tshogs //
NK030(a)001:19848: thugs dgongs rnam dag dgyes tshul du mar bcas //
NK030(a)001:19849: thugs rje bka' drin mnyams med byin rlabs dang //
NK030(a)001:19850: thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje gzhon nu dpal //
NK030(a)001:19851: mnyes pa'i sgo nas gnang sbyin rim par bcas //
NK030(a)001:19852: bstan la phan phyir mdo rgyud sems gsum gyi //
NK030(a)001:19853: dbang mchog legs par brtsam dgos bka' brtsal dang //
NK030(a)001:19854: sprul pa'i sku mchog zha dmar cod pan 'dzin //
NK030(a)001:19855: chos kyi grags pa ye shes dpal bzang pos //
NK030(a)001:19856: dgyes pa'i tshul drug gser gyi me tog sogs //
NK030(a)001:19857: gnang nas mdo dbang bri dgos gsung ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19858: gzhung lugs rab 'byams thugs su chud pa yis //
NK030(a)001:19859: bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po pa la sogs bshes gnyen mang pos bskul ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19860: bdag kyang lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam dag gis //
NK030(a)001:19861: bla ma rnams kyi thugs dgongs rdzogs pa dang //
NK030(a)001:19862: mkha' mnyam 'gro rnams bde skyid 'byung ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19863: myur du sangs rgyas thob par bya phyir ste //
NK030(a)001:19864: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba phun tshogs la //
NK030(a)001:19865: brten nas gsang sngags mdo rgyu sems gsum gyi //
NK030(a)001:19866: dbang gi chog 'grig bsgrubs thabs gsal bar brtsams //
NK030(a)001:19867: de 'ang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK030(a)001:19868: ka thog chos kyi rgya mtsho chu yi gter //
NK030(a)001:19869: thos bsam sgom gsum srubs las legs par 'khrungs //
NK030(a)001:19870: sngags 'chang rdo rje 'dzin pa tsha zer rgyas //
NK030(a)001:19871: rta bdun mkha' la dbus kyi ri rgyal skor //
NK030(a)001:19872: gdul bya mdo rgyud pad tshal rgyas par byas //
NK030(a)001:19873: rnams dpyod blo yis bung ba rdo rje mchus //
NK030(a)001:19874: rgyud gzhung man ngag bcud rnams du ma bsdus //
NK030(a)001:19875: dbang mchog sbrang rtsi'i rgya mtsho yon tan tshangs //
NK030(a)001:19876: e ma 'di la mi sems su zhig yod //
NK030(a)001:19877: e ma 'di yi ro mchog myong bar byos //
NK030(a)001:19878: gnyis pa brtsams pa'i dge rtsa byang chub du bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK030(a)001:19879: de ltar brtsam pa'i dge rtsa dri med dang /
NK030(a)001:19881: / 'khor 'das lam gsum bsdus pa'i dge rtsa gnyis //
NK030(a)001:19882: phyogs gcig sdom pa kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK030(a)001:19883: zhi bar gshegs pa rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK030(a)001:19884: brgyud pa'i bla ma thugs rje can rnams la //
NK030(a)001:19885: lus ngag yid gsum mos pas phul ba yis //
NK030(a)001:19886: sa las yon tan gong du 'phel ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19887: rdo rje 'chang bar myur du gshegs nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:19888: bdag sogs 'gro rnams 'dren ston mdzad gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19889: yangs gcig brtsams pa'i dge rtsa dri med dang //
NK030(a)001:19890: sbyin pa tshul khrims sgom las byung ba yis /
NK030(a)001:19891: rab dkar dge ba'i tshogs rnams bsam las 'das //
NK030(a)001:19892: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i dge tshogs phyogs gcig sdom //
NK030(a)001:19893: kun tu bzang po mchod pa'i sprin phung gis //
NK030(a)001:19894: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po mnyes phyir 'bul //
NK030(a)001:19895: de las byung ba'i mthu stobs byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)001:19896: sku la mtshan mchog bzang po sum cu gnyis //
NK030(a)001:19897: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcus rab tu spras //
NK030(a)001:19898: dag pa'i 'khor tshogs nam mkha'i skar tshogs bkra /
NK030(a)001:19899: sku mchog rgyan gyis 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19900: gsung la dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cu dang //
NK030(a)001:19901: chos kyi dung chen gsung lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK030(a)001:19902: chos kyi grags pas phyogs bcur khyab gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19903: gsung mchog brgyan gyi 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19904: thugs ni ci lta ci rnyed dbyer med mkhyen //
NK030(a)001:19905: chos dbyings me long mnyam nyid so sor rtogs //
NK030(a)001:19906: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK030(a)001:19907: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag du ma thugs chud pa'i //
NK030(a)001:19908: thugs mchog brgyan gyi 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19909: sna tshogs rin chen sa gzhi mnan na nem //
NK030(a)001:19910: bteg na 'phar la mig mang ris su bris //
NK030(a)001:19911: rgya mdo thams cad rin chen tshom bus spras //
NK030(a)001:19912: ltar mi bzod pa'i 'od dang ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)001:19913: yon tan zhing khams sna tshogs thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19914: rat+na sna tshogs las grub gzhal yas khang //
NK030(a)001:19915: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs chos 'khor gdugs //
NK030(a)001:19916: brgyan rnams sna tshogs du mas spras pa yi //
NK030(a)001:19917: gzhal yas yon tan ldan pa thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19918: rin po che'i khri la mdzod mig ldan //
NK030(a)001:19919: seng ge glang chen rta mchog rma bya dang //
NK030(a)001:19920: shang shang brgyad brgyad rnams kyi btegs pa'i steng //
NK030(a)001:19921: mu thig dra ba la sogs khri khebs ldan //
NK030(a)001:19922: pad+ma stong ldan nyi ma zla ba yis //
NK030(a)001:19923: gdan khri yon tan can la bzhugs gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19924: dar dang rin chen rus pa du ma yis //
NK030(a)001:19925: dbu rgyan snyan cha mgur chu phreng ba dang //
NK030(a)001:19926: dpung rgyan phyag gdub zhabs gdub sor gdub sogs //
NK030(a)001:19927: rgyan cha yon tan ldan pas rgyan gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19928: sngon po dkar po ser po dmar po ljang //
NK030(a)001:19929: nyi shu rtsa lnga stong phrag du ma yis //
NK030(a)001:19930: mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba gur du phub /
NK030(a)001:19932: / 'od zer yon tan ldan pa 'phro gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19933: nad dang gdon dang sdig sgrib thams cad dang //
NK030(a)001:19934: dgra dang bgegs dang bar du gcod pa yis //
NK030(a)001:19935: spangs bar 'os pa ci mchis thams cad kun //
NK030(a)001:19936: zhi pa'i 'phrin las chen po 'grub gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19937: tshe dang bsod nams bkrag dang gzi brjid dang /
NK030(a)001:19939: / 'khor dang longs spyod dpal dang 'byor pa dang //
NK030(a)001:19940: nyams dang rtogs pa sku dang ye shes sogs //
NK030(a)001:19941: rgyas pa'i 'phrin las thams cad 'grub gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19942: lha 'dre mi gsum khams gsum srid pa gsum //
NK030(a)001:19943: zas nor longs spyod 'dod dgu gang dgos pa //
NK030(a)001:19944: ji ltar 'os ba'i dngos po thams cad kun //
NK030(a)001:19945: dbang du 'dus pa'i 'phrin las thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19946: nang gi nad gdon sdig sgrib bag chags dang //
NK030(a)001:19947: phyi nas sdo ba'i dgra bo dmag tshogs dang //
NK030(a)001:19948: bgegs kyi rigs la stong phrag brgyad bcu dang //
NK030(a)001:19949: ye 'brogs sum brgya dang ni drug bcu sogs //
NK030(a)001:19950: drag pos thams cad brdul du brlag gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19951: yang gcig dge rtsa mchod sprin rgya mtsho yis //
NK030(a)001:19952: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin chen po dang //
NK030(a)001:19953: gnas lnga pan chen mngon dga' chos rdzong pa //
NK030(a)001:19954: zhwa dmar cod pan 'dzin pa bzhi pa ba //
NK030(a)001:19955: bshes gnyen rgya mtsho dang bcas rnams la 'bul //
NK030(a)001:19956: spangs rtogs mthar phyin rdo rje 'chang thob nas /
NK030(a)001:19958: / 'gro drug sems can thar lam bkod gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19959: yang gcig 'di ltar bsgrub pa'i dge rtsa des //
NK030(a)001:19960: dkyil 'khor gcig tu zhugs pa skal bar ldan //
NK030(a)001:19961: thams cad kun rig kun bzang rtse pa sogs //
NK030(a)001:19962: rig 'dzin bsgrub mchog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK030(a)001:19963: mtho ris yon tan bdun ldan thob nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:19964: sku lnga lhun grub tshe gcig mngon sangs rgyas /
NK030(a)001:19966: / 'khor ba ma stongs bar du brten mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)001:19967: ded dpon dam pa mchog ni thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19968: de rnams las byung dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
NK030(a)001:19969: dus gsum pha ma sbyin bdag grogs mched dang //
NK030(a)001:19970: zab don chos dang dkar nag las kyis 'brel //
NK030(a)001:19971: sgrib gsum bag chags bcas pa dag nas kyang //
NK030(a)001:19972: nye 'khor dam pa nyid du sangs ni rgyas gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19973: gzhan yang 'gro drug sems can thams cad rnams //
NK030(a)001:19974: myur du sangs rgyas go 'phang thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)001:19977: byang chub sems dpa' tog dkar gyis //
NK030(a)001:19978: rgyal tshab mi pham mgon po la //
NK030(a)001:19979: dbu la srog zhu phul ba ltar //
NK030(a)001:19980: chos kyi rgyal po blon 'khor bcas //
NK030(a)001:19981: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen sogs //
NK030(a)001:19982: rgyu sbyor yon bdag 'khor dang bcas /
NK030(a)001:19984: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:19985: ces pa ltar 'og ma rnams la'ang //
NK030(a)001:19986: spyi bye brag ci rigs par sbyaro //
NK030(a)001:19987: yum ni sgyu ma lha mdzes kyis //
NK030(a)001:19988: sems can rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:19989: na tsha'i sdug bsngal zhi ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:19991: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:19992: thub pa yum las bltam pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:19993: seng sprug gnyis kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:19994: bsdo ba zil gyi mnon pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:19996: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:19997: yum ni sgyu ma lha mdzes la //
NK030(a)001:19998: glang sprug gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20002: / 'di tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20003: thub pa yum la ltams pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:20004: tshangs dang rgya byin dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20005: mkhyen pa'i bye brag mkhas pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20008: thub pa ltams nas zhag bdun tshe //
NK030(a)001:20009: sh+aaka rigs 'tshogs nas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20010: shes bya ma rmongs dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20013: don 'grub yi ge slob pa'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20014: yig mkhan slob dpon dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20015: lha mi yi ge mkhas pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20017: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20018: sngon gyi rgyal bu don 'grub la //
NK030(a)001:20019: ko tas brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20020: sa dang rdo yis phyag 'tshal ltar /
NK030(a)001:20024: yab kyi gzhu'i dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20025: bdud kyi sgyu rtsal 'dul ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20028: sngon gyi rgyal bu don 'grub la //
NK030(a)001:20029: drang srong skar ma la dga' bas /
NK030(a)001:20034: sngon gyi rgyal po don 'grub la /
NK030(a)001:20036: / 'khor los bsgyur bar dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20037: mi rtag mkhyen pa'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20040: sngon gyi rgyal po don 'grub la /
NK030(a)001:20042: / 'bangs kyis chibs phul rab byung bas //
NK030(a)001:20043: nyon mongs thar ba'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20045: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20046: sngon gyi don 'grub rab byung tshe //
NK030(a)001:20047: lha bus shan gris dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20048: nyon mongs sgrib pa gcod pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20051: don 'grub dka' thub rdzogs pa la //
NK030(a)001:20052: lha bus bsregs par dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20054: / 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20057: bcom ldan bsnyen pa rdzogs pa la //
NK030(a)001:20058: lha bus na bza' ngur smrig gsol //
NK030(a)001:20059: nyon mongs srid skyob dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20061: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20062: bcom ldan bsod snyoms gshegs pa la //
NK030(a)001:20063: spre'u'i rgyal pos sbrang rtsi phul //
NK030(a)001:20064: bkra shis rdzas mchog dam par ldan /
NK030(a)001:20067: bcom ldan dka' thub rdzogs pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)001:20069: sku gser phyis pa lta bur 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:20072: thub pa shing drung gshegs pa'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20073: r+ts+wa 'tshong r+ts+wa mchog bkra shis mas //
NK030(a)001:20074: r+ts+wa phul gdings bas bdud btul ltar /
NK030(a)001:20077: bcom ldan gyad kyi nye 'khor bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20078: tshangs pa nye 'khor legs skyabs kyi //
NK030(a)001:20079: bum ram shing dang sbrang rtsi phul /
NK030(a)001:20082: mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs dus su //
NK030(a)001:20083: dpal chen phyag na rdo rje la //
NK030(a)001:20084: mchod rten gnyis sogs dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20087: thub pa gyad kyi nye 'khor bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20088: dpal chen phyag na rdo rje la //
NK030(a)001:20092: bcom ldan rgya mtsho gling bzhugs dus //
NK030(a)001:20093: dpal chen phyag na rdo rje la //
NK030(a)001:20094: rgya mtshos dbang bskur skye med rtogs /
NK030(a)001:20097: bcom ldan zom du chos 'khor skor //
NK030(a)001:20098: phyag na rdo rje ri rab dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20099: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa ltar //
NK030(a)001:20100: 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20101: bcom ldan rdo rje gdan bzhugs dus /
NK030(a)001:20102: phyag rdor sa bzhis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20103: bkra shis byin chags dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20106: bcom ldan ba ra na s+air bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20107: phyag rdor bdud rtsis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20108: skye shi med pa'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20111: bcom ldan ri rab zam la bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20112: brgya byin dar gyi na bza' phul //
NK030(a)001:20113: chos sgra chen po'i byin rlabs ldan /
NK030(a)001:20116: bcom ldan rtsa gsum na bzhugs dus //
NK030(a)001:20117: brgya byin rin chen khri rkang phul //
NK030(a)001:20118: chos shes rgyud la go ba sgrogs /
NK030(a)001:20120: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20121: bcom ldan chos 'khor bskor ba la //
NK030(a)001:20122: brgya byin me tog sngon po phul /
NK030(a)001:20124: / 'khor ba bslu brid dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20127: bcom ldan ri rab khang bzang bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20128: lha bu dam pa 'od zhes pas //
NK030(a)001:20129: rnga yab phul bas gzi mdangs ldan /
NK030(a)001:20132: bcom ldan rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20133: lha bu 'od zer brdul yab phul //
NK030(a)001:20134: chos la skyon gyis ma gos ltar /
NK030(a)001:20137: bcom ldan nags tshal dgon par bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20138: rtsa gsum lha bus sbrang g.yab phul //
NK030(a)001:20139: sems can 'dzin chags skyon grol ltar /
NK030(a)001:20142: bcom ldan rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs /
NK030(a)001:20144: / 'khor ni rnam bzhis bla bres phul //
NK030(a)001:20145: nyon mongs gdung ba sel ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20148: bya rgod phung por chos 'khor bskor /
NK030(a)001:20150: / 'khor ni rnam bzhis rgyal mtshan phul //
NK030(a)001:20151: che ba'i yon tan mi nub ltar /
NK030(a)001:20154: bcom ldan skyed mos tshal bzhugs dus /
NK030(a)001:20156: / 'khor ni rnam bzhis gdugs phul bas //
NK030(a)001:20157: tsha ba'i sdug bsngal bsil ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20159: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20160: yangs pa can gyi drung bzhugs dus //
NK030(a)001:20161: nya pa rnams kyi nya brgya phul //
NK030(a)001:20162: nya pa lnga brgya sangs rgyas ltar /
NK030(a)001:20165: bcom ldan skyed mos tshal du gshegs //
NK030(a)001:20166: khyim bdag bu mo bzang ldan mas //
NK030(a)001:20167: sku reg gsol bas sku rten ltar /
NK030(a)001:20170: ri rab kha ba can bzhugs dus //
NK030(a)001:20171: gnod sbyin rnams kyi spos lnga phul //
NK030(a)001:20172: dbang po lnga tshim gyur pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20175: bcom ldan nags tshal chen por bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20176: klu yis snying po lnga rnams phul //
NK030(a)001:20177: mi mdzad mdzod du zhugs pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20179: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20180: bcom ldan gru 'dzin ri la bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20181: gnod sbyin rin chen sna lnga phul //
NK030(a)001:20182: mi zad nor mdzod ldan gyur ltar /
NK030(a)001:20184: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20185: a g+ha ma g+ha d+ha na bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20186: rgyal po gsal rgyal 'bru lnga phul //
NK030(a)001:20187: mi ge'i sdug bsngal zhi ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20189: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20190: bcom ldan tsan dan tshal du gshegs //
NK030(a)001:20191: gcan gzan stag gi sman lnga phul //
NK030(a)001:20192: bkra shis phun tshogs dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20195: bcom ldan seng ldeng tshal du gshegs //
NK030(a)001:20196: gcan zan rgyal po seng sprug gis //
NK030(a)001:20197: seng khri phyag phul bkra shis ltar /
NK030(a)001:20200: bcom ldan btang bzang chen por bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20201: sog pos 'bri ha phyag du phul //
NK030(a)001:20202: sman mchog sna lnga'i bkra shis ltar /
NK030(a)001:20205: rgyal byed tshal du bcom ldan bzhugs //
NK030(a)001:20206: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis //
NK030(a)001:20207: ha sa de phul bkra shis ltar /
NK030(a)001:20210: bcom ldan nags tshal gseb du gshegs //
NK030(a)001:20212: ka ta ka ri phul ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20215: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis //
NK030(a)001:20216: don 'grub sogs la phyag rgya yis //
NK030(a)001:20217: dbang bskur sku dang ye shes thob /
NK030(a)001:20220: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20222: / 'khor la snying po sngags dbang bskur //
NK030(a)001:20223: tshe dang ye shes phun gsum 'tshogs /
NK030(a)001:20226: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20228: / 'khor la gser thur dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20229: ma rig bsal nas ye shes gsal /
NK030(a)001:20232: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20234: / 'khor lo me long dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20235: chos rnams snang la rang bzhin med /
NK030(a)001:20238: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20242: / 'gro don thogs pa med pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20244: / 'dir 'tshogs dpon slob bcom ldan 'das la lha dbang gis //
NK030(a)001:20245: g.yas 'khyil dung phul chos sgra sgrogs //
NK030(a)001:20246: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug bcur ldan /
NK030(a)001:20249: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20251: / 'khor la me tog dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20252: tshul khrims 'phreng ba yongs su rdzogs /
NK030(a)001:20255: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20257: / 'khor la rdo rjes dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20258: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang thob 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:20260: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20261: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)001:20263: / 'khor la phyag rgyas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20264: yon tan rigs gyi dbang thob 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:20267: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20273: ri rab rtse mor rnams snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20275: / 'khor la rgya gram dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20276: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang thob 'gyur /
NK030(a)001:20279: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20281: / 'khor la seng ges dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20282: logs tshogs zil gyis mnon pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20285: ri rab rtse mor rnams snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20287: / 'khor la nyi mas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20288: ma rig mun pa sel ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20291: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20293: / 'khor la zla bas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20294: tsha ba'i sdug bsngal bsil ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20296: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20297: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20299: / 'khor la bdud rtsis bum dbang bskur //
NK030(a)001:20300: rnam par rtogs pa sel ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20303: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20304: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong gis //
NK030(a)001:20305: skor bas gling bzhi dbang 'dus ltar /
NK030(a)001:20308: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20309: rta mchog zhon nas gling bzhi po //
NK030(a)001:20310: nyi ma shar ka gcig las bgrod /
NK030(a)001:20313: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20314: glang po rin chen gser gyi dra ba g.yogs //
NK030(a)001:20315: g.yul las rgyal ba'i mthu dang ldan pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20318: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20319: nor bu rin chen rgyal mtshan rtser //
NK030(a)001:20320: btags pas thams cad gsal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20323: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20324: blon po rin chen lha mig ldan //
NK030(a)001:20325: dpag tshad tshun gyis gter rnams mthong /
NK030(a)001:20328: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20329: gzugs mdzes lta sdug btsun mo rin po che //
NK030(a)001:20330: reg na bde zhing yid du 'ong ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20332: / 'dir 'tshogs dpon slob rnams la bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20333: rgyal po rgyal rig dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20334: dmag dpon rin chen rgyal po bsam bzhin byed //
NK030(a)001:20335: pha rol dpung 'joms bsdo ba zil gyis non /
NK030(a)001:20338: rgyal po rgyal rigs dbang bskur dus //
NK030(a)001:20339: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20341: / 'khor la ral gris dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20342: nyon mongs gcod pa'i dbang bskur ltar /
NK030(a)001:20345: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20347: / 'khor la mda' gzhus dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20348: thabs dang shes rab dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20351: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20353: / 'khor la rnam ral dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20354: bar du gcod pa'i bdud 'joms ltar /
NK030(a)001:20357: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20359: / 'khor la shan gris dbang skur bas /
NK030(a)001:20361: / 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20364: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis //
NK030(a)001:20365: nye ba'i rin chen dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20366: bgegs dang log 'dren med pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20369: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20371: / 'khor la tshangs pa'i kha skud kyis //
NK030(a)001:20372: dbang bskur 'dod yon thob pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20375: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20377: / 'khor la na bzas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20378: grang ba'i sdug bsngal la skyobs pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20380: / 'dir tshogs dpon slob bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20381: ri rab rtse mor rnams snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20383: / 'khor la chags kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20387: ri rab rtse mo kun rigs kyis //
NK030(a)001:20388: khri snyan sa le'i spags pa yin //
NK030(a)001:20389: dbang bskur snying rje 'dren pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20392: bcom ldan 'das kyi yungs dkar gyis //
NK030(a)001:20393: rgyal po bgegs kyi gnyan por rlabs //
NK030(a)001:20394: stong phrag brgya bcus mi tshugs ltar /
NK030(a)001:20397: sngon gyis bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la /
NK030(a)001:20398: khyim bdag bzang skyongs zho phul bas //
NK030(a)001:20399: gzi brjid mdangs dang ldan pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20402: sngon gyi bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la //
NK030(a)001:20403: bram ze kun d+has r+ts+wa dur phul //
NK030(a)001:20404: dge rtsa brgya rtsar 'phel ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20407: sngon gyi bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la //
NK030(a)001:20408: sa'i lha mos li khri phul //
NK030(a)001:20409: chags pas sems can mi ltung bzhin /
NK030(a)001:20412: sngon gyi bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la //
NK030(a)001:20413: gzugs gyi lha mos me long phul //
NK030(a)001:20414: kun gzhi gnas gyur ye shes mthong /
NK030(a)001:20417: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20419: / 'khor la dung gis dbang bskur gnas //
NK030(a)001:20420: tshangs pa'i sgra sgrog gyur pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20423: sngon gyi bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la //
NK030(a)001:20424: glang po che na sa bsrung gis //
NK030(a)001:20425: g+hi hang phul bas nad sel ltar /
NK030(a)001:20428: sngon gyi bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la //
NK030(a)001:20429: shing tog bil ba phul ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20431: / 'bras bu'i chos rnams yongs su rdzogs /
NK030(a)001:20434: bcom ldan bdud kyis bsdo dus su //
NK030(a)001:20435: thugs kyi dpal ber bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20436: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20439: bcom ldan bdud kyi brgol ba'i dus /
NK030(a)001:20440: sku la rgyal mtshan bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20441: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20444: bcom ldan bdud kyi rgal ba'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20445: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20446: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20449: bcom ldan bdud kyis bsdo dus su //
NK030(a)001:20450: ljags la pad+ma'i bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20451: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20454: bcom ldan bdud kyi rgal ba'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20455: mgul la bum pa'i bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20456: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20459: bcom ldan bdud kyi rgal ba'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20460: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20461: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20464: bcom ldan bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20465: tshem la dung gi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20466: bsdo ba'i phyogs las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20469: bcom ldan bdud kyi bsdo ba'i dus //
NK030(a)001:20470: phyag zhabs nya'i bkra shis pas //
NK030(a)001:20471: bsdo ba'i bdud las rgyal ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20474: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20476: / 'khor la rgya gram dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)001:20481: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20488: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20490: / 'khor la p+au tsas dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20491: rgyal theb skar ma'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20494: ri rab brtse mor kun rigs gis /
NK030(a)001:20496: / 'khor la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20497: tha dag nyan pa'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20500: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20502: / 'khor la chags shing dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20503: chos rnams 'chad pa'i dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20506: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20508: / 'khor la po tis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20509: chos kyi sgo la mkhas pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20512: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)001:20514: / 'khor la rdor dril dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20515: ye shes chos dbyings rtogs par ltar /
NK030(a)001:20518: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)001:20520: / 'khor la brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20521: chos kyi rgyal srid thob pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20524: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20526: / 'khor la dbu brgyan dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20527: mi 'jigs pa la mnga' mnyes ltar /
NK030(a)001:20530: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs gis /
NK030(a)001:20532: / 'khor la zhabs gdub dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20533: stobs bcu mnga' mnyes dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20536: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)001:20538: / 'khor la phyag gdub dbang bskur pas //
NK030(a)001:20539: tshul khrims rnam dag dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20542: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)001:20544: / 'khor la do shal dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20545: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa ltar /
NK030(a)001:20548: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20550: / 'khor la cod pan dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20551: brdul gyi bag chags bral ba ltar /
NK030(a)001:20554: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)001:20556: / 'khor la ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20557: rdo rje 'chang gi dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)001:20560: ri rab rtse mor don 'grub la //
NK030(a)001:20561: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)001:20562: rnam snang nyid du sangs rgyas ltar /
NK030(a)001:20565: sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang /
NK030(a)001:20566: gsung lnga lhun grub dam chos rgya mtsho dang //
NK030(a)001:20567: thugs lnga lhun grub rgyal sras smin pa'i tshogs /
NK030(a)001:20569: / 'dir 'tshogs dpon slob rnams kyis bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20570: rdzogs sangs rgyas nas da lta'i bar //
NK030(a)001:20571: bum chu gcig nas gcig byo dang //
NK030(a)001:20572: mar me gcig nas gcig spar bzhin //
NK030(a)001:20573: dus rgyun 'chad med pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)001:20574: gsum pa brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK030(a)001:20575: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen nas //
NK030(a)001:20576: bdag gi bar du rim pa bzhin //
NK030(a)001:20577: snyan brgyud gdams pa ma 'chugs pa'i //
NK030(a)001:20578: cho ga rim bzhin bri tshar bas //
NK030(a)001:20579: dam bca' dang po sangs pa yis //
NK030(a)001:20580: dbang gi chu bo rnam pa bzhi //
NK030(a)001:20581: rgya mtsho chen por bskyil ba yis //
NK030(a)001:20582: legs bshad rim pa tshar ba dang //
NK030(a)001:20583: dam bca' gnyis pa sangs pa yin //
NK030(a)001:20584: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga //
NK030(a)001:20585: bsnyen pa dang ni nye ba'i bsnyen //
NK030(a)001:20586: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK030(a)001:20587: legs par bkod pa gsum pa sangs //
NK030(a)001:20588: re shig bshad du ma mchis pas //
NK030(a)001:20589: rdzogs so zhes ni tha snyad brjod //
NK030(a)001:20590: bkra shis dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK030(a)001:20591: phan thogs 'dzam gling brgyan gyur cig /
